Chào mừng bạn đến với bộ sưu tập miễn phí đặc biệt của những công thức giúp bạn nấu được những món ăn ngon miệng nhất, hấp dẫn nhất và cũng độc đáo nhất – DẠY NẤU ĂN.* Một trong những Cuốn sổ tay Công thức nấu ăn miễn phí ĐỘC ĐÁO và TIỆN LỢI nhất giúp bạn KHÁM PHÁ thế giới ẩm thực với hàng nghìn món ăn ngon miệng một cách thật DỄ DÀNG và ĐƠN GIẢN.* TRẢI NGHIỆM cảm giác của một Đầu bếp thực thụ với khả năng biến hóa hàng trăm món ăn khác nhau chỉ bằng một loại nguyên liệu với những hướng dẫn chi tiết cụ thể từ ứng dụng DẠY NẤU ĂN này.Hơn 7.000 món ăn với 50 thể loại đang chờ bạn khám phá được cập nhật hằng ngày trên hệ thống Online* Bạn muốn nấu một bữa ăn thật ngon với những công thức thật mới lạ, độc đáo nhưng cũng không kém phần hấp dẫn cho gia đình, bạn bè và người thân? ứng dụng DẠY NẤU ĂN sẽ giúp bạn làm được điều đó một cách thật đơn giản, thay vì phải nghiên cứu và tỉ mẩn ngồi đọc những quyển sách dạy nấu ăn dày cộp và khô khan.* Với một loạt các hướng dẫn nấu ăn và công thức được trình bày một cách chi tiết và cụ thể, kèm theo hình ảnh minh họa sinh động, bạn hoàn toàn có thể biến hóa và trải nghiêm với các món ăn truyền thống của chính đất nước mình. Những món ăn mà bạn tưởng như vô cùng phức tạp và cầu kì sẽ trở nên vô cùng đơn giản dưới sự hướng dẫn của ứng dụng DẠY NẤU ĂN.Chúc các bạn thành công và hạnh phúc.

appName: 倩女幽魂 - 孫慧雪化身小倩全力推薦
description: =======《倩女幽魂》新玩法大改版！======全新職業女甲士震撼登場，一槍入魂就係咁簡單！新增轉職系統七大職業話轉就轉。跨服關寧校場、幫會宣戰爭奪全服最強王者！夢島新功能幫你識盡全港九新界倩女玩家！『女甲士震撼登場，轉職系統話轉就轉』新加入嘅女甲士作為團隊核心角色，係你最堅強嘅護盾！坦王吸怪團隊輔助，配埋出色嘅突進控場俾你一槍入魂！轉職系統俾你隨心所欲體驗各職業奧義技能，連裝備都幫你一Take過轉換！『跨服PK爭奪全服王者，幫派宣戰捍衛榮譽』關寧校場跨服對決，全服王者等你嚟挑機，感受前所未有嘅刺激感！全新幫會宣戰系統，考驗你嘅團隊默契，唔怕神一樣嘅對手，有成班兄弟幫你一齊捍衛幫派榮譽！『夢島熱點交友零障礙，全新座騎等你收服』開通全服熱點分享，幫你網羅全港九新界嘅倩女巴打絲打，交友從此零障礙！騎上全新雙人座騎-雪鵰，同你嘅心愛俠侶暢遊三界，即刻成為全場焦點！ ======================================【遊戲介紹】堅靚‧堅本地！經典原著改編超高質RPG遊戲！由香港《倩女幽魂》原著改編手機版，全廣東話完整呈現淒美動人故事，並配以全3D電影級畫質，帶你走入經典玄幻嘅古風世界！『六大職業有特色，天賦配點考知識』甲士、異人、射手、方士、魅者、醫師六大職業各具特色，坦打補控定位清晰。每個職業仲有三種唔同天賦配點，可自由組合技能駁招，俾你最刺激震撼嘅ARPG Combo新體驗！『香港配音最純正，電影畫級至高清』全程以小倩甜美聲線同你聲音導航，大家熟悉嘅經典角色寧采臣、燕赤霞通通番哂嚟！加上遊戲栩栩如生嘅電影級高清畫質，忠實還原「人鬼仙」三界場景，帶俾你最熟悉嘅《倩女幽魂》！『裝備自由可交易，公平競爭有肉食』公認遊戲中最公平嘅自由交易系統，神裝珍寶通通可透過市場的公平競賣，亦可透過1:1方式自由交易，確保大家絕對有付出有肉食。當然，組隊打寶都有公平嘅分寶方式自由選擇，靚裝勁寶Easy拎！『打殘歷代鬼Boss，約齊班Frd嚟Happy』帶你重溫金陵、逍遙觀、蘭若寺等主線經典劇情，挑戰歷代鬼王。再加埋勇闖墓穴奪寶，野外實感PVP、天下比武會、千人幫會賽等等刺激體驗！《倩女幽魂》還原組隊打寶樂趣，係人係鬼？打下咪知囉！ 『今日人鬼情未了，夢島系統隨你DIY』跨越三界嘅戀愛，識得玩梗係要娶返個「鬼」火咁靚嘅新娘！加埋原創特有「夢島」系統，DIY個性造型，跨服識朋友、拜個神仙師徒就係咁簡單！

For Experian Credit Tracker℠ members in the U.S., this app lets you quickly access your Experian Credit Report, FICO® Score, and monitor your credit. Your Experian Credit Report and FICO Score are automatically updated for you each day you sign in to the app, ensuring you always have today’s up-to-date credit information at your fingertips. You’ll also get notifications on your Android device when key updates to your credit report are detected.As an Experian Credit Tracker member, just sign in to your account with your Username and Password to start using the app.Key Features:CREDIT REPORTS•View your full Experian Credit Report so you can see the same kind of information that banks see – including all of your credit accounts, inquiries, and any public records.•Your Experian Credit Report will automatically be updated every day when you sign in.FICO SCORE•Get your current FICO Credit Score. FICO Scores are used in 90% of credit decisions. •Track how your FICO Score changes over time and see the key areas that influence your FICO Score.•Score Factors tell you which of your financial behaviors are helping and hurting your FICO Score. •Your FICO Score will automatically be updated every day when you sign in.CREDIT MONITORING & ALERTS•We monitor changes to your credit profile such as when a new credit account is opened in your name, an address change is reported, or an inquiry appears on your credit report.•When these changes occur, we’ll send you an alert so that you can view it right away on your device.CREDIT AT-A-GLANCE•Dashboard provides an overview of your most recent credit health and trends.•Your Credit Summary shows you the five key elements that make up your FICO Score based on your Experian Credit Report.NOT A MEMBER YET?•Buy your Experian Credit Report for $1 and start your 7-day trial membership with Experian Credit Tracker. After the trial is over, your membership will be $21.95/month.•Just tap “Sign Up” and complete the enrollment process on your device – then you’ll have unlimited access to your Experian credit data and monitoring!Download the new Experian Credit Tracker app for Android devices today for a faster, easier way to access your credit on the go.FAQs:•What’s a FICO® Score? Which credit score does Experian Credit Tracker offer? FICO® Scores are developed by the Fair Isaac Corporation and are used in 90% of credit decisions. While your score may vary based on the specific scoring model the lender chooses to use, your score range is likely the same across the board. Experian Credit Tracker uses the FICO 8 scoring model to calculate your FICO Score using information drawn from your Experian credit report.•How often does my credit score get updated? Why doesn’t my score update immediately when I pay off a bill? Your FICO 8 Score responds to changes in your credit activity and is based on factors that include your payment history, amount currently owed, length of your overall credit history, and any new credit accounts. Experian Credit Tracker updates your FICO Score automatically the first time you sign in each day, so if changes in your credit have been reported, you’ll see them appear then. Remember, your credit activity is reported to the major credit bureaus by your creditors and lenders, and may not be reported immediately upon receipt of your payment. Changes will show up once your creditors report them to Experian.•How much does the app cost? There’s no cost to use the app: it’s available to download as part of your existing Experian Credit Tracker membership without an additional charge.Follow Us:http://www.facebook.com/experianhttp://www.twitter.com/Experian_US http://www.plus.google.com/+experian/posts http://www.youtube.com/experian http://www.experian.tumblr.com http://www.pinterest.com/experian http://www.instagram.com/experian

Kuik Taxi es la App gratuita que cuenta con la mayor flota de taxis de Catalunya. Con esta aplicación podrás solicitar un taxi allí donde te encuentres: en una terraza tomando un café, en el sillón de casa o al finalizar una reunión de negocios. En la pantalla observarás la posición exacta del taxi mientras viene a recogerte, y si lo deseas, también mientras te lleva como pasajero. Una vez llegues al destino podrás abonar el importe en efectivo, con tarjeta, vía App o con tu cuenta de empresa.Kuik Taxi es la App con más taxis en Catalunya. ¿Quién crees que te recogerá antes?La única con soporte telefónico los 365 días del año, las 24 horas del día. ¿Te has dejado un paraguas, una maleta o documentos importantes dentro del taxi? Llama a nuestras operadoras, localizarán el taxi en el que ibas y resolverán todas tus dudas.Kuik Taxi ya está disponible en el Área Metropolitana de Barcelona, en la ciudad de Girona y poblaciones cercanas, en Vilaseca y en Salou. En breve está previsto que esté disponible en el resto de poblaciones del área urbana de Catalunya.ES MUY FÁCIL DE UTILIZARCon solo dos clics.1. Selecciona tu ubicación. Confirma el punto de recogida.2. Elige cuando quieres que te recojan, las opciones y el medio de pago.¡Te sorprenderá lo rápido que llega tu taxi!

Dünyaca ses getiren 1010! ve Merged! oyunlarının geliştiricisi Gram Games’den yepyeni bir oyun: Six!. Bu oyun hem iddialı, hem de heyecan verici fakat aynı zamanda da sinir bozucu. Tüm büyük bulmaca oyunlarında olduğu gibi Six! de, bir dakikalık kısa zaman aralığı ya da saatlerce süren eğlence için gerçekten harika bir seçenek olma niteliğinde.Oyunda; üzerinde altıgen bir blok duran ve farklı şekilli tuğlalardan oluşmuş bir kule bloğuyla etkileşime geçme göreviniz var. Amacınız ise puan kazanabilmek için altıgen bloğu kule bloğundan aşağı indirmek. Bu adımı da tuğlaların üzerine dokunma ile onları yok ederek ve altında açılan boşluğa altıgeni indirerek başarıyorsunuz.Kulağa kolay gelse de, altıgen yuvarlanmaya veya kule eğilmeye başladığında aslında düşündüğünüz kadar kolay olmadığını fark ediyorsunuz. Blokların kaldırılması ile kuleyi yıkar ya da altıgen kazandığı ivmeyle ekrandan yuvarlanır ise oyun sona ermiş demektir ve en baştan başlamanız gerekir.Oynaması son derece basit, keyifli ve bir o kadar da heyecanlı.Six!, kuleyi indirebildiğiniz kadar aşağı çekmeye çalışırken sizi kendine bağlamış olacak. Gram Games’in popüler oyunlarıyla uyumlu olarak, bu bulmaca oyununu da oynamak kolay ve eğlenceli olacak fakat liderlik tahtasında yer edinmek ve arkadaşlarınızın önüne geçmek mücadeleci ve ödüllendirici olacak.Ana Özellikler•    Öğrenmesi kolay ve oyun içinde ustalaşması eğlenceli,•    Arkadaşlarınızın yüksek skorlarına ve tüm dünyaya meydan okumaca,•    Merak uyandırıcı ve alışkanlık yapıcı,•    Eğlenceli ve sempatik görseller.

Если с Вами ребенок, мы предоставим бустер.Особенности приложения:- New: удобная навигация, заказ такси за минуту- Прозрачные тарифы (виджет на главном экране и в профиле)- New: оплата банковской картой- Возможность отследить автомобиль по карте и связаться с водителем по телефону- Контроль качества поездки и оценка водителяДля Вас во время поездки: - Вежливые и молчаливые водители, знающие город- Бустер для Вашего ребенка - Бесплатный WiFi в салоне, возможность зарядить телефон- Отслеживание рейса, встреча с табличкой в аэропорту или на вокзале- Доступна перевозка домашних животныхВот каким должно быть настоящее городское такси!

Avec Napster Unlimited plus Mobile, vous pouvez écouter toute la musique que vous aimez sur mobile et tablette Android. Avec plus de 25 millions de titres en tout genre et de nouvelles musiques ajoutées tous les jours, si c’est de la musique, nous l’avons ! La nouvelle appli pour téléphone Android est ici. Une appli plus rapide, plus intelligente et plus jolie pour votre téléphone. Un nouvel écran d’accueil vous permet de naviguer plus facilement jusqu’aux musiques. La fonction Relecture se rappelle des chansons que vous avez écoutées et à quel moment. L’idéal pour les listes de lecture pendant vos séances d’exercice, les trajets en voiture avec des enfants, etc. Vous voulez découvrir de nouveaux morceaux ? Vous aurez accès à un flux continu de nouvelles suggestions musicales, de critiques d’albums et de publications de notre équipe éditoriale.Cela dit, n’oubliez pas notre appli pour tablette. Il ne s’agit pas d’un simple redimensionnement de l’application, mais d’une nouvelle expérience à part entière. Plus tactile, plus agréable, avec des quantités de contenus et de nouveaux moyens de découvrir la musique.Vérifiez par vous-même : vous pouvez essayer Napster GRATUITEMENT pendant 7 jours pour découvrir le plaisir de pouvoir écouter de la musique en illimité partout où vous allez.Fonctions incluses :- 7 jours d’essai gratuit- Des millions de chansons à écouter en ligne- Enregistrement des chansons hors ligne pour les écouter sans connexion- Recommandations de notre équipe de mordus de la musique- Les dernières nouveautés musicales ajoutées tous les lundis- Partage facile de la musique avec vos amis : Facebook, Twitter, c’est vous qui décidez- Synchronisation automatique de la musique entre votre portable et votre ordinateurSi vous possédez une tablette Android, nous avons une appli qui vous est spécialement dédiée. Il ne s’agit pas d’un simple redimensionnement de l’application, mais d’une nouvelle expérience pour profiter pleinement de la taille de la tablette.Si vous êtes déjà membre de Napster Unlimited plus Mobile, il vous suffit de télécharger l’application pour commencer à écouter. Si vous débutez, visitez www.napster.com, inscrivez-vous pour l’essai gratuit et connectez-vous à l’application à l’aide de vos identifiants.

appName: ดาบมังกรหยก 3D - TH
description: ดาบมังกรหยก3D-TH เกมส์มือถือกำลังภายในอันดับ 1 ที่ดำเนินเรื่องด้วยวัฒนธรรมที่น่าภาคภูมิใจของแดนมังกร ได้รับลิขสิทธิ์จากกิมย้งโดยตรง เพื่อทำเป็นเกมส์แนวMMOARPGที่มีวิธีเล่นหลากหลาย ชาวเกมเมอร์จะได้ตะลุยยุทธภพที่เต็มไปด้วยบุญคุณและหนี้แค้นไปพร้อมเตียบ่อกี้และเตี๊ยเมี่ยง ดันเจี้ยนบทละครมากมาย พร้อมสงครามที่มีหลากชีวิตเป็นเดิมพัน กับวิชาตัวเบาที่จะทำให้คุณได้พบกับความอิสระแบบที่ไม่เคยมีมา และฟังก์ชั่นที่เกี่ยวข้องกับวัฒนธรรมที่น่าสนใจต่างๆ อีกมากมาย กราฟฟิกระดับจอเงิน ให้ความคมชัดสูงมาก จนคุณจะต้องตะลึงจนตาค้าง สุดท้ายนี้ ยังมีกระบี่อิงฟ้าและดาบฆ่ามังกรที่จะแผลงความเป็นจอมยุทธ์ในตัวของคุณออกมาได้เป็นอย่างดี ทั้งหมดนี้ พร้อมจะประจักษ์สู่สายตาของเกมเมอร์ทุกท่านแล้ว เกมส์นี้ยังเคยร่วมงานนิทรรศการเกมส์ Gamescom และ Tokyo Game Show มาแล้ว และได้รับเสียงตอบรับจากสื่อและเกมเมอร์ต่างชาติเป็นอย่างดีจุดเด่นของเกม★เกมมือถือออนไลน์3Dที่ได้รับลิขสิทธิ์แท้จากกิมย้ง กำลังภายในของจริง100%ที่ได้รับการสืบทอดยอดเยี่ยม ดาบฆ่ามังกร ผู้นำแห่งปฐพี อาวุธในตำนานที่กำเนิดจากผู้เชี่ยวชาญ ถ่ายทอดความเป็นดาบฆ่ามังกร กระบี่อิงฟ้าแบบดั้งเดิม เกมเมอร์สามารถเลือกได้ว่าต้องการเป็นชาวเส้าหลิน บู๊ตึ๊ง ง้อไบ๊หรือเม้งก่า ร่วมชิงดาบฆ่ามังกรกับผู้เล่นนับหมื่นเพื่อเฟ้นหาผู้ชนะคนนั้น!!★กราฟฟิกล้ำยุค PKพร้อมกันเป็นร้อยคน กับศึกชิงชัยสำนัก ไม่ได้ชัยชนะก็ไม่มีวันเลิกรา วรยุทธอมตะ ทำลายศัตรูด้วยปลายเล็บ สุดยอดสกิล มันส์สะท้านทรวง เตรียมตัวพบกับสกิลหลบหลีก สกิลถล่มตีและสกิลท่าไม้ตาย จัดคอมโบเทพๆ ดาเมจแรงๆ หรือจะรักษาลูกทีม พลิกสถานการณ์ให้ทันเวลาก็ได้เช่นกัน ให้กลยุทธ์และการแข่งขันปะทะกันมันส์ยิ่งกว่าเดิม!★เกมส์นี้นำระบบ Era รุ่นที่ 3 ที่ทาง Perfect World พัฒนาขึ้นเองมาใช้ด้วย เพื่อเพิ่มความสมจริงด้านแสง สีและเสียงให้กับนิยายกำลังภายในจากแผ่นดินจีนนี้ ให้มีชีวิตชีวายิ่งกว่าเดิม★วิชาตัวเบาอิสระ ล่องลอยทั่วยุทธภพ ล่องลอยบนน้ำด้วยวิชาตัวเบา สุดยอดวิชาไร้ขีดจำกัด กราฟฟิกล้ำยุค คมชัดทะลุจอ ให้คุณฟินกับยุทธภพได้เต็มที่★เกมส์นี้ได้จัดระบบแต่งงานให้จอมยุทธ์ทั้งหลายบอกลาชีวิตที่มีแต่ความเหงา เพราะแม้จะเป็นจอมยุทธ์ ก็ไม่อาจใช้ชีวิตอย่างเดียวดายได้ แถมยังมีฉายาคู่รักพิเศษ โบนัสทักษะ กิจกรรมต่างๆ ให้ความสัมพันธ์ของคู่รักช้ายสาวทั้งหลายลึกซึ้ง แน่นแฟ้นยิ่งกว่าเดิม!★สร้างสรรค์มหาศัสตราวุธ พร้อมพิณ หมากรุก ตำรา ภาพวาด ที่สุดแห่งยุทธภพ แถมยังมียุทธภพบังเอิญ จอมยุทธ์ You must drive a mobster crime boss around the city while he takes on the police. Its an offer you cannot refuse. Be careful - he's a little crazy. The goal is to race around the city without getting stopped by the cops. All in super fun 3D graphics and Taxi driving gameplay.6 INSANE LEVELS:Mobster Taxi Training - you gotta get some driving skills firstTruck Thief - steal some boxes from a truckRob a Bank - you gotta get the money, watch out for the policePay your debts - this crazy taxi driver owes some moneyRevenge - time for some paybackEscape from the City - you are a wanted criminal, get outta the city.REAL 3D CITY ENVIRONMENT-Race the Taxi through a real city environment-Encounter other cars and objects-Watch out for the police, they will chase you.Don't wait any longer, come and give Mob Taxi a try.

بانک پیامک پاپیون - نسخه ۲ ( کاملا رایگان )مجموعه ای از جذاب ترین پیامک ها ( بیش از 26000 پیامک ) در 17 موضوع اصلی و 140 زیر گروه مختلف به همراه آپدیت دوره ای***** با ۵ ستاره از ما حمایت کنید *****----------------------------------------------------دسته بندی پیامک ها ( موضوعات اصلی ) :خنده و سرگرمیعاشقانهجدیداحساساتغمگینروابطزیبافلسفی و پندآموزمذهبیرفاقت و دوستیشعر و ضرب المثلورزشیتبریک و تسلیتمناسبت هامتفرقهپیامک به زبان انگلیسیپیامک به زبان های دیگرو در 140 زیر گروه----------------------------------------------------برخی قابلیت های برنامه :طراحی سبک و زیبادارای موضوعات متنوع و جدیدآپدیت دوره ای ( ++ آپدیت ویژه مناسبت ها)امکان آپدیت پیامک ها از درون برنامه ( به صورت کلی و جداگانه )بدون پیامک تکراری ( حذف شده توسط سیستم پاپیون )دارای سیستم سریع جستجو در کل پیامک ها (سیستم جدید ، سریع تر از همیشه)قابلیت ارسال برنامه از طریق بلوتوث ، ایمیل و ....قابلیت برجسته کردن کلمه جستجو شده ( فعال کردن در تنظیمات )قابلیت انتخاب پیامک ها به عنوان منتخب ، خوانده شده ، حذف پیامک ها و بازگرداندن پیامک حذف شدهقابلیت ارسال بدون دردسر پیامک ها و همچنین کپی پیامک هاقابلیت به اشتراک گذاری پیامک ها در واتس اپ ، هنگ اوت ، نیمباز ، ایمیل و ....دارای تنظیمات فونت ( نوع فونت ، اندازه ، رنگ )قابلیت جابجایی سریع در صفحهقابلیت حل مشکل نمایش زبان فارسی در دستگاه هایی که از فارسی پشتیبانی نمی کنند.بخش ارتباط با ما جهت ارتباط بیشتر ما و شما ( ارسال نظرات ، پیشنهادات و مشکلات برنامه )راهنمای کامل برنامه ( راهنمایی تعاملی و اینتراکتیو )++ همچنین شما می توانید پیامک های خودتون رو با استفاده از سیستم "ارسال پیامک به پاپیون" برای ما فرستاده و پس از تایید با نام خود مشاهده فرمایید.

123Banking ist eine Onlinebanking App, mit der sich Konten von vielen verschiedenen HBCI-fähigen Banken gleichzeitig nutzen lassen. Umsätze, Kontostand, Überweisung - Sie haben Ihre aktuellen Finanzen immer Mobil verfügbar.MULTIBANK- UND MULTIKONTENFÄHIGMit unserer 123Banking App lassen sich beliebig viele Konten aller Banken und Sparkassen, welche den HBCI oder FinTS Standard unterstützen, verwalten. Außerdem können Sie Kassenbücher anlegen, in denen Sie selbst Umsätze eintragen können.Bei der Entwicklung dieser Online Banking App stand die Unterstützung und Verwaltung mehrerer Banken und Sparkassen im Vordergrund.Folgende Banken werden von 123Banking unterstützt und sind somit auch für Sie verfügbar:- Sparkasse- Haspa (Sparkasse Hamburg)- Postbank- Deutsche Bank- Volksbanken und Raiffeisenbanken- Sparda Bank- DKB (Deutsche Kreditbank),ebenfalls DKB VISA CASH- HVB (Hypovereinsbank)- comdirect- Cortal Consors- 1822direkt- Sofortbank- Norisbank- ING-DiBa- Oyak Anker Bank- Umweltbank- netbank- Commerzbank (per HBCI-Schlüsseldatei)- Ihre Bank oder Sparkasse ist nicht dabei? Keine Sorge wir unterstützen noch viele weitere Kreditinstitute, probieren Sie es einfach aus!Sollte eine Ihrer Banken nicht dabei sein oder nicht in der Banksuche auftauchen, liegt dies wahrscheinlich daran, dass diese kein HBCI-Protokoll unterstützt.Folgende Kreditinstitute können wir somit leider nicht unterstützen:- Bank of Scotland- Targobank- DABbank - Direkt Anlagen Bank- Santander Bank- KFW- BMW Bank- VW BankKOMPATIBILITÄT UND UNTERSTÜTZUNGÜber diese Onlinebanking Applikation ist es Ihnen möglich Umsatz- und Saldenabfragen, sowie Inlands- und SEPA-Überweisungen bei Ihrem deutschen Bankinstitut von Ihrem Smartphone aus durchzuführen.Die Finanzverwaltung erfolgt über Ihren normalen HBCI-Zugang und Überweisungen werden wie gewohnt mit Ihren gewählten TAN-Medien freigegeben.Die 123Banking App unterstützt alle aktuellen und somit sicheren TAN-Medien, wie TAN-Liste (iTAN), optische und manuelle TAN-Verfahren über einen TANGenerator (Chip-TAN, Sm@rtTan) und SMS-TAN (MobileTAN).Ob Girokonto, Kreditkarte, Tagesgeldkonto, Darlehenskonto, Bausparvertrag oder Sparbücher - Mit unserer App haben Sie alle Ihre Bankprodukte von allen Ihren Kreditinstituten immer per Mobilebanking im Blick.SICHERHEITUm das Onlinebanking mit dem Smartphone möglichst sicher zu gestalten, werden alle Daten, welche 123Banking auf dem Handy speichert, mit einer Mischung aus AES- und RSA-Verschlüsselung geschützt.Zudem legt der Nutzer bei der Einrichtung der App ein Passwort fest. Wird dieses mehrfach falsch eingegeben, werden alle gespeicherten Kontodaten auf dem mobile banking-fähigen Handy automatisch gelöscht.Ein Missbrauch ist somit ausgeschlossen. Ohne Kenntnis des Passworts sind Ihre Finanzen nicht sichtbar.Durch regelmäßige Updates wird ein sicherer Standard realisiert.FUNKTIONAL UND KOMFORTABELBei der Entwicklung unserer Online Banking App wurde auf eine übersichtliche und leichte Bedienbarkeit geachtet. Verständliche Icons und Android-bekannte Funktionen wie Wischen zum Seitenwechsel machen die Handhabung der App intuitiv und selbsterklärend.Aber auch komfortable Funktionen wie z.B. Drag&Drop zur Kontensortierung wurden integriert.Mit der „Ein-Klick-Überweisung“ kann der Empfänger aus der Liste der Bankkontakte aus bestehenden Umsätzen gewählt werden.Soweit unterstützt sind sowohl Inlands-, als auch SEPA-Überweisungen möglich. Mit dem integrierten IBAN-Rechner werden dabei IBAN und BIC automatisch errechnet.Natürlich funktioniert 123 Banking auch mit Ihrem Android Tablet.Bevor Sie mit einem oder zwei Sternen bewerten, geben Sie uns die Chance nachzubessern.ÜBER DEN HERAUSGEBER, PETAFUEL:Die petaFuel GmbH, ein vom TÜV Süd zertifizierter Entwickler von Finanzdienstleistungssoftware.

appName: ホットペッパー グルメ 飲食店予約とお得なクーポン検索
description: リクルートが提供する日本最大級のグルメ情報サイト「ホットペッパー グルメ」の公式アプリです。「近くに安くておいしいお店ないかな？」「どうせ行くならおいしいものをお得に食べたい！」「来週のデートは雰囲気が良いレストランがいいな」そんなあなたが求めている条件にぴったりのお店を探すことができます。もちろんお得なクーポンも探せます。たとえば・女子会やデートの人気店・誕生日や記念日にサプライズできるお店・二次会のカラオケ・食べ放題や飲み放題がある居酒屋・雰囲気の良いバーや夜カフェのお店■機能内容1)アプリからお店をすぐに予約できるお店の空席状況を確認して空きがあれば、アプリからすぐに予約ができます。二次会のお店探しにも便利です。（※即予約に対応している店舗に限ります）2)条件検索 現在地や駅・エリア、お店のジャンルや予算などからサクサクお店を探すことができます。3)地図検索 地図検索を使えば、オフィスの近くや観光地の近くなど、自分の行きたい場所の近くにあるお店が地図で探せます。4)画像がきれい 店舗の雰囲気や料理の写真など大きくて綺麗なお店の写真がたくさんあります。5)いま営業中のお店がその場で見つかる 現在地取得機能を利用すれば、今営業中のお店を簡単に探すことができます。6)クーポンでおトクに！ もちろん、おトクなクーポンもついています。お店でクーポン画面を掲示すると、クーポンに記載されたサービスを受けることができます。ホットペッパーグルメアプリで、会社の歓送迎会や忘年会、友人との楽しい食事、家族とのディナーや記念日も、いつもの食事に「嬉しい」をプラスしよう☆■アクセス権限について ・現在地 (GPS/ネットワーク基地局)　現在地検索や周辺のお店検索で現在地を取得します。・端末のステータスと ID の読み取り　利便性の向上及び統計データ作成の為にアクセスログ、エラーログを取得しています。　※法的に要求された場合を除き、第三者に当該ログは公開しません。■Androidバージョン4.0未満をお使いの方へ2015年6月1日をもちまして、Androidバージョン4.0未満のサポートを終了させていただきます。今後アプリのアップデートおよび新規インストールが出来なくなりますが、ダウンロード済みのアプリは引き続き利用することが可能です。Androidバージョン4.0以降の端末につきましては引き続き利用可能です。■アプリバージョン4.7.0以下のアプリをお使いの方へ2015年4月16日（木）より、バージョンが4.7.0以下のアプリからは、会員ログインができなくなります。最新バージョンにアップデートをしますとログインできるようになりますので、対象のアプリをご利用のかたは、アップデートをお願いします。ご不便おかけしますが、よろしくお願いします。■ホットペッパー グルメのWebサイトはこちらhttp://www.hotpepper.jp/【お問い合わせ】皆様のご意見を聞き、より良いアプリにしていきます。ご要望や不具合は下記のURLまでをお寄せください。http://goo.gl/wxs1f

TrueCar is a free service that helps car buyers connect with our network of over 10,000 new car dealers across the U.S. Each TrueCar Certified Dealer is committed to providing upfront pricing information for every vehicle on the lot – including full disclosure of any hidden costs or fees – in a hassle-free car buying experience for TrueCar members. The TrueCar car buying app provides tools to understand the current market price for brand new cars and trucks in your local area, and helps you understand the Guaranteed Savings* being offered by each TrueCar Certified Dealer. The app also includes a tool that reveals the TrueCar Price from any window sticker while on a TrueCar Certified Dealer's lot.This should help you understand what we're about:• A service designed to provide new car buying without hassle or stress.• See what others paid in your local area and compare that to the TrueCar Estimate.• Get Guaranteed Savings buying from a TrueCar Certified Dealer (an average of $3,221 off MSRP!!)**• Access to dealers committed to price transparency with upfront prices on every new car in stock.• Know which salesperson to ask for to make sure you get the TrueCar hassle-free buying experience.• No surprises, hidden fees or "extras" baked into your deal – you always know how much you should pay.• Search through all the new cars at TrueCar Certified Dealers to get the TrueCar Price while on the lot, or simply scan window sticker barcodes.• No pressure to make a decision or stress over negotiating the price.• Easily configure and save your ideal vehicle with your favorite options, colors and the very latest manufacturer incentives.• Get competitive price estimates for the new car you desire from up to three TrueCar Certified Dealers.• Receive offers on in-stock vehicles within 24 hours of engaging with your dealer.Some stuff our marketing team thought we should mention:• 97% of TrueCar users who purchased a car from a Certified Dealer would recommend to others. (That's pretty cool.)• Over 2 million cars sold by TrueCar Certified Dealers to our members.• Members buying with TrueCar have saved more than $1 billion off MSRP.Some stuff the lawyers wanted us to mention:* Guaranteed Savings currently not available in all states. In these instances, a "Target Price" is presented, which is not an advertised price, but an example of what you can reasonably expect to pay for a vehicle with your preferred options. Guaranteed Savings represents the amount that a TrueCar Certified Dealer selected by you guarantees that you will save off the Manufacturer's Suggested Retail Price ("MSRP") on any in-stock vehicle that is the same make, model, and trim as your Ideal Vehicle. The Guaranteed Savings is based on a vehicle without factory or dealer installed options and includes generally available manufacturer incentives.** Between 4/1/14 and 6/30/14, the average estimated savings off MSRP presented by TrueCar Certified Dealers to users of TrueCar powered websites, based on users who configured virtual vehicles and subsequently purchased a new vehicle of the same make and model listed on the certificate from Certified Dealers, was $3,221, including applicable vehicle specific manufacturer incentives. Your actual savings may vary based on multiple factors including the vehicle you select, region, dealer, and applicable vehicle specific manufacturer incentives which are subject to change. The Manufacturer's Suggested Retail Price ("MSRP") is determined by the manufacturer, and may not reflect the price at which vehicles are generally sold in the dealer's trade area as not all vehicles are sold at MSRP. Each dealer sets its own pricing. Your actual purchase price is negotiated between you and the dealer. TrueCar does not sell or lease motor vehicles.Copyright ©2015 TrueCar, Inc. All rights reserved.

"Pedometer" records the number of steps you have walked and displays them again along with the number of calories that you have burned, distance, walking time and speed per hour.It is easy to use. Once you push the Start button, all you have to do is hold your smartphone as you always do and walk.Of course, it will continue to automatically record your steps even if you put it in your pocket or bag.You can view a graph with the number of steps you have walked and all other information anytime.Let's enjoy walking with this app!How to use- Touch on the number of steps, burned calories, distance, walking time, or speed to display the graph with that information.- Touch the graph to highlight information data for a specific time or date.- Swipe to the left to see the data recorded until the previous day.- If you want to change the look of the app, change the theme.- In order to display the correct number of burned calories, please enter your age, gender, weight and step length accurately.- In order to display the correct distance and speed, please enter your step length accurately.Important- Some devices will not record the number of steps when they are locked. This depends exclusively on the specifications of each device and it is not a bug of the app.- If you find errors in the number of steps recorded, please adjust the sensitivity.

DU Recorder adalah aplikasi perekam layar yang stabil, gratis, dan kualitas tinggi yang membantu Anda merekam video layar ponsel dengan jernih dan tanpa kendala. Dengan beragam fitur dan tanpa memerlukan rooting, DU Recorder menyediakan cara mudah untuk merekam video game, video panggilan, pertunjukan langsung, dan lainnya—mempermudah segalanya!Fitur Utama: ★Perekaman LayarDU Recorder menyediakan perekaman layar yang stabil dan lancar. Anda dapat merekam video game populer; Anda dapat merekam panggilan video dengan keluarga dan teman; Anda juga dapat merekam program populer di Twitch dan Periscope! DU Recorder didesain dengan fitur gratis berikut: ------ Tersedia berbagai resolusi, kecepatan bingkai, dan kecepatan bit; mendukung video HD ------ Menjeda/melanjutkan rekaman ------ Mengaktifkan kamera depan------ Merekam suara eksternal------ Mengontrol rekaman melalui jendela floating atau bilah notifikasi; sembunyikan jendela floating untuk video tanpa bingkai------ Menampilkan operasi klik dalam rekaman ★ Pengeditan Screenshot dan Gambar Dengan DU Recorder, Anda dapat mengambil screenshot hanya dengan 1 klik. Cukup dengan satu tangan. Tidak perlu dua kali menekan dan menahan. Cepat dan mudah! Anda juga dapat membagikan screenshot atau menggunakan alat pengeditan gambar dalam aplikasi untuk menempelkan dan memotong gambar lokal. ------ Gunakan bilah notifikasi atau jendela floating untuk mengambil screenshot 1 klik.------ Tempelkan Gambar—Dengan cerdas menggabungkan beberapa gambar menjadi satu. ------ Buramkan Gambar—Pikselasikan gambar untuk menutupi area yang tidak ingin ditampilkan.------ Potong Gambar—Simpan hanya bagian gambar yang Anda inginkan.★ Memeriksa dan Berbagi Video------ Memeriksa rekaman video dengan mudah melalui jendela floating dan bilah notifikasi.------ Berbagi video situs sosial. Bagikan rekaman Anda dengan teman!------ Memodifikasi judul video di halaman video lokal agar lebih mudah dikelola.Jika Anda memiliki komentar atau saran tentang DU Recorder, hubungi kami di gameshowdu2015@gmail.com. Kami sangat menghargai saran & kritik Anda!

BÍBLIA OFF-LINE + DICIONÁRIO + COMENTÁRIOS BÍBLICOS + ESBOÇOS DE MENSAGENS + PERGUNTAS E RESPOSTASO Pregai! é uma excelente ferramenta de apoio ao estudo da Bíblia Sagrada, que é a Palavra de Deus.A consulta automática das palavras-chave, um recurso exclusivo do Pregai!, permite que você consulte o significado das principais palavras que compõem um determinado versículo, em um dicionário com mais de 5200 termos.Com mais de 240 passagens bíblicas comentadas, cerca de 135 mensagens (esboços de pregações) e ainda uma seção de perguntas respondidas, o Pregai! é rico em conteúdo, que é atualizado periodicamente.Quer procurar por um versículo e não lembra onde está? A pesquisa bíblica do Pregai! te ajuda a encontrar! Basta escrever duas ou mais palavras do versículo e você terá uma relação completa de todos os versículos da Bíblia que contém tais palavras!Adicionar marcadores e escrever anotações sobre versículos nunca foi tão fácil e prático! Com os marcadores agrupados por cor, você sempre terá acesso rápido aos versículos destacados.Quer compartilhar um versículo, mensagem, comentário, dúvida, ou ainda um termo do dicionário? Super fácil: basta acionar a opção Comp. (de compartilhar) que fica na parte inferior da tela. Você poderá compartilhar via SMS, MMS, E-mail ou ainda enviar para outros programas, como o Twitter e Google Plus (Facebook em breve!)Nas mensagens, comentários, dúvidas e no dicionário, todas as referências a textos bíblicos são automaticamente convertidos em links, assim você pode ler versículo sem ter que fechar a tela atual. Muito prático!E o que é melhor: tudo isto é disponibilizado GRATUITAMENTE, sem propagandas, e TODO O CONTEÚDO FICA DISPONÍVEL OFF-LINE, isto é, FUNCIONA SEM CONEXÃO COM INTERNET!Caso você goste do aplicativo, ajude a divulgá-lo. Avalie o APP com 5 estrelas, se você julgar que ele merece isto.Você ainda poderá ser um colaborador do Pregai!, enviando mensagens, comentários bíblicos, dúvidas (com ou sem resposta) e termos do dicionário. Para isto, basta enviar um email para o desenvolvedor. Há um atalho na opção "Sobre", da tela principal do APP.Que Deus abençoe a todos com a paz do Senhor Jesus!BÍBLIA, A PALAVRA DE DEUS=========================Examinais as Escrituras, porque vós cuidais ter nelas a vida eterna, e são elas que de mim testificam; João 5:39A Bíblia é a palavra de Deus.Apesar de ter sido escrita por homens, este livro é totalmente inspirado pelo Espírito Santo de Deus.E somente o Espírito Santo pode revelar ao homem os mistérios escondidos neste livro sagrado.O objetivo deste aplicativo é ser uma ferramenta para os que têm o privilégio de pregar a Palavra de Deus.Que Deus abençoe a todos!MARANATA: O SENHOR JESUS VEM!Conheça nosso site: http://autaz.com/pregai

Melty Style100% des profils sont vérifiés manuellement et notre service client est disponible 24/24h.Alors n’attendez plus pour rejoindre notre communauté, vous serez entre de bonnes mains !Afin d'augmenter vos chances de faire des rencontres, abonnez-vous et :• Contactez en illimité les personnes qui vous intéressent• Découvrez les personnes à qui vous plaisez• Accédez à l’intégralité des informations renseignées sur les fiches profils• Naviguez sans publicité• Profitez d’un prix réduit sur nos ateliers et soirées thématiques organisés chaque semaine• Boostez votre profil et multipliez vos contacts par 3 (option Booster) (1)Vous pouvez acheter un pass renouvelable pour une durée de 1 mois, 3 mois ou 6 mois pour profiter de l'ensemble des services Meetic.Adopte Meetic et rencontre le mec ou la fille célibataire de tes rêves, plus de 6 millions de couples (gay, lesbienne, hétéro) se sont rencontrés sur Meetic.FAQ :• Je suis déjà inscrit sur le site web, puis-je utiliser l’application mobile ?Connectez-vous avec vos identifiants habituels et accédez à l’ensemble des services et fonctionnalités dont vous bénéficiez déjà sur le site !• Je ne possède pas encore d’abonnement, puis-je m’inscrire sur l’application ?L’inscription est gratuite et vous aurez accès à l’ensemble du service en choisissant un de nos abonnements directement depuis l’appli.Votre abonnement vous donnera accès à la totalité des services sur le web et sera renouvelé automatiquement pour la même durée et au même prix que l’offre initialement choisie. Votre accès au service ne sera ainsi jamais interrompu sans que vous le décidiez.• Comment puis-je modifier / annuler mon abonnement ?Il vous suffit de vous rendre sur meetic.fr.-Passez votre souris sur votre pseudo en haut à droite. -Cliquez sur « Mon compte et abonnement »-Cliquez sur « Gérer votre abonnement »Pour des raisons techniques, la résiliation de l’abonnement ne pourra être faite pendant les 24h après l’achat de l’abonnement et les 48h avant la date d’échéance de l’abonnement en cours, sauf si vous bénéficiez d'une offre d'essai.Meetic fait partie du groupe Match.com, n°1 mondial de la rencontre, qui possède également Tinder, OkCupid, Plenty Of Fish, Amoureux et Twoo.(1) Meetic ne peut garantir le volume d'activité dont votre profil fera l'objet*Enquête en ligne conduite par TNS pour Meetic du 29/10 au 06/1 2014, auprès d'un échantillon représentatif de 1500 célibataires âgés entre 18 et 65 ans en France.**Estimation du nombre de couples formés sur les sites du groupe Meetic en Europe. "Lady Pill Reminder" is the perfect app to keep track of taking your birth control pills. It is very simple to set up and use. You just have to indicate the type of birth control pill you take (number of pills in the packet) and the time you usually take your pill, and "Lady Pill Reminder" will notify you when you'll have to take your pill. In addition, you can check the status of the current pill packet.Lady Pill Reminder is the application you need to keep track of taking your birth control pills: easy, effective, and free!.Features:- Daily reminder, you won't forget to take the pill anymore.- Reminder is automatically disabled for days you don't have to take the pill.- Reminder is done through notifications (no more annoying alarms).- You can choose the notification sound.- You can enable/disable notification vibration.- Notification led flashes with notifications (only if your device has a notification led).- This app also reminds you that you have to buy pills when you have to start a new packet.- Number of pills per packet customizable (so is compatible with all birth control pill types)- The application displays the status of your pill packet.- You can use the widgets "Lady Pill Widgets": It's a pack of 2 widgets for your home screen: one shows your pill calendar (so you can see future months predictions), and the other shows your current cycle day, and also shows you if you have to take pill today or not ("Lady Pill Widgets" is sold separately).

胸きゅん学園ライフアプリ「ボーイフレンド（仮）」が贈る新作学園青春リズムゲーム、「ボーイフレンド(仮)きらめき☆ノート」！今度の行事は学校内にとどまらず、ステージパフォーマンスで街中を盛り上げる『ステラマリスフェス』。あなたは藤城学園のカレ達のサポーターとして、数々の困難を乗り越え、その先に待っているものは――40人以上の個性豊かなカレ達をサポートし、ドキドキとワクワクの青春ストーリーを解放していきましょう！◆◇◆アプリ概要◆◇◆■3Dのカレ達とコミュニケーション！ボーイフレンド(仮)のカレ達が、キュートな3Dになって登場します！3Dのカレ達とコミュニケーションを楽しんだり、ルームで過ごしたり、リズムゲームを一緒にプレイしたりなど、楽しい機能が盛りだくさん！また、華やかで魅力的な衣装には限定ボイスがついているので、様々な衣装を着たカレたちとのコミュニケーションを楽しんでくださいね。今後、キャラクターは続々追加予定です。■カレ達とのストーリーが楽しめるアドベンチャーパート！藤城学園のカレ達との青春のメインエピソードはもちろんのこと、キーを集めて開かれていくカレとの親密なエピソードも！たくさんのストーリーを楽しみましょう！■豪華声優のキャラクターソングでリズムゲーム！多くの声優陣が参加するキャラクターソングでリズムゲームが楽しめます！キュートな3Dのカレ達のダンスを見たり、お揃いの衣装にしたり…楽しみ方はあなた次第。仲良しのカレ達と一緒にリズムゲームをすると、いいことがあるかもしれません。今後、楽曲は続々追加予定です。◆◇◆声の出演◆◇◆KENN、蒼井翔太、阿部敦、石田彰、入野自由、置鮎龍太郎、小野大輔、小野友樹、柿原徹也、梶裕貴、川原慶久、岸尾だいすけ、黒田崇矢、櫻井孝宏、島﨑信長、杉山紀彰、杉田智和、鈴村健一、諏訪部順一、関智一、高梨謙吾、髙橋孝治、竹内栄治、武内健、武内駿輔、立花慎之介、谷山紀章、寺島拓篤、鳥海浩輔、浪川大輔、西田雅一、羽多野渉、花江夏樹、林勇、日野聡、平川大輔、福山潤、保志総一朗、前野智昭、増田俊樹、水島大宙、宮野真守、村田太志、森川智之、森久保祥太郎、山下大輝、山寺宏一、遊佐浩二、横山遵、代永翼（五十音順・敬称略）*************************************【推奨環境】AndroidOS Aplikasi perdagangan opsi biner seluler, anyoption, memungkinkan Anda untuk berdagang dengan mudah kapan saja, di mana saja. Anda dapat membuka perdagangan baru dan dengan mudah memantau posisi terbuka (open position) Anda di mana pun Anda berada. Fitur:• Mudah digunakan dan intuitif• Perdagangan real-time kapan saja, di mana saja.• Perdagangan sosial dengan data perdagangan real-time • Ratusan aset acuan tersedia untuk diperdagangkan• Ikuti tren pasar dan kunci posisi Anda (hedging)• Beli dan Jual opsi biner untuk forex, indeks, saham, dan komoditas• Sinkronisasi yang mulus dengan akun web anyoption Anda• Tersedia dalam bermacam-macam bahasa • Dukungan langsung oleh tim profesional kami• Penyetoran dan penarikan dengan bermacam-macam metode penyetoran• Tanpa komisi ataupun biaya tersembunyi, tanpa sebaran, tanpa iklan.Aplikasi perdagangan opsi biner kami adalah hasil dari penawaran perdagangan opsi biner pada perangkat seluler selama lebih dari 5 tahun. Pilih dari ratusan aset acuan dari bermacam-macam bursa saham di seluruh dunia – Anda dapat memperdagangkan opsi biner untuk forex, indeks, saham, dan komoditas.Unduh aplikasi ini sekarang juga untuk mengetahui mengapa anyoption adalah platform perdagangan opsi biner yang terdepan di dunia. PERNYATAAN SANGKALAN: Perdagangan opsi biner tidak terlepas dari risiko kehilangan investasi Anda dan mungkin tidak cocok untuk Anda. Harap pastikan bahwa Anda memahami risiko yang ada sepenuhnya.

description: ◆◇◆◇こんな方にオススメ◆◇◆◇・お着替えゲームが好き！・ロールプレイングゲームが好き！・コーディネートが好き！・ファッションが好き！・美しいグラフィックが好き！・洋服を集めることが好き！・豪華声優陣によるボイス付きのゲームが好き！・ゴーでバトルをしてみたい！・気軽にゲームを楽しめたい！・濃厚ストーリーを満喫したい！特徴：√斬新なプレイモード！コーディネーターとのバトルに挑む！ 斬新なゲームプレイスタイル。「エレガント」「ゴージャス」「セクシー」「かわいい」などのスタイル採点基準を導入し、あなたのコーディネートを細かく評価してくれるよ！ファッションセンスがどんどん磨かれていこう！ コーディネーターたちとの激しいバトルを楽しめる！　バトル中に使える多彩な「スキル」でより楽しく！√2000種類以上のアイテムで、可愛いも凛々しいもあなたの思いのまま！七つの国、七つのファッションスタイル、数多くセットコーデを集めよう！ すべての衣装は高精度に描かれ、たくさんの衣装の中から、好きな服を選んでコーデしよう！カジュアル系、和風、エレガント系、ガーリー系、ボーイッシュ系、サイバーパンクなど、ニキシリーズ数年の経験から生まれた、今までにないビジュアル体験！√カラー・柄・組み合わせ、材料を集め、オーダーメイドでオリジナルな洋服を作っちゃおう!!三種類の衣装を組み合わせてリメイクできちゃう！　オーダーメイドの面白さがアップグレード！衣装のカラーや柄をカスタマイズし、進化させたお洋服で素敵なコーディネートに変身！ デザイナーと出会い、ストーリーを楽しみながら、デザイナーのソウルデザインアイテムを獲得～育成・衣装作り・集めの醍醐味を満喫！√スナップショットでお気に入りの瞬間を記録しよう【光のギャラリー】で自由にコーディネートしたら、スナップショットでお気に入りの瞬間を記録して、友達にシェアできちゃう！自慢のコーディネートをみんなにどんどん見てもらおう！ √ミラクルニキは、七つの異なるコーディネートスタイルを持つ国を舞台に、物語は進んでいく―――。壮大な世界観で繰り広げられる物語は、まるで小説のよう！ 美しいイラストとともに、ニキの世界をたっぷりとご堪能あれ！スマートでセレブな美しさを尊ぶパテール連邦、キュートでメルヘンなファッションを持つリリス王国、伝統的な東洋スタイルをベースにしながらも、常に新しい要素を取り入れる雲上帝国など。 総勢数十名の個性的な仲間たちと一緒に、小説のような濃厚なストーリーを体験しよう！ √素敵なボイス：豪華声優陣起用！不思議な旅で出会う個性豊かな仲間たち 声優キャスト（リスト一覧）：花澤香菜、大谷育江、小野大輔、梅原裕一郎、佐倉綾音、斎藤千和、能登麻美子、西山宏太朗、東山奈央、竹本英史、高野麻里佳、村瀬歩、安済知佳、折笠富美子、橋本ちなみ操作方法： 1.APPを起動し、ゲームをスタートする。 2.チュートリアルに従い、テーマに合うコーディネートをする。 3.アイテムのスタイル（「エレガント」「ゴージャス」「セクシー」「かわいい」など）に注目しながら、コーディネートする。 4.採点が対戦コーディネーターより高ければ、ミッションクリアとなります。 連絡先： 1. True Contact : Block unwanted & spam callsFeatures:• Caller ID - the true smart caller id with name with address and picture.• SPAM Blocker - block spam, fraudulent and just unwanted calls with single click!• Contacts Manager - Save resolved contacts to your phone book• Social profile- true contacts data updated and cross checked with social networks like Facebook, Linkedin, Twitter, Google plus• Call log - retrieve true caller id information for unknown numbers from call history list in single view.• Update Phone-book - Keep your phone-book up-to-date with your friends latest address info, pictures, address and more.• Caller location - worldwide caller true & smart Geo-location service• Notifications for detected caller id or blocked calls. Caller ID profile may contain :★ personal name or business name★ address★ personal photo or business logo★ status, titleTrue Contact Smart & True Caller ID provide coverage for the following countries :• North America: USA, Canada• Europe: Germany, Switzerland, Austria, France, Norway, Italy, Hungary, Poland & many more .• Asia: India, Thailand, Taiwan, Malaysia and Indonesia• Africa : Ghana, Egypt, South Africa, Botswana & many more.• South America: Brasil, Argentina, Mexico True Contact uses contact and caller id information from several sources incl. social networks.Spam block - a new True & Smart Spam Blocker feature from True Contact.Automatically blocks unwanted, fraudulent & spam calls. True Contact Caller ID pays huge attention to data security and privacy.True Contact Caller ID does not sell, share data with any third party application and/or organization.True Contact can be installed natively along with other connectivity applications such as native dialer application, skype, whatsapp, telegram or voxer.True Contact is a smart caller id and spam block for your mobile device. A popup with true caller id details will appear on top of the screen when there is incoming call.During incoming call you will see the true caller id details.Now you have a choice to answer it if this is someone you trust, or drop the call in case of spammers, advertisers, telemarketing and fraud calls.Please note, caller id feature requires network connection. In case of network connection unavailable during the call , true contact will fetch caller id details right after finish of a call.We also added new phone-book history caller id feature. This allows you to obtain true caller id information for calls stored in your contact book.True Contact pay's a huge attention for performance and responsibility and this means that fetching of caller id information will take no more than just few seconds.In most cases caller id information fetched within 1-2 seconds.This allows you to answer a call only when you know who is the person calling you!True Contact - smart caller id is absolutely free caller id application. If you enjoy it - feel free to rate it accordingly.In the future releases we plan to add comprehensive spam protection. Auto block for spam numbers based on caller id's of telemarketers and spammers. Please note : ★ During incoming call , Caller ID information will appear on the screen. ★ Network connection is required to allow connection to True Contact servers. ★ This free version may collect your personal phone-book information to improve caller details lookup quality. ★ If you care about extended privacy and want to enjoy fully functional version with contact enrichment feature - please consider to purchase a True Contact Pro version.True Contact systematically improves contact and caller id data quality!

L’app Trenitalia ti accompagnerà dall'acquisto del biglietto fino al viaggio in treno. Ecco cosa puoi fare.Orario e Acquisto In questa sezione puoi consultare gli orari e comprare il biglietto per i tuoi viaggi. Puoi selezionare le stazioni di partenza e arrivo dall'apposito elenco che è scrollabile. In questo elenco, con un tap sulla stellina puoi scegliere le tue stazioni preferite o cancellare la preferenza. Puoi utilizzare anche una delle tue ultime ricerche effettuate, salvate in ordine cronologico. Una volta selezionati tutti i parametri della tua ricerca, ti sarà mostrato l'elenco delle soluzioni disponibili. Puoi ordinare la lista delle soluzioni di viaggio per orario di partenza, di arrivo e durata.Accanto ad ogni soluzione acquistabile viene mostrato in un riquadro rosso il miglior prezzo disponibile e i relativi punti cartafreccia. Clicca sulla freccia nel riquadro per proseguire nell’acquisto.I Miei ViaggiIn questa sezione puoi vedere i viaggi ancora da effettuare acquistati tramite l’utenza Trenitalia dal sito o tramite app. Per ognuno dei viaggi, hai a disposizione le seguenti opzioni: - Cambiare la prenotazione - Chiedere il rimborso - Inserire il viaggio in calendario- Ricevere una notifica con il PNR ed i posti all'arrivo in stazione (disponibile da iOS 5 e successive) o 1h dal viaggioStato TreniIn questa sezione puoi controllare l'andamento in tempo reale di un treno nella giornata odierna o dei treni in partenza da una stazione.Puoi inoltre impostare un servizio di notifica sulla circolazione di uno o più treni.CartaFRECCIAIn questa sezione puoi controllare i dati relativi alla tua cartaFRECCIA associata all’utenza Trenitalia con il relativo estratto conto.

Nerede olursanız olun, evde, kafede, yazlıkta ya da sinemada — hızlı ve kullanışlı Yandex.Arama servisi her zaman sorularınızı yanıtlar.Sorgularınızı klavyede yazarak ya da sesli yapabilirsiniz. Mobil aramada popüler olan konular için hazır yanıtlar mevcuttur — kafelerin veya ATM’lerin haritada konumu, ilgi alanınızda olan görseller gibi. Örneğin, müzik klibi veya dizi için arama yaparken, uygulama size video önerir, yabancı bir kelimeyi araştırırken ise, çevirisini gösterir. Ayrıca, güncel haberleri ve şehrinizdeki hava durumunu da gösterir.Aradığınız şeyi daha hızlı bulmanızı sağlamak için, bazı soruların yanıtları doğrudan ipuçlarında yer alır; örneğin, şehir kodu, nehrin uzunluğu ya da döviz kurunu, sorgunuzu tam yazmadan bile öğrenmeniz mümkün.Uygulama ile birlikte masaüstü için, arama çubuğu, şehrinizdeki hava durumu, trafik ve döviz kurunu gösteren widgeti kurabilirsiniz (4х4).Yandex.Arama, sadece internette değil, telefonunuzda da arama yapabilir. Uygulama rehber, SMS ve yüklenen uygulamalar arasında arama yapabilmektedir.

☆ ☆ ☆ ENGLISH GRAMMAR ULTIMATE (Grammar now in my pocket) ☆ ☆ ☆ Grammar is the study of words and the ways words work together. An invisible force that guides us as we put words together into sentences. Any person who communicates using a particular language is consciously or unconsciously aware of the grammar of that language. To speak in a clearer and more effective manner we study grammar. A person who has unconscious knowledge of grammar may be sufficient for simple language use, but the ones who wish to communicate in an artful manner and well, will seek greater depth of understanding and proficiency that the study of grammar provides. This android application will help to improve your English grammar. Need a lift? Use Lyft to get an affordable ride in minutes. Instead of hailing a cab or waiting for the bus, just request a car with the tap of a button, and get picked up by a nearby friendly driver who’ll take you to your destination right away. Enjoy a welcoming, affordable, and memorable ride today.Our app is cheaper than a taxi, faster than the bus, and easy to use. • Getting Started: After downloading Lyft and signing up, simply open the app and request a ride. • Paying: Never worry about having cash for a cab or the bus again — with Lyft, you pay through your phone. It’s easy, fast, and secure. • Split the Cost: Easily split the cost of a ride with friends through the app. No more IOU’s. About Our Drivers • All Lyft drivers pass comprehensive background and DMV checks before being approved for the service. • Drivers are rated by passengers and only the highest-rated drivers are allowed on the road. • Lyft provides a first-of-its-kind $1M liability insurance for total peace of mind.Join the millions who’ve chosen Lyft instead of a cab for commuting, going out at night, and getting to events. Next time you need a ride, skip the bus, taxi, or car service and choose Lyft.—What people are saying:"Ride-sharing programs like Lyft are providing commuters with less expensive and more social ways to get around. Users log into the app, specify where they’re heading, and a background-checked driver picks them up for less than a typical cab ride." - TODAY Show on how Lyft works"In a city where taxis can be scarce and Uber’s black town cars are rampant but expensive, Lyft has quickly gained visibility due to low prices and quirky branding." - Ad Age on what differentiates Lyft"Lyft's focus on the everyman has recently extended to the wildly successful Lyft Line carpool service aimed at commuters, which offers discounts of 30% to 60% for sharing a Lyft ride with others." - Fast Company on Lyft Line“...Special emphasis was put on making rides reflect the values of the company. The founders didn’t want the experience to be like a taxi or an Uber ride, where a passenger sat in the back and didn’t interact with the driver.” - Techcrunch on Lyft’s community values“Lyft is a foreign country for an Uber refugee, but it doesn't take long to feel at home there.” - Mashable, on switching to Lyft from Uber “ A few weeks ago, one Lyft driver served me homemade lemon bread. The experience feels less mercenary than taking an Uber ride, as if you’re engaging a friend rather than a chauffeur, which is exactly the atmosphere you’d want in a daily car pool.” - New York Times, on the difference between Lyft and Uber —For Lyft drivers using the app, continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.

appName: バッテリー長持ち・節電　Yahoo!スマホ最適化ツール
description: Yahoo!最適化ツールは、ワンタッチでスマホのメモリを解放し、バッテリーを長持ちさせる無料アプリです。おまかせ節電はもちろん、カスタマイズ節電もシンプルで簡単！指１本の操作で、重くなったスマホをサクサク最適化しましょう。■掲載メディア多数・スマホに買い替えた両親に入れてあげたい（GIZMODE）・圧倒的な分かりやすさ！ バッテリー＆メモリ管理アプリ（ファミ通App）　など、テレビ・雑誌・ニュースサイトなど15媒体以上に掲載されました■アプリ概要 簡単操作でバッテリー節約と、スマホの動作もサクサクなんて一石二鳥。一目でスマホのバッテリー残量や容量の空き状況状態がわかり、しかも、バッテリー残量が20％を切ると自動でお知らせします。■こんな方におすすめ・最近スマホの充電の減りが早くて困っている！・ややこしい設定なしで楽して簡単に節電したい・バッテリー残量があとどのくらいもつか知りたい。・容量が無く手間暇かけて少しでも長くスマホを使う努力をしている。・毎日充電している。・外出するときは充電器がないと不安になる 。・スマホが熱くなる。・少しでも電池を伸ばすため画面を暗めにして使っている。・スマホの節電をどうやっていいのかが分からない！・いろいろアプリを入れたら動作がモッサリしてきた！・簡単にアプリの整理がしたい。・動画・音楽・漫画・カメラアプリをよく使う。・LINE・Facebook・カカオトーク・Twitterなどをよく使う。・暇つぶしにスマホでゲームをしたり、2ちゃんねるまとめを見たりする。・仕事でスマホを使うことが多く、外出も多い。・スマホの容量をスッキリとCleanにしたい。・Battery DocterやBattery Mix、Battery Pro等を使っている人。・ブーストして今までよりスマホを２倍長く使いたい人。・いちいちアプリを起動せずに簡単に端末をサクサクにしたい人。・お気に入りのゲームもゲーム最適化で爆速に！ ■機能詳細・おまかせ節電　ONにしている間、アプリが自動的に節電を行います。　また、通知バーのアイコンに電池の残量（電池残量）をパーセントで表示します。　本体設定をなるべく変更せず、　画面ロック中に使っていないアプリを終了したり、　バッテリー残量が少ないときにWi-FiをOFFにしたり、　使い勝手を保ったままバッテリーの消費を抑えます。　※設定状況によっては、他のアプリが期待の動作をしなくなる場合がありますのでご注意ください。・もっと節電　スマホの各種機能をOFFにでき、節電します。　どの機能をOFFにすれば何分バッテリーが長持ちするか、わかりやすく表示します。・動作サクサク（メモリ解放）　不要なタスクを切断し、メモリ節約。動作がサクサクに。・容量スッキリ（アプリ削除）　サイズの大きいアプリを削除しスマホをスッキリ。　どのアプリが知らない間に起動したかも一目で分かります。・バッテリー節約の通知機能　バッテリー残量が20％を切った場合には通知します。　バッテリー充電を開始時に節電効果を通知します。・ワンタップ最適化　ホーム画面に設置されたショートカットアイコンをタップすることで、その場ですぐに最適化が行われます。　アプリを立ち上げる事なく、端末の動作を簡単にサクサクにすることができます。・ウィジェット　ホーム画面にウィジェットを設置することで残り時間や節電具合を確認できます。・キャッシュ削除（不要なファイルの削除）　システムのキャッシュやそれぞれのアプリのキャッシュをボタン一発で削除できます。　かんたんにキャッシュ削除したい人におすすめです。本アプリケーションは、Yahoo! JAPAN利用規約（ソフトウエアガイドラインを含みます）をご確認のうえ、ご利用ください。■Yahoo! JAPAN利用規約http://docs.yahoo.co.jp/docs/info/terms/■プライバシーポリシーhttp://docs.yahoo.co.jp/docs/info/terms/chapter1.html#cf2nd■ソフトウエアガイドラインhttp://docs.yahoo.co.jp/docs/info/terms/chapter1.html#cf5th

ออล ไทย แท็กซี่1. สามารถเรียกใช้บริการผ่าน Application ALL THAI TAXI2. มีค่าเรียกใช้บริการครั้งละ 20 บาท (จ่ายทุกครั้งที่ทำรายการเรียกใช้บริการ) + ค่าโดยสารตามมิเตอร์ปกติ3. กรณีโบกเรียก ไม่มีค่าบริการ 20 บาท ชำระเฉพาะค่าโดยสารตามมิเตอร์ปกติ4. ค่าผ่านทางด่วน หรือทางพิเศษ ผู้โดยสารจะเป็นผู้จ่าย5. ชำระค่าบริการเป็นเงินสด และตัดบัตรเครดิต หรือบัตรเดบิตที่ลงทะเบียนไว้6. จำกัดที่นั่งผู้โดยสารสูงสุดไม่เกิน 4 ท่าน7. คาดเข็มขัดนิรภัยทุกครั้งเมื่อโดยสารรถแท็กซี่8. สัมภาระที่นำติดตัว จำกัดน้ำหนักไม่เกิน 20 กก.ต่อชิ้น และมีขนาดหรือจำนวนไม่มากเกินกว่าที่จะบรรจุในรถได้9. ห้ามสูบหรี่ และดื่มสุรา ในขณะโดยสาร10. ไม่พกพาอาวุธ สิ่งของหรือวัตถุ ที่เสี่ยงต่อการเป็นอันตรายขึ้นรถ11. กรุณาช่วยกันรักษารถที่ท่านใช้บริการ12. งดการขีดเขียน หรือกระทำใดๆที่ก่อให้รถเกิดความเสียหายกับอุปกรณ์ต่างๆภายในตัวรถ13. งดทำให้รถสกปรก งดการวางเท้าบนเบาะที่นั่ง14. งดนำอาหารที่มีกลิ่นแรงหรือสิ่งที่อาจก่อให้เกิดกลิ่นที่ไม่พึงประสงค์ขึ้นรถ15. งดนำสัตว์เลี้ยงทุกชนิดขึ้นรถ16. การเรียกใช้บริการผ่าน Call Center 1624 จะแจ้งให้ทราบเมื่อระบบพร้อมใช้งาน17. การยกเลิกบริการ- ยกเลิกภายใน 5 นาทีหลังจากเรียกใช้ ไม่คิดค่าบริการ- ยกเลิกบริการช้ากว่า 5 นาทีหลังจากเรียกใช้ คิดค่าบริการครั้งละ 100 บาท - หากผู้โดยสารไม่อยู่ที่จุดนัดเกินกว่า 5 นาทีเมื่อรถมาถึง ถือว่ายกเลิกบริการ คิดค่าบริการ 100 บาท18. กรณีชำระค่าโดยสารเป็นเงินสด กรุณาเตรียมค่าโดยสารให้พอดี หรือใกล้เคียงกับจำนวนค่าโดยสารที่ต้องชำระ

Save on the things you already buy at Target with Cartwheel! Select from hundreds of discounts ranging from 5% to 50% off, and add them to your personalized Cartwheel barcode, all from the convenience of your smartphone. Then save on your next Target run by scanning your barcode at checkout in store. Use the discounts as many times as you like before they expire. You can even stack Cartwheel on top of your Target REDcard discount and other coupons! Don't have time to browse the app for deals before you shop? No problem! Just use the barcode scan feature found in the app menu to scan the barcode of any item in store and see if there is a Cartwheel offer for that item. If no offers are available, we'll show you similar deals. Add the barcode widget to your device for dependable access while in a Target store - never worry about connectivity problems again!Unlock more spots on your Cartwheel list by earning badges. Find out more by visiting the Badges section in the app.Curious which items are on Cartwheel AND the Target Weekly Ad at the same time? Check out the Weekly Ad Collection on the Collections screen.Get started today by signing in with Target, Google+ or Facebook and instantly start seeing your savings add up!

İBB CepTrafik ile anlık trafik bilgisine, her zaman ve her yerden ulaşın!İstanbul Büyükşehir Belediyesi’nin bir hizmeti olan İBB CepTrafik uygulaması ile, anlık trafik durum bilgisine, dilediğiniz an cep telefonunuz ile ulaşabilirsiniz. İBB Ceptrafik, İstanbul Büyükşehir Belediyesi'nin geliştirdiği anlık trafik durumu bilgisini trafik kameraları ve yoğunluk haritası ile almanızı sağlayan bir uygulamadır. Bu uygulama ile İstanbul Büyükşehir Belediyesi'ne ait trafik sensörlerinden alınan hız bilgilerine, trafik kamera görüntülerine ve Trafik Kontrol Merkezi tarafından yayınlanan trafiğe ilişkin duyurulara ulaşabilirsiniz.Destek için tkm@ibb.gov.tr ile irtibata geçebilirsiniz.İBB CepTrafik uygulamasında kullanıcıların internet trafiğini minimize etme amacıyla trafik kamera görüntüleri, her bir dakikada bir değişen ve ard arda oynatılan 3 resim halinde sunulmaktadır.Trafik sensörlerini veya daha fazla kamerayı görebilmek için haritayı yakınlaştırmanız gerekmektedir.Uygulamayı kullanabilmek için internet bağlantısına sahip olmanız gerekmektedir.

2GIS Santiago - directorio gratuito de empresas y organizaciones con el mapa de la ciudad Santiago de Chile. También funciona sin conexión a Internet.2GIS Santiago contiene todas las empresas y organizaciones de la ciudad, sus contactos, direcciones, horarios de trabajo + un mapa tridimensional detallado + rutas en transporte público (Transantiago y Metro) o en auto.Directorio• Encuentre una empresa por su nombre, dirección o actividad• Averigüe qué farmacias, tiendas o correos Santiago de Chile están abiertas ahora mismo o de turno y qué formas de pagos aceptan• Vea en el mapa y en el directorio los cajeros automáticos (atm), radio taxi y las estaciones de servicio más cercanas• Descubra todos los restaurantes, cines, piscinas y espacios de recreación de su comuna o, por ejemplo, próximo a su hotel en Santiago.• Busque en el mapa de la ciudad los locales de comida rápida, de pizza para llevar, sushi o comida china más cercanos a su domicilio• Encuentre a Banco del Estado de Chile, Сarabineros, Bomberos, clínicas y centros de salud de forma rápida y precisa• Realice llamadas a las empresas directamente desde el directorio• Conozca la ubicación de los principales puntos de interés, museos, plazas, parques, empresas para organizar tures en bus, zoológicos, aeropuertos en Santiago. Mapa tridimensional detallado• Haga clic en cualquier edificio en el mapa para ver su dirección, el número de pisos y las empresas ubicadas en él• Encuentre el lugar que necesita en el mapa: edificio, calle, parque o comuna• Añada sus lugares preferidos a Favoritos• Mejore su percepción de la ciudad con detallados mapas en 3DRecorrido en auto y en transporte público• Averigüe cómo llegar a su destino en todos los tipos de transporte público (incluyendo Transantiago y todos sus transbordos)• Planifique su viaje y recorridos en Metro de Santiago• Conozca los paraderos de Transantiago en toda la ciudad• Utilice la búsqueda del trayecto en automóvil con las indicaciones de navegación y mapa ruteros• Encuentre estacionamientos cerca de su lugar de destinoFuncionamiento sin conexión a Internet• Descargue la base de datos de su ciudad y utilice la aplicación sin conexión a Internet• Todas las características del directorio y del mapa, incluida la búsqueda de rutas, seguirán disponibles en su dispositivo móvil: ideal para vacaciones y viajes de negociosDatos siempre actualizados• Las actualizaciones de la base de datos de las ciudades se publican mensualmente• Los datos del directorio son verificados continuamente por nuestro propio call-center y por nuestros especialistas en recolección de información• Los mapas de 2GIS han sido creados por cartógrafos profesionales a partir de imágenes satelitales actualizadas y continuas verificaciones en terreno• Nuestros mapas crecen y se complementan al ritmo de la ciudadGPS y brújula• Determine su ubicación exacta en el mapa de Santiago de Chile mediante GPS, Wi-Fi o redes celulares• Oriéntese con la ayuda de la brújula y averigüe en qué dirección están los lugares que le interesanActualmente están disponibles más de 250 ciudades en Chile, Rusia, Ucrania, Italia, Chipre, República Checa y Kazakstán.

Bạn không thích đánh nhau đẫm máu, bạn cần một tựa game mobile giải trí đúng nghĩa, Mộng Bá Vương 3D chính là lựa chọn hàng đầu cho bạn. Game ghi điểm với hình ảnh nhân vật kute dễ thương. Tham gia game, người chơi được lựa chọn một trong bốn class: Võ Tướng đẹp trai, Mưu Sĩ quyến rũ, Thích Khách lạnh lùng, Phương Sĩ kute. “Thể hiện cá tính – Thỏa mãn ước mơ” chính là những gì game thủ được thể hiện trong Mộng Bá Vương 3D. Thích sống ảo – Tha hồ selfie với thú cưỡi dễ thương, thích trở thành mỹ nhân – dự thi hoa khôi trong game thôi, thích ngầu và oai – chúng tôi đưa bạn làm vua tức thì. Đặc biệt đừng bỏ lỡ cơ hội khám phá tính năng Facebook ingame đầu tiên xuất hiện tại Việt Nam trong game. Ngoài ra, Mộng Bá Vương 3D vẫn có đất diễn cho người chơi tha hồ thể hiện bản lĩnh game thủ: PK đã tay, Vận tiêu, Quốc công, Quân đoàn chiến…Game hội tụ tất cả những tinh túy của cả thể loại MMORPG, ARPG, Casual đem đến cho người chơi một trải nghiệm thú vị nhất từ trước đến nay. Đến với Mộng Bá Vương bạn sẽ được tận hưởng:- Tạo hình nhân vật kute vô đối- Thoải mái selfie hàng nghìn kiểu với thú cưỡi ngộ nghĩnh- Tham gia bình chọn mỹ nữ, trở thành hoa khôi trong game- Khám phá Facebook ingame đầu tiên xuất hiện tại Việt Nam- Kết nghĩa anh em, chị em cây khế trong game- Minigame Zombie chất lừ- PK tự do đã tay, so tài cao thấp cùng hàng vạn cao thủ- MOBA Tam Quốc - Đấu trường 4 vs 4 đỉnh cao- Quốc chiến khốc liệt, thỏa mộng một lần làm vua - Quân đoàn chiến, thể hiện bản lĩnh anh tài- Quốc công oai phong, sở hữu thú cưỡi và vật phẩm cực chất- Thiết kỵ tung hoành, PK trên ngựa vô cùng đặc sắc- Liên thông server, thỏa sức giao lưu anh em bốn phương trong game- Giao dịch tự do trong game, làm giàu không khó- Tướng hồn hộ thể, hóa thân thành các anh hùng mỹ nhân chinh chiến: Quan Vũ, Trương Phi, Lữ Bố, Điêu Thuyền…- Phụ bản phong phú: tài nguyên, kinh nghiệm, đào khoáng…- Hệ thống vận tiêu kịch tính đến phút trót- Săn Boss thế giới cùng quần hùng- Hệ thống kinh mạch gia tăng thuộc tính cho nhân vậtCòn rất nhiều tính năng khác nữa, sẵn sàng khám phá ngay thôi! Applicazione ufficiale Sony per Lifelog. Grazie a Lifelog è possibile visualizzare le informazioni sul benessere e il fitness e approfondire i propri comportamenti. Le informazioni archiviate in Lifelog vengono raccolte in parte utilizzando una tecnologia a sensore contenuta all'interno del dispositivo Sony SmartWear e in parte grazie alle app e ai sensori dello smartphone Android™.Lifelog consente di controllare il grado di attività sostenuto, i luoghi visitati e come sono stati raggiunti durante il giorno.È possibile ora accedere a Lifelog anche dall'indirizzo Web - https://lifelog.sony.com. Sarà possibile visualizzare la propria storia con qualsiasi schermo, dallo smartphone al tablet o il televisore. Basta solo effettuare l'accesso tramite l'account Lifelog.Controlla il blog Sony Mobile http://blogs.sonymobile.com/tag/lifelog/ per essere sempre aggiornato.Registra la tua giornata ogni giorno, momento per momento.Lifelog utilizza software di analisi per raccogliere e riunire le statistiche e i dati di utilizzo per aiutarci a migliorare le applicazioni e i servizi. Tali dati non possono essere utilizzati per identificare l'utente. Ulteriori dettagli sull'argomento sono disponibili all'interno dell'Informativa sulla privacy di Sony Mobile.

This application is used to detect hazards on the road, such as speed cameras (mobile ambush, static speed cameras, red light cameras), speed bumps, bad roads and etc.This application uses database of hazards previously detected by other users. The latest version supports all the countries of the world!The workflow of the application differs from the hardware radar detector. Hardware radar detector - is a passive receiver that does not block the signal to which it is set, but simply notify the driver of the presence in the field of the radar radio interference. This application works differently, it uses a database of hazards previously detected by other users. For example, if the application is informed about mobile ambush, it means that at this point can probably be mobile ambush.Any user can add new hazard to shared database. Also user can influence on rating of hazard (when user get danger alert he can define whether danger exists or not in fact).The application plays the sound and shows hazard on the map and distance to this hazard.If you are connected to the internet you will be able to monitor the traffic jams.There is a feature update the database of the hazards.The application may run in the background (even when the screen is off), just enable option "Use speech when hazard detected".To start monitoring hazards just press "On" button in the left bottom screen corner.★★★ Features ★★★★ Night mode adjustment on screen ★ 3D tilt on map support (3D buildings)★ Map auto zoom and rotation map along the way★ Dashboard with current speed ★ 140 000 active hazards POIs around the world (check your country in FREE version of this APP at first)★ Daily database updates!★ Support voice alerts★ Support of working in background or with other Navigation APPs★ You can add their own POI to shared database

Photo Studio is a powerful all-in-one image processing application for photographers of any level. It contains basic and precise tools that provide multiple ways of retouching your images. Save images in JPEG and PNG.• Photo Studio PRO includes all unlocked packs, tools and features.Facebook: http://facebook.com/kvadgroupTwitter: http://twitter.com/kvadgroup

Reverse Movie FX is an app that lets you create a reverse video that looks like a magic trick! First record a video of someone (or you): walking, drinking orange juice, talking or any other idea that comes to your head! After that select a desired movie fragment and press start! The app will reverse your video: you will see people walking backwards, your friend spitting the juice out, people talking backwards!A few ideas of video reverse:- item kinetic attraction (you have to throw an item)- tear a sheet of paper- throwing a sheet of papier to the toilet- drinking a juice (and spitting it out as a result)- spilling a juice- money attracting- etc.Reversing options:- Add music- reversed + original- original + reversedGive it a try, you'll be amazed! You can share the result with your friends of course anywhere you want: facebook, e-mail etc.

The TapTaxi app allows you to get any taxi at any time. Talking to dispatcher is no longer necessary with the app. Only a few taps and your taxi will arrive in 5–10 minutes.TapTaxi is operational in the cities: Balashiha, Bryansk, Vladimir, Volgograd, Voronezh, Votkinsk, Gelendzhik, Dzerzhinsk, Domodedovo and Domodedovo Airport, Izhevsk, Kazan, Kaluga, Kiev, Kirov, Korolev and Mytishchi, Kostroma, Krasnodar, Kursk, Nevinnomyssk, Nizhny Novgorod, Novorossiysk, Orel, Perm, Podolsk, Pyatigorsk, Rostov-on-Don, Samara, Sochi, Stavropol, Ufa, Khimki and Sheremetyevo Airport, Cheboksary, Yaroslavl.TapTaxi offers following possibilities:* to сall the taxi without long conversations with dispatcher,* to see how the app determines your current location,* to mark the point on the map without writing down long address by hand,* to save popular addresses and quickly call them up,* to select any car — which is close by or which looks nicer,* to track the car on the map,* to add the disreputable drivers to the black list and never see them on the list again,* and mark nice drivers, so next time be able to use checked car,* to see on the screen detailed cost of the ride to exclude fraud.Taxi services which operate TapTaxi:Balashiha, Domodedovo and Domodedovo Airport, Kiev, Korolev and Mytishchi, Nevinnomyssk, Novorossiysk, Podolsk, Pyatigorsk, Rostov-on-Don, Sochi, Stavropol, Khimki and Sheremetyevo Airport — RedTaxi.Bryansk, Vladimir, Voronezh, Volgograd, Gelendzhik, Dzerzhinsk, Kaluga, Kirov, Krasnodar, Kursk, Nizhny Novgorod, Samara, Ufa, Cheboksary, Yaroslavl — Taxi Saturn.Votkinsk — Karetny Dvor.Izhevsk — Taxi 373.Kazan — Taxi Tatarstan.Kostroma — Kostroma Troyka.Orel — Taxi Voyage.Perm — Permskie Taxomotornye Linii.

Насколько хорошо Вы можете писать текст без ошибок? Хотите проверить? :)Данный тест поможет вам проверить свои знания по русскому языку. Вам предлагается ответить на 5 несложных вопросов по русскому языку, по окончанию которых игра оценит уровень ваших знаний и выдаст окончательную оценку. Не расстраивайтесь, если не сможете с первого раза получить удовлетворительную оценку, попробуйте ещё раз и всё обязательно получится!По завершению игры вы сможете просмотреть все совершённые ошибки, дабы не допустить их в дальнейшем. Искренне надеемся, что вам прийдётся по вкусу наша игра :)

Take WWE with you wherever you go – any time, day or night – with the official WWE app for your Android device. Now, in addition to the latest WWE videos, news and thousands of photos, you can use the WWE App as your exclusive portal to WWE Network – a 24/7 streaming service with both scheduled programming and a massive, on-demand library. Only on WWE Network, you’ll see all 12 WWE live pay-per-view events, including WrestleMania, groundbreaking original series, reality shows and documentaries. You’ll also be able to explore sports-entertainment’s most comprehensive video-on-demand library, featuring every WWE, WCW and ECW pay-per-view ever – uncut and uncensored – plus, classic matches and replays of Raw and SmackDown episodes from 2012 and 2013. When you watch WWE Network shows on another screen, and Monday Night Raw or Friday Night SmackDown on television, you’ll have exclusive access to WWE's second screen companion experience. Only with the WWE App, you’ll discover content designed for and synchronized to WWE's programs. Join your fellow WWE Universe members at the next WWE Live Event near you – for which you can find complete details within the WWE App. Explore our full schedule of events around the globe, find out which Superstars will be in action, set reminders and order your tickets for the experience of a lifetime. The WWE App provides instant access to your favorite WWE Superstars, Divas and Legends. View Superstar profiles for a quick look at extensive career milestones, biographies, video highlights and Twitter feeds. If you want to outfit yourself like your favorite Superstar, enjoy the brand-new WWE Shop experience right from your device, where official WWE Shop merchandise is available at the swipe of your fingertip. The WWE App is your key to unlocking a revolution!

แอปพลิเคชั่น Today for Tomorrow เคียงข้างคุณแม่เพื่อช่วยวางรากฐานชีวิตสู่อนาคตที่เป็นต่อของลูกรักในทุกช่วงวัย นับตั้งแต่ คุณแม่ตั้งครรภ์ ไปจนถึงลูกวัย 5 ปี เตรียมพร้อมศักยภาพลูกรักกับแบบทดสอบวัดแววความสามารถของลูกรักที่ออกแบบโดย รศ.ดร.อุษณีย์ อนุรุทธ์วงศ์ นายกสมาคมพัฒนาศักยภาพและอัจฉริยภาพมนุษย์ อัดแน่นเนื้อหาความรู้ด้านพัฒนาการ และคำแนะนำเจาะลึกทุกช่วงวัยโดย พญ. เสาวภา พรจินดารักษ์ กุมารแพทย์พัฒนาการและพฤติกรรม ตลอดจนความรู้ด้านโภชนาการช่วงแรกแห่งของชีวิต (Early Life Nutrition) ในแอปพลิเคชั่นนี้ นอกจากประกอบไปด้วย เคล็ดลับดีๆ (Tips) และ กิจกรรมแนะนำ (To-do) ส่งตรงถึงมือถือคุณแม่ทุกวัน เพื่อให้ลูกรักของคุณแม่เปี่ยมด้วย ศักยภาพที่เหนือกว่าทั้งความพร้อมทางด้านสมอง ร่างกาย และภูมิต้านทาน อีกทั้งยังมีเครื่องมืออันชาญฉลาดที่ช่วยคุณแม่บันทึก และติดตามพัฒนาการของลูกรักเพื่อการวางแผนการดูแลได้อย่างแม่นยำ เครื่องมือเพื่อคุณแม่ตั้งครรภ์ • บันทึกน้ำหนัก คำนวน BMI ดัชนีมวลกาย ประมวลผลพร้อมให้คำแนะนำ ช่วยให้คุณแม่ตั้งครรภ์หมดกังวลเรื่องภาวะน้ำหนักเกิน หรือน้ำหนักไม่เป็นไปตามเกณฑ์ พร้อมคำแนะนำจากผู้เชี่ยวชาญในการดูแลเรื่องโภชนาการที่เหมาะสม • โภชนาการระหว่างตั้งครรภ์ในแต่ละไตรมาส เทคนิคการปฏิบัติตัวตั้งแต่เริ่มรู้ว่าตั้งครรภ์ จนถึงการคลอด และคำแนะนำพิเศษเฉพาะ สำหรับคุณแม่ที่ผ่าคลอด รวมถึงเคล็ดลับและข้อมูลโภชนาการที่เหมาะสมระหว่างที่ยังอยู่ในระยะให้นมบุตร เครื่องมือเพื่อลูกรักแรกเกิดจนทั้งถึงช่วงก่อนวัยเรียน • บันทึกและเฝ้าติดตามการเจริญเติบโตของลูกรัก ประมวลผลลัพธ์ทั้งส่วนสูงและน้ำหนักเทียบกับเกณฑ์มาตราฐานของเด็กในแต่ละช่วงวัย พร้อมคำแนะนำด้านโภชนาการและการเลี้ยงดู • แบบวัดแววความสามารถ ปูทางสร้างอนาคตเตรียมพร้อมให้ลูกรักให้มีประสิทธิภาพยิ่งกว่า Have you ever wondered.... - As a rider/passenger: “I bet there’s someone nearby who could drive me where I want to go” - As a driver: “I bet there’s someone nearby willing to share my car and reduce my costs”Direct Ridesharing provides with the best carshare options when and where they need them.Direct Ridesharing is revolutionising passenger transport by connecting drivers and passengers immediately. You no longer need to plan your journey in advance! This app works in real time and GPS-guidance technology will direct the driver to their future passenger in no time at all. The app will find you available ridesharers, thanks to its automatic launch function.You no longer need to waste time or money organising inconvenient travel plans. Find a ride that suits you and meet new people in the process!Keywords : Carpooling, ridesharing, transport, hitchhiker

Bugün bu uygulamayı alın ve orada en iyi durumları okuyun.Eğer göndermeden hangi biri emin değilseniz - Bu uygulama ile ilham alın.Eğer bunu başarmak eğer doğru durumunu Başlarken gerçekten isabetli olabilir. Birçok farklı duygudurum türlerini açıklayan cümle çeşitli bulacaksınız, bu yüzden muhtemelen belirli bir anda size uygun bir şey bulacaksınız. Kolayca ne gibi PaylaşmakEğer bu liste ile sosyal ağlar üzerinde zaman harcamak yanlısı ol. Sosyal ağ hizmetlerinin ana tip, (genellikle kendini açıklama sayfaları) ile arkadaşları ile bağlanmak anlamına gelir (örneğin eski okul yılı veya sınıf gibi) kategorisinde yer bulundurmak olanlardır ve öneri sistemi güven bağlı. Popüler yöntemleri artık Amerikan tabanlı hizmetlerle, bu çok birleştirir. Bir sosyal ağ hizmeti (ayrıca sosyal paylaşım sitesi veya SNS) sosyal ağlar ya da benzer ilgi alanlarına, faaliyetleri, arka veya gerçek hayat bağlantıları paylaşan insanlar arasında sosyal ilişkiler kurmak için bir platformdur. Bir sosyal ağ servisi her kullanıcı (genellikle bir profil), onun toplumsal bağlantıları ve ek hizmetler çeşitli bir temsili oluşur. Sosyal ağ siteleri bireyler, genel bir profil oluşturmak bağlantıları paylaşmak kiminle kullanıcılar ve bakış bir listesini oluşturmak ve sistem içindeki bağlantıları geçmesine izin web tabanlı hizmetlerdir. Web tabanlı sosyal ağ servisleri, siyasi, ekonomik ve coğrafi sınırlar ötesine ilgi ve faaliyetleri paylaşan insanları bağlamak mümkün kılar. Bir hediye ekonomisinin andreciprocal fedakarlık işbirliği ile teşvik edildiği, e-posta ve anlık mesajlaşma yoluyla, çevrimiçi topluluklar oluşturulur. Bilgiler nonrival iyi ve hemen hemen hiçbir ücret ödemeden yetenekli olabilir gibi bilgiler, hediye ekonomisi için uygundur.Bir sosyal statü, belirli bir anı anlatır ve bir devlet yakalar. Sosyal paylaşım sitelerinde ortaya çıkan eğilimlerin ön planda "gerçek zamanlı web" ve kavramı "konum tabanlı." Gerçek zamanlı kullanıcılarının yüklenen ediliyor gibi daha sonra yayın içeriğini katkı sağlar - konsept radyo ve televizyon yayınlarını canlı benzerdir. Şirketler sosyal ağ kavramları, bulut bilgi işlem gibi iş teknolojileri ve çözümleri, birleştirmeye başladı. Bunun yerine sosyal ilgi dayalı bireyleri bağlayan, şirketlerin ortak iş ihtiyaçlarına veya deneyimlerine dayanarak bireyler bağlamak interaktif toplulukları geliştiriyoruz. Birçok uzman ağ araçları ve kendi web siteleri üzerinden erişilebilir uygulamaları sağlamak. Diğerleri şirketlerin giderek daha "toplumsallaşmış" sosyal ağ sitelerinin güç bazı koşum kariyer merkezi sitelerine hissediyorum geliştirmekteyiz. Bunlar daha fazla iş ile ilgili siteler çoğunlukla kendi isimlendirme var ama en yaygın adlandırma kuralları daha yakından sosyal ağ ilkelerine dayalı bireysel ağ ilişkileri bağlı eski olan "Mesleki Ağ Siteleri" ya da "Eğitim Medya Ağları" dir.Bizim app Beğendim? Yorumlarınızı bırakın, biz düşüncelerinizi duymaktan mutlu olurdu. Daha fazla sorunuz varsa, bize e-posta çekinmeyin. Biz indirmek için teşekkür ederiz.

Descárgate ya la app gratuita de MeinFernbus y reserva tus billetes de autobús baratos directamente con tu smartphone. MeinFernbus FlixBus ofrece, con sus más de 80.000 conexiones de autobús diarias a lo largo de toda Alemania y Europa, la red más extensa de autobuses de larga distancia. Ampliamos permanentemente nuestra red de autobuses de larga distancia en toda Europa para ofreceros cada vez más salidas, conexiones más rápidas y nuevos destinos a precios económicos. ¿Qué puedes hacer con nuestra app?✓ Buscar y reservar tu viaje✓ Mostar tu billete en el móvil al conductor ✓ Llegar hasta tu parada con la navegación GPS ✓ Visualizar la información de tu viaje✓ Disfrutar de ventajas exclusivas sólo disponibles en la app ✓ Obtener respuesta a todas tus preguntas sobre MeinFernbus FlixBus ✓ Viajar en bus a la luna: estamos en ello… ;)Nuestras prestaciones en detalle:★ ReservaEncuentra muy fácilmente la conexión de MeinFernbus FlixBus que desees a través del buscador de líneas, comprueba disponibilidad y precios actualizados y reserva directamente en nuestra app billetes baratos para tus viajes en bus. Guarda en tus datos de pago tu IBAN y BIC para reservar todavía más rápido y fácil. Sin importar si se trata de Berlín, Barcelona, Hamburgo, Múnich, Ámsterdam, Bruselas, París, Praga, Copenhague, Milán... – ¡Allí te llevaremos!★ Mis billetes Puedes acceder con tu móvil a todos los billetes que hayas comprado online. Al reservar tu billete vía app, tu billete queda directamente guardado en "Mis billetes". ¿Has reservado el billete desde la web? En tal caso sólo tienes que añadir tu reserva en "Mis billetes" a través del botón "Buscar reserva". Introduce tu número de reserva y correo electrónico - ¡Y Listo! El billete quedará guardado en tu app. Otra opción incluso más sencilla es añadir tus billetes mediante el código QR. Para ello, solo tienes que escanear el código QR de la confirmación de reserva y tendrás acceso al billete en la App (por esta razón necesitamos poder tener acceso a tu cámara).Gracias a la app de MeinFernbus el papeleo y los impresos pasan a la historia. El conductor escaneará cómodamente el billete en tu móvil en el momento de subir al autobús. ★ Paradas ¿No tienes ni idea de dónde para el autobús o no sabes cómo llegar a la parada? ¡Que no cunda el pánico! Accede en "Estaciones" a nuestro localizador e inmediatamente te aparecerá la parada más cercana. Naturalmente, puedes elegir cualquier otra de nuestra paradas y dejarte llevar al autobús siguiendo las instrucciones del navegador.★ Info/ Preguntas típicas ¿Cuánto equipaje está permitido? ¿Hay WiFi gratis en el autobús? ¿Cómo puedo modificar mi billete o cambiar el viajero? ¿Cómo canjeo mi cupón? No dejes que tus preguntas te hagan perder el control. Naturalmente encontrarás todo sobre los viajes de MeinFernbus FlixBus en el menú de información de nuestra app.Y por último, pero no menos importante, una simple explicación de los permisos que pide nuestra aplicación:✓ Calendario: nos permite añadir tu viaje a tu calendario.✓ Ubicación: este permiso nos permite mostrarte las estaciones de autobús más cercanas.✓ Cámara: nos permite añadir tus billetes a la app solo con escanear el código QR de tu confirmación de reserva. Estamos en continua mejora y amplicación de nuestra app por lo que seguro que te gustarán muchas de las nuevas prestaciones - por ello, lo mejor es que te descargues siempre la última versión. Te deseamos que disfrutres con nuestra app, está claro que MeinFernbus FlixBus cuenta con la mejor oferta de viajes.¿Tienes comentarios y sugerencias para ayudarnos a mejorar? ¡Envíalos ahora mismo! Estamos encantandos de recibir tu correo electrónico en android@flixbus.es Y ahora, basta de bla bla: ¡instala ya la app de MeinFernbus y compra tu billete! Más fácil imposible ;)

Поръчай сигурно, пътувай лесно, плати умно!Преоткрийте света на такси услугите, с новия сигурен, удобен и модерен начин за поръчка на такси. ТАКСИСТАРС създаде първата национална мрежа за такси поръчки в България. Таксистарс е първото приложение в България, което ви предлага плащане на такси пътувания с банкови карти директно от мобилното ви устройство. Таксистарс ви дава възможност сами да определяте качеството на такси услугите посредством потребителски рейтинг и възможност за персонализация на избора ви на любиминежелани шофьори. С точна и предварителна информация за вашия шофьор и кола, имате възможност да превърнете избора си на такси в приятно и сигурно преживяване!Кликнете си такси - за секунди, без разговори с оператор, само с няколко докосвания по екрана на телефона! Над 20 сигурни таксиметрови компании с над 1500 таксита в София, Пловдив, Бургас, Сливен, Враца, Монтана, Дупница, Хасково, Димитровград и Благоевград са на Ваше разположение. Услугата е достъпна в пилотен режим в градове Русе, Варна и Гоце Делчев.Вече може да създадете собствена група от любими шофьори. Добавете сами в собствен списък проверени от вас шофьори. Лесно и удобно вашите поръчки автоматично стигат с предимство до тях. Въведете промо код в Менюпромоции и заредете вашата сметка с електронен ваучер.Свалете Taxistars на телефона си и регистрирайте своя профил. Приложението съхранява в него вашите адреси и ви позволява да поръчвате такси с три клика. Паролата се въвежда само при регистрацията и е нужна, в случай че телефонът ви се повреди и желаете да възстановите вашата информация на друго устройство.Основни предимства:• Откривате такси без разговори - автоматично поръчвате такси през вашия смартфон, без разговори с оператор или махане с ръка на улицата. Лесно и бързо, както трябва да бъде!• Където и да сте - дори когато не знаете точния адрес, на който се намирате, Taxistars определя местоположението ви и вашето такси пристига.• Проверени превозвачи – Taxistars работи с лицензирани такси фирми с доказано име. Виждате на екрана информация за вашата кола и шофьор, според оценките на предишни пътници.
