Join 50 million other users worldwide and expand your social influence on BAND! Use our community forum to join groups, talk, share, and connect with hundreds of different communities that share similar interests.Discover topics that you’re passionate about and engage in conversations with like-minded individuals, or create a new Band and grow your own community by inviting members.BAND allows for traditional posting and chat, but moves beyond those basic features with a full suite of free tools. Members can utilize group polling, events, calendar, file sharing, and photo albums. For greater convenience, users also have the ability to access their Bands on desktop (www.band.us).FEATURES:DISCOVER NEW TOPICS AND PEOPLE - Band has communities for everyone. Whether you're a gamer looking for tips from a fellow Minecraft or COC enthusiast, a romance seeker in need of dating Advice or new in town and interested in hearing what foodies have to say about a local restaurant - Band is the place for you. Talk about the latest issue of your favorite fashion magazine or last night's sports game, share hilarious MEMES, find fitness partners and just have fun. Find what you like on our Discover page, join in, and join the conversation!YOUR HOME BASE – Create a home for your community on BAND. You can become an admin or a group leader of your own group, customizing the appearance to suit your Band’s identity, and sharing what matters most to your community. Make it your own. SHARE EVERYTHING – The home-base for your Band allows members to keep up with different members’ activity or share their own. Each member can post and organize photos, videos, gifs, PDFs, location, and files from Dropbox or Google Drive into your Band homepage. This is the place for sharing, venting and communicating. EASY CONSENSUS – No more endless discussions, going back and forth between different opinions. Use Band’s polling feature to make sure every member’s opinion counts. Create polls to let members vote on options for events, merchandise, personal decisions etc. The polls can be set to anonymous or public and lets you easily track how many members prefer specific options. CHAT WITH ANYONE - Have an instant chat with all the members of your Band, a select few or one-on-one. You can share photos, voice messages, and stickers while chatting.PLAN EVENTS AND ACTIVITIES – Want to create a meetup? Use the calendar! Anyone can create an event in a Band’s calendar and ask other members to RSVP to that specific time and date.Oh, did we mention that all of these awesome features are FREE? No pricing model ever. The easiest way to officially retrieve and pay your traffic fines through the road police and public payment information system databases.Download the official Traffic Fines app and pay your traffic fines online with one click.PAY SAFELY. All you have to do is scan the ticket barcode with your smartphone camera.The payments are processed in an instant. For your convenience, you can choose to save your card data. That would avoid you having to enter your details anew for each payment you make. You can also access the payment history at any time. Your card data will be securely protected.GET A FORMALLY STAMPED RECEIPT ACKNOWLEDGED BY THE ROAD POLICE AND PRINT IT OUT FROM YOUR DEVICEStop wasting your time. No need to keep fishing for a ticket at the place of your residence and stand in lines to pay traffic fines in a bank.Do you fear that the passport control officer will find an unpaid fine? Do you doubt that the road police actually got your payment?Pay your fines via our Official Traffic Fines app, which enables you to keep the receipt and print it out from your mobile device. THE APP PROVIDES ONLY RELIABLE AND OFFICIAL DATA.Search and review your fines through an online road police database * Pay with your bank card * Enable free pop-ups on new fines * Get your receipt and use it as a confirmation for the road police * Extend your insurance policy * Available across Russia * Online access to the 2015 Factbook on Traffic Fines and Penalties * Verification by driving licence and vehicle certificate * Government services * Formal settlements with the road police * Print out your receipt from the phone * Create payment orders * Search fines by the ticket number *We only use formally approved methods to source data from public databases.Committed a traffic offence and facing a fine? Phone Tracking for Family Members With Feature Phones Family members who don’t have the latest smart phone (or a smart phone at all), can still enjoy our GPS tracking features and benefits. ZArchiver - is a program for archive management. It has a simple and functional interface.ZArchiver lets you:- Create the following archive types: 7z (7zip), zip, bzip2 (bz2), gzip (gz), XZ, tar;- Decompres the following archive types: 7z (7zip), zip, rar, rar5, bzip2, gzip, XZ, iso, tar, arj, cab, lzh, lha, lzma, xar, tgz, tbz, Z, deb, rpm, zipx, mtz, chm, dmg, cpio, cramfs, img (fat, ntfs, ubf), wim, ecm, arc (freearc);- View archive contents: 7z (7zip), zip, rar, rar5, bzip2, gzip, XZ, iso, tar, arj, cab, lzh, lha, lzma, xar, tgz, tbz, Z, deb, rpm, zipx, mtz, chm, dmg, cpio, cramfs, img (fat, ntfs, ubf), wim, ecm, arc (freearc);- Create and decompress password-protected archives;- Edit archives: add/remove files to/from the archive (zip, 7zip, tar, apk, mtz);- Create and decompress multi-part archives: 7z, rar(decompress only);- Partial archive decompression;- Open compressed files;- Open an archive file from mail applications;- Extract splited archives: 7z, zip and rar (7z.001, zip.001, part1.rar, z01);Key features:- Multithreading support (useful for multicore processors);- UTF-8/UTF-16 supporting in filenames. Allows you to use national symbols in filenames;- No need for enabling multiselect mode. You can select files by clicking on the icon from the left of the filename;ATTENTION! Any useful ideas and wishes are welcome. You can send them by email or just leave a comment here.Mini FAQ:Q: What password?A: The contents of some archives may be encrypted and the archive can only be opened with the password (don't use the phone password!).Q: The program is not working correctly?A: Send me an email with detailed description of the problem.Q: How to compress files?A: Select all files, you want to compress, by clicking on icons (from the left of filenames). Click on the one of selected files and choose "Compress" from menu. Set desired options and press OK button.Q: How to extract files?A: Click on archive name and select suitable options ("Extract Here" or other).

EBookDroid - это программа просмотра документов и электронных книг для Андроида.Поддерживаемые форматы:PDF, DjVu, XPS (OpenXPS), Comic books (cbz,cbr), FictionBook (fb2, fb2.zip) и, начиная с версии 2, EPUB, RTF, MOBI и AWZ3.Версия 2.1.1 предлагает более гибкий подход для использования шрифтов в ПДФ: - Если внешний шрифт найден в папке рядом с документом, он будет использован. - Также пользователь может задать один или несколько каталогов (/sdcard/fonts по умолчанию) для поиска внешних шрифтов. - Если внешний шрифт в документе ПДФ совпадает по имени семейства с одним из найденных в этих каталогах, именно этот найденный шрифт и будет использоваться в данном случае. - В противном случае будет использоваться наиболее подходящий шрифт из семейства NimbusL.Версия 2.0 предоставляет новые инструменты: - Выделение текста и поддержка словарей - Рисуемые от руки аннотации - Текстовые заметкиПоддерживаемые интернет-протоколы для работы с онлайн библиотеками:OPDS (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OPDS)Если у вас возникли какие-либо проблемы, пожалуйста, сообщите нам на сайте: http://code.google.com/p/ebookdroid/ВНИМАНИЕ!!!!Перед тем как писать гневные комментарии свяжитесь с разработчиками, возможно вы что-то не так делаете.Если возникают проблемы при открытии или отображении определенного документа, пожалуйста, предоставьте этот документ.ВНИМАНИЕ!!!!EBookDroid использует mime Для открытия файлов. Андроид и файловые менеджеры не поддерживают некоторые типы. Из-за этого вы не можете открывать некоторые типы файлов через файловые менеджеры. В некоторых файловых менеджерах есть возможность добавлять новые типы файлов. Обратитесь к документации по файловому менеджеру или используйте встроенный в EBookDroid файловый менеджер. Поддерживаемые Mime типы можно найти у нас на wiki страницах.

★★当アプリはハッピーメール運営会社公認の公式アプリになります★★【ハッピーメールアプリがリニューアル】新たなデザインになったほか操作性、スピードも大幅に向上！より快適にご利用頂けるようになっています。【ハッピーメールアプリについて】ハピメの愛称で親しまれて16年。出会えると評判のハッピーメールの公式アプリになります。出会い探しの決定版ですので、ちょっとしたお暇な時間に気軽に出会いを楽しめるSNS系アプリになります。恋人・友達・婚活・恋愛など様々なニーズに合った出会いを提供しており会員数も日本最大級ですので、たくさんの会員の中から写真・プロフィール・掲示板を見て、気の合う方とのマッチングが可能です。◆Facebookアカウント対応ハッピーメールアプリはFacebookアカウントでも登録、利用が可能です。登録も簡単ですのですぐに始められます。Facebookアカウントで登録は行いますが名前はイニシャル表記に変換されますので安心してご利用いただけますまた、名前はいつでも変更可能です※ハッピーメールでどんなアクションをしてもお客様のタイムライン上には情報は一切流されませんのでご安心下さい。◆万全のサポートハピメでは24時間365日体制で運営管理を行っております。プロフィール画像不正や掲示板の不正書き込みなどは発見次第削除、注意を行い改善が見られない場合は強制退会などの処置をおこなっております。またお客様の問い合わせ等に関しましても迅速に対応致しますので安心して出会いを楽しむことができます。◆プロフ画像検索機能ハッピーメールアプリでも人気の機能です。プロフィール写真を登録している方の一覧が表示されそちらからお相手にメールを送る事ができる機能です。まずは見た目からといった方にオススメです。◆タイプ機能タイプ機能はプロフィール写真を設定している相手に好みである事をアピールできる機能です。自分がプロフィール写真を設定していると異性からタイプのアピールを受け取ることができます。メールではちょっとアプローチしにくいなんて場合にもこの機能を使えば間接的にアピールできます。◆出会い掲示板機能ハッピーメールではお客様の目的にあった出会い掲示板をご用意。掲示板から相手にメッセージを送ったり、自分で投稿して相手からのメッセージを待ったりと自分に合った出会いを楽しめます。掲示板を利用し素敵な恋人、友達を見つけて下さい。掲示板のジャンル・今からあそぼ今すぐ遊びたい！という方にオススメ。恋人に発展するかも。・友達募集お友達を探すコーナーになります。趣味や価値観が同じ方なら急接近できるかも・恋人募集恋人が欲しい!恋愛がしたい。デートなど恋愛がしたい。そんな方にオススメです。・全国メル友日本全国からメル友を募集するコーナー男女問わず交友関係を広げたい方に。・メル友募集いきなり会うのはちょっとという方に。まずはメールを通してお互いを良く知ろう。メル友から恋愛に発展することも・ヲタ友/ヲタ恋一緒にヲタな話ができる友達や恋人が欲しい。そんなあなたにはこちらのコーナーを。・ミドルエイジ/シニアミドルエイジ/シニア（40代～/60代以降）の方同士または同年代のお相手との出会いを求める方々にオススメ。まだまだ恋愛したい方はコチラ・ピュア画像掲示板写真付きの掲示板です。タイプの人が居たら積極的にアプローチしてみよう。◆豊富なプロフィール検索ハピメの検索機能は他の出会い系アプリに比べても検索機能が豊富。地域/年齢/身長/スタイル/ルックス/職業/血液型/興味ある事/等いろんな条件で検索が絞れますので彼氏、彼女を募集している方、婚活中の方、趣味友達を探している方など様々なニーズにあった出会いを探す事ができます。◆ダウンロード、登録無料アプリのダウンロード、登録は無料です。◆似顔絵機能似顔絵機能は、あなたの顔写真を元にあなたそっくりの似顔絵を作成する機能です「ノーマル」「アバター」「キュート」｢劇画｣｢漫画｣の5種類から選択でき「ノーマル」ならお一人様初回のみ無料で作成が可能。顏写真を公開するのに抵抗がある方は似顔絵を利用されてみてはいかかがでしょうか。◆利用料金についてハッピーメールアプリのポイントは１ポイント10円で男性は掲示板閲覧1ポイント、メール送信5ポイントが必要になります。女性は男性とのコンタクトに関しては全て無料です。ハッピーメールアプリを退会するとポイントは全て抹消されます。◆【ハピメ会員全国拡大中】ハッピーメールは宣伝活動も他の出会い系アプリに比べかなり力を入れております。圧倒的に多い会員数は看板・トラック・雑誌・インターネット広告・街中の大型モニター・ポケットティッシュ配布などの宣伝活動によるもの。それらの活動の成果により、男女問わず毎日数多くの方に登録を頂いており出会えると評判の優良コンテンツに成長してきました。◆18歳以上の年齢認証について生年月日もしくは年齢、証明書の名称、証明書の発行者名が明示された公的証明書(運転免許証、パスポート、健康保険被保険者証、国民保険被保険者証、年金手帳、共済組合会員証など)を提示していただき、18歳未満の児童でないことを認証しております。◆安全への取り組み365日24時間体制で常時サポート・パトロール監視業務を行っております。セキュリティも万全、出会いアプリで心配な情報管理は徹底しております。インターネット異性紹介事業届出・福岡公安委員会　認定番号 90080003000第二種電気通信事業者届出済　届出番号H4-094『ハッピーメール/HAPPYMAIL』　商標登録第5150003号JAPHIC(ジャフィック)マーク取得　認定番号1309400008◆運営会社について会社名：株式会社アイベック住所：〒810－0041福岡県福岡市中央区大名2丁目1-30A・IビルB館連絡先：092-525-7179メールアドレス：support@happymail.net代表者：板井　明生

It's a must have app for your phone.EBook reader is one of the best reading tools. It can help you to easily manage, and open all the ebooks on your phone. We also integrate multiple free ebook download sites, allowing you to easily get the desired eBooks.Supports ebook formats: epub (non-DRM), fb2, doc, txt, rtf, html, chm, tcr, pdb, prc, mobi (non-DRM), pml. Key features:* Pages or scroll view. Page flipping animation.* Table of contents, bookmarks, text search. * Bookmarks on text fragments (comments or corrections) - useful for proof reading.* Export of bookmarks to text file.* Built-in file browser, quick recent books access. * Online catalogs (OPDS) support.* LitRes online book store support.* Text to Speech (TTS) support.* Hyphenation dictionaries; * Most complete FB2 format support: styles, tables, footnotes. * Additional fonts support (place .ttf to /sdcard/fonts/)* Support for Chinese, Japanese, Korean languages; autodetection of TXT file encoding (GBK, Shift_JIS, BIG5, EUC_KR).* Day and night profiles (two sets of colors, background, backlight levels). * Brightness adjustments by flick on left edge of screen.* Background texture (stretched or tiled) or solid color.* Paperbook-like page turning animation or "sliding page" animation.* Dictionary support (ColorDict, GoldenDict, Fora Dictionary, Aard Dictionary).* Customizable tap zone and key actions.* Autoscroll (automatic page flipping) - start using menu/goto/autoscroll or assign action Autoscroll on key or tap zone; Change speed using volume keys or bottom-right and bottom-left tap zones; stop - tap any other tap zone or key.* Can read books from zip archives.* Automatic reformatting of .txt files (autodetect headings etc.)* Styles can be customised in wide range using external CSS.* Select text using double tap (optional).Place additional textures to /sdcard/.cr3/textures/ -- to be used as tiled page backgrounds.Place additional textures to /sdcard/.cr3/backgrounds/ -- to be used as stretched page backgrounds.(/cr3/ directory can also be used instead of /.cr3/, and internal SD or internal storage instead of /sdcard/)We believe that this eBook reader is what you're looking for.Need to learn more features, please download the trial.------------------Disclaimer：This app is based on Cool Reader code, and licensed under the GNU General Public License.Cool Reader: http://sourceforge.net/projects/crengine/GNU General Public License: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/

RLive App allows you to quickly listen to live radio stations from Israel and from around the world.RLive has a friendly user interface that lets you access quickly and easily, many live radio station streams With RLive you’ll have all the radio stations at your fingertips. You won’t need any other Radio App on your phone. RLive includes many new radio stations that were unavailable previously.RLive radio stations are sorted by: Municipal Radio stations, National Radio stations, Radio Genres, Radio stations by country, Middle Eastern Music radio stations, Greek Radio stations, Religious Radio stations and much more…RLive include the following radio stations: Galgalaz Radio, Radio Haifa, Radio Darom, Tel Aviv Radio, Radio Jerusalem, Radio 99 (eco), Reshet Alef, Reshet Beit, Reshet Gimel, Radios 100, Galei Zahal (GLZ) and many many more.RLive includes more than just music playing stations, it includes News, Sports radio, entertainment radio, talk shows radio, a variety of music genres and much more.The benefits of RLive:•Unique design and great user experience•The largest live Israeli radio stations •Ranking the radio stations according to their popularity•Advance technology for quick streaming and stability control•Automatic updates of stations listRLive features include:•Easily create your own favorite stations list for quick access•Timer to stop playing automatically•Alarm clock feature – wake up with your favorite radio station playing•Driving mode – listen to your favorite station while driving•Search your favorite Radio station includes voice recognition search•Easy access to control the radio station you play from the Notifications Screen•Report any inactive station and we’ll fix it•Search your preferred radio station by category or popularity •Easily share your favorite stations with others•Listen to any of these leading radio stations LIVE: Galgaltz, Galei Zahal (GLZ), radio Lelo Hafsaka, radio Lev Hamedina, radio Hamesh, Kol Barama, radio Galey Israel, Radio Mizrahit and moreAbout RLive App and RLive.co.il:RLive lets you listen to all the radio stations in one place. All stations are sorted and displayed and are easily accessed.Rlive.co.il is the only source of all Israeli radio stations and selected radio stations from around the world. The site and App are updated frequently with new radio stations.RLive App is available for Windows Phone, iPhone and iPad or by simple using your browser.

A music tag editor on your phone!#Feature*Standard id3 tags support.*Music Title, Artist and Album editor*Support quick search and preview in player *Easy Cover with "lucky cover"*Support mp3, ogg, m4a and flac.#Please send me a bug report before you give 1 star, 1 star doesn't help fixing the problem at all.#Credit: Italian translation by Gabriele Ravanetti. Swedish translation by Magnus Burton.#Notice1.WAV file doesn't support standard ID3 tags, not everything will work on WAV files.2.If you are using version 1.9.10, please update.It has problem under 2.1 and below.3.This editor uses ID3v23 format for saving.4.If you find any bug, feel free to send us feedback, you can also send me the problem file using send in long press menu.#Android KitKatIf you are using Android 4.4.2, you may find out that the app can't operate your files on your SD card anymore. That's Google changing the rules in Android, not us. No app can do that anymore. We are trying to provide a solution for this, but for now you can just move your music files to your internal storage. It will resolve all problems you are complaining.#WARNINGSamsung phones have a problem with corrupt ID3 tags. The phone's media scanner will crash when scan a corrupt file and part or all of your music will not show up in system music player any more. If your music are missing after editing, just find the file you edited and delete it. The bug doesn't exist on motorola and htc phones. And this app also has no problem with corrupt files. We are doing more tests on more phone models.#Buy the paid version if you like it.#If you have problem with editing specific audio files, please send the files to developer to improve the product.

Hailo is the easiest way to hail a ride, hands down! Set your pickup location, select a car of your choice, tap Hailo Now and that’s it! Available in the UK - London, Manchester, Leeds, Liverpool | Ireland - Nationwide | Spain - Barcelona, Madrid | Singapore - Nationwide. Track your car in real time as it comes to pick you up in minutes. Or just kick back and relax, we’ll notify you when your car has arrived. Payments are simple and happen right from the app so you can just hop out when you arrive at your destination. And safety is a top Hailo priority -- all of our drivers are licensed by the local authority.Get started with £10 or €10 off your first ride, choose the right promo code for your city: APPLDN | APPMNC | APPLEEDS | APPLIV | APPIRE================================================================Why choose Hailo?Setting your pickup location is a breeze: We integrate with Foursquare and we remember your frequently used locations.Car choices:Whether in a classic taxi or a luxury car, it’s easy to choose how you want to roll. Fare Quotes: Never again agree to pay for a fare without knowing about how much it will cost. Use our fare quotes feature to enter your destination, and we’ll give you an estimate of how much your fare will cost.An easy way to pay:No more fussing with paying for your taxi. Enter your card in our app and we’ll safely and securely keep it stored. Add multiple cards if you want, and you can switch between them for any trip. For those that must, don’t worry as you can still pay with cash.Trip History and Receipts:Handy dandy receipts are kept in your history, and we’ll also email you a copy at the end of your trip.Recover lost items: One day we left our wallet in the back of a taxi and it made for a pretty bad day. So we thought it would be great if Hailo offered a way to help you recover lost property. Accessibility: Need a wheelchair accessible taxi? No problem, flip the accessibility switch on and we’ll only send accessible vehicles.Twitter & Facebook integration: This is major because if you don’t tweet or post about your journey, how do people know it actually happened? Did it actually happen?

Avec MyScript Calculator (calculatrice), réalisez des opérations mathématiques en utilisant votre écriture.Simple, pratique et intuitif: il vous suffit d’écrire une expression mathématique sur l’écran et de laisser MyScript opérer sa magie en convertissant les symboles et les nombres en texte numérique et en affichant le résultat en temps réel.Retrouvez le plaisir d’écrire sur une feuille de papier et bénéficiez des avantages du digital (reconnaissance des gestes de suppression, reconnaissance en temps réel, etc).Bénéfices et caractéristiques :- Fonctionne avec votre smartphone Android - Fonctionne avec votre tablette Android- Utilisez votre écriture manuscrite pour écrire n'importe quelle formule arithmétique.- Écrivez et calculez des expressions mathématiques de façon intuitive et naturelle, sans clavier.- Utilisez des gestes de rature pour effacer facilement des symboles et des nombres.- Fonctionne en mode portrait et paysage.- Fonctions Annuler et Rétablir.OPÉRATEURS PRIS EN CHARGEOpérations de base : +, -, x, ÷, +/-, 1/x Opérations diverses : %, √, x!, |x| Puissances/facteurs exponentiels : ℯx, xy , x2 Parenthèses : ( )Trigonométrie : cos, sin, tanTrigonométrie inverse : acos, asin, atanLogarithmes : ln, log Constantes : π, ℯ, Phi *** IMPORTANT : Si vous souhaitez signaler un problème rencontré avec MyScript Calculator ou simplement poser une question à MyScript, n'utilisez pas l'espace de Google Play réservé aux commentaires, car il nous est impossible de vous répondre à cet endroit. Site Web de support : https://support.myscript.com/ ***Remarque sur les autorisations :Nous vous demandons l'autorisation d'accéder à la connexion Internet afin de vous permettre de regarder le didacticiel vidéo et de recevoir des notifications automatiques sur les produits.Futures versions :Nous prenons note de tous vos commentaires et remarques. Beaucoup d'entre vous nous sollicitent à propos des équations. Vous pouvez visiter notre page Web de démonstration où vous pourrez voir ce que nous avons l'intention d'ajouter dans le futur concernant les équations. Visitez :Démonstration Web sur les équations : http://webdemo.myscript.com/#/demo/equationDémonstrations Web de reconnaissance d'écriture manuscrite : http://webdemo.myscript.com/#/home

¡Bienvenido a Liga Argentina! La mejor aplicación para seguir en vivo los torneos del fútbol argentino, copas internacionales y ligas de Europa con jugadores argentinos. Sigue los partidos, lee las últimas noticias y recibe las novedades minuto a minuto.Elige además los equipos de los que quieres mantenerte informado y diariamente recibirás las noticias más importantes.Liga Argentina es una aplicación de noticias gratuita que te acerca en tiempo real toda la información que necesitas de las ligas más importantes del Fútbol Argentino, de los torneos internacionales en los cuales participan equipos argentinos y de los torneos de Europa donde juegan jugadores Argentinos!Con Liga Argentina podrás acceder a fixtures completos de Primera A, Nacional B, B Metropolitano, Federal A, Copa Libertadores, Copa Sudamericana, Mundial, torneos europeos con jugadores argentinos (Champions League, España, Italia, Inglaterra, Francia y Alemania), y sus respectivas tablas de posiciones y goleadores.Durante cada partido, te puedes informar de las formaciones de cada equipo y el detalle completo con tarjetas, goles, cambios, árbitros y estadios.También vas a puedes seguir los partidos en vivo, recibir notificaciones de cada evento importante y los goles que se hacen ¡minuto a minuto!Todas las notificaciones son configurables para que saques el máximo provecho a Liga Argentina y entérate al instante que está pasando en los partidos en curso.Liga Argentina es una versión beta totalmente gratuita. Laipni lūdzam Liga Argentīnu! Labākais pieteikums sekot dzīvot spēlēs Argentīnas futbola, starptautisko kausi un līgās Eiropā ar Argentīnas spēlētājiem.Sekojiet spēlēm, jaunākās ziņas un saņemt ziņu minūti pa minūtei.Arī izvēlēties komandas vēlaties palikt informēti un saņemt svarīgāko ikdienas ziņas. Līga Argentīna ir bezmaksas programma, kas parādīs jums ziņas reālā laikā visu jums nepieciešamo informāciju par svarīgākajiem Argentīnas futbola līga, starptautiskie turnīri, kuros piedalās Argentīnas un Eiropas turnīrus, kur spēlētāji spēlē Argentīnas komandas!Ar Liga Argentīnas jūs varat piekļūt pilnīgu ķermeņi Pirmās A, National B, B Metropolitan Federal, Libertadores Cup, Dienvidamerikas kauss, Pasaules kauss, Eiropas turnīri ar Argentīnas spēlētājiem (Čempionu līgas, Spānija, Itālija, Anglija, Francija un Vācija), un to attiecīgās Līgas un spēlētāji.Katras spēles laikā, jūs varat informēt jūs par veidojumi katras komandas un sīkumos ar kartēm, mērķiem, izmaiņām, tiesnešiem un stadioniem. Jūs arī varat sekot spēles tiešraidē, saņemt paziņojumus katram nozīmīgam pasākumam un mērķus, kas tiek veiktas ar minūti!Visi paziņojumi ir konfigurējamas lai jūs varētu iegūt vislabāko no Līga Argentīnā un uzzināt uzreiz, kas notiek ar spēles gaitu. Līga Argentīna ir bezmaksas beta versiju.

Save time, order taxis directly and without a dispatch call! Thanks to the TaxiAgent application you will see all taxis in your surrounding and your order goes directly to the driver. Complete information about price, arrival time, picture of the car and its equipment is at your disposal, before you order.In the fast selection option you find a pre-chosen nearest or the cheapest car.You do not have to wait in rain, on your display you can readily see when the taxi arrives.You carry skis, need a child seat, an English-speaking driver or you are afraid of late-night rides and prefer a woman to drive you? A green price means a guaranteed amount!You don’t need to search for names of streets around you, the application locates your current position by GPS.Last bank note in your pocket and a long way home? Even if you already know how much you will be charged, you can still check your route with a GPS controlling taximeter. Moreover, all drives are stored. Commandez un repas en ligne via votre téléphone Android ou votre tablette grâce à l'application de Thuisbezorgd.nl. L'application s'adaptera.✔ L'application est disponible en 4 langues. Wabbitemu creates a Texas Instruments graphing calculator right on your Android device. Wabbitemu supports the TI-73, TI-81, TI-82, TI-83, TI-83 Plus, TI-83 Plus Silver Edition, TI-84 Plus, TI-84 Plus Silver Edition, TI-85, and TI-86. Fast and convenient, Wabbitemu allows you to always have your trusty calculator with you. Because Wabbitemu is an emulator, the calculator it creates will act exactly like the real thing. Wabbitemu, like all emulators, requires a ROM image. Wabbitemu includes an easy to use setup wizard that will help you create a ROM image for your TI.Frequently Asked Questions:1. How do I bring up the menu?You can bring up the menu by swiping from the left edge of the screen, or pressing the menu key (if your device has one).2. How do I disable vibration when I tap on a button?Open the menu and click on settings. Under the 'Skin' category unselect 'Vibrate on keypress'3. How do I load apps like PlySmlt2 or Inequalz?To load any file to your calculator you need to first download it to your SD card or internal storage on your device. You can find the official TI applications for the 84 Plus (non color) available here: http://education.ti.com/en/us/software/search/ti-84-plus-family-ti-83-plus-family#view=math-apps. Once you have downloaded the app to your device open Wabbitemu. Swipe from the left edeg of the screen to bring up the menu, and select 'Load file'. Find the file you just downloaded in the list and select it. The file will be sent to your calculator. Apps for the 83+ and 84+ calcs will end in *.8xk. Apps for the 84+CSE will end in *.8ck or *.8xk.4. I'm missing fraction options when I press Alpha+F1! How do I get these fraction options?Fraction options (and the rest of the Alpha+FN menus) are only available on OS 2.55 MP. Wabbitemu allows you to download both 2.43 and 2.55 MP. You can check your OS version by hitting '2nd' then '+'. Then press enter to go to the about screen. If it not 2.55 MP or 2.53 MP you will need to upgrade. To upgrade you will need to recreate your ROM by going through the setup wizard again. The setup wizard is runnable if you bring up the menu by swiping from the left edge of the screen. Then select 'Re-run setup wizard'. As you go through the setup make sure you have selected OS 2.55 MP on the OS selection screen.More documentation can be found on the official website, http://wabbit.codeplex.com

STOP CIGARRETES est la meilleure application pour aider les gens qui veulent arrêter de fumer.Pour réussir d’arrêter de fumer l’application offre:* Statistiques en temps réel : le temps que vous avez été sans fumer, l'argent économisé puisque vous cessez de fumer, le nombre de cigarettes pas fumées, les minutes de la vie que vous n’avez pas perdu en fumant ....* Mérites et vie que vous avez obtenus depuis que vous avez arrêté de fumer.* Notifications chaque fois que vous atteindre un mérite ou une vie.* Lecture suggérée : une série de guides pour atteindre l’objectif, arrêter de fumer! Cela aidera aussi à prévenir les rechutes.* Communauté : les utilisateurs de Facebook de la communauté de partager le processus avec les autres.* Tests : Le prestigieux test s de Richmond et Fageström pour évaluer votre niveau de dépendance et de motivation, respectivement, avant de quitter. Test de suivi pour vérifier périodiquement les niveaux de sevrage de la nicotine.La méthodologie de STOP CIGARRETE est basée sur des études et des services offerts par les centres de santé les plus qualifiés. Cette méthode est universellement adoptée par les experts de l'aide pour arrêter de fumer. Tout au long du processus de cesser de fumer, nous avons identifié plusieurs états différents : penser à arrêter de fumer, décider d'arrêter de fumer, cesser de fumer et la rechute . Et on a trouvé que les besoins des ex-fumeurs changent pendant le processus de cesser de fumer. Avec cette philosophie, nous avons réussi à créer l'application STOP Cigarettes pour arrêter de fumer.Les gens qui ont essayé d'arrêter et n'ont pas réussi savent que cesser de fumer n'est pas seulement une question de symptômes de sevrage (maux de tête, irritabilité, etc.), Mais plutôt à surmonter avec succès la nécessité psychologique et qui est présent tout au long de la journée. Il est donc nécessaire de changer les habitudes acquises au cours de sa vie comme le tabagisme, et c'est ici que la méthodologie de STOP Cigarette est adressée.STOP Cigarette fournit des conseils, des tâches et des objectifs sur ​​la base de ces études, qui peuvent vous aider à surmonter la dépendance à la nicotine et finir avec l’habitude de fumer. Nous savons que cesser de fumer est très difficile, mais nous savons aussi que c'est possible. Et, sans aucun doute , nous savons que notre programme fonctionne!Ceci est une version d'essai, vous pouvez obtenir la version complète ici: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=es.centroestudiosalbacete.dejardefumarpro

LocalCast is the number one casting solution on Android with over 2,000,000 users!Send videos, music or pictures FROM your phone or tablet, NAS (DLNA/UPnP or Samba), Google Drive, Google+, Dropbox or a webpage TO a Chromecast, Roku, Nexus Player, Amazon Fire TV or Stick, AppleTV, Sony Bravia, Samsung, LG, Panasonic and other SmartTVs, Sonos, Xbox 360, Xbox One or other DLNA Devices.// Unique features- Videos: Zoom & rotate (Chromecast & other Google Cast devices)- Pictures: Zoom & rotate & pan Chromecast & other Google Cast devices)- NAS: SMB access- Subtitles: Opensubtitle.org integration & subs from the same folder will be added automatically// VideosPlease be aware that the Chromecast only supports a couple of formats. It can read containers like mp4, mkv, 3gp and m4v, but all these containers can use different codecs. If you can't hear the audio of a video, then the audio codec is not supported. If you can't see the video but hear the audio, then the video codec is not supported.(I am looking into "on-the-fly" transcoding)// MusicIf you cast from your device or DLNA, the album cover will be displayed on the TV. The queue and playlists work with all files, but were added to easily set up music for your next party and don't worry about it.// PicturesOn a Chromecast, Nexus Player or other Cast device:You can rotate, zoom and pan pictures easily from the "Now playing" screen, just touch the button with the four arrows.// SubtitlesIf you use a Chromecast, Nexus Player or other Cast device:You can easily add subtitles. You can download them easily inside the app from Opensubtitles.org. Subtitles in the same folder will be added automatically. You can set a dedicated subtitle folder which will be searched when you start a video. Subtitle timing, font, background and color can be changed.You can change the subtitle encoding in the settings, e.g. for arabic subtitles choose UTF-8Internal subtitles which are inside the video container don't work YET// Wireless headphones (beta)Touch "Route audio to phone" on the "Now playing" screen, to listen to what you are watching on your phone. Приложение для выбора, покупки и продажи подержанных автомобилей, мотоциклов и коммерческой техники. Более 300 000 актуальных объявлений с описаниями комплектаций и фотографиями — для тех, кто ищет авто. Возможность создать объявление прямо с мобильного — для тех, кто хочет продать. ПокупкаМожно искать конкретную модель или подбирать машину по цене, марке, пробегу и ещё паре десятков параметров. Среди прочего, можно оставить в выдаче только авто, проверенные на юридическую чистоту в системе «Автокод». Настройки поиска удобно сохранять, чтобы не задавать каждый раз заново, а определиться с выбором помогут отзывы других автовладельцев.ПродажаВыставить авто на продажу можно за несколько минут — только расскажите о его основных характеристиках. В объявление легко добавить фотографии и видео, снятые на мобильный. Все ваши объявления доступны в личном кабинете — в приложении и на сайте Авто.ру.Свои вопросы, замечания и любые идеи по улучшению приложения присылайте на hepldesk@auto.ru

Noticias Chévere es una de las aplicaciones de información más atractivas que suman las últimas noticias sobre los asuntos actuales, guapas, videos y graciosos en Colombia.El soporte técnico de Noticias Chévere se llama Motor Inteligente de Push(PIE), el cual es una tecnología basada en datos grandes. description: ReLIFE 単行本1〜4巻 累計発行部数90万部突破！ 大好評販売中！本アプリでは、オリジナルコンテンツとして「番外編エピソード」「ReLIFE登場人物紹介」「特典待ち受け画像」などをご用意！すでにReLIFE（リライフ）を読んでいる方にもお楽しみいただける内容となっています。【ストーリー】主人公 海崎新太（27歳）は、新卒として入社した会社を3ヶ月で退職。その後の就活もうまく行かず親からの仕送りも打ち切られ田舎に戻ることを迫られる。悩みを打ち明けられる友だちも彼女もいない・・・途方に暮れる新太の前に謎の人物「夜明 了」が現れる。夜明は新太にニートを対象にした社会復帰プログラム「リライフ」への参加を持ちかける。その内容は謎の秘薬で見た目だけ若返り、1年間高校生として高校に通うこと。新太はあやしい話といぶかりつつも生活費支援や実験終了後の就職斡旋などの見返りに目がくらみ実験に参加してしまい・・・。【comicoについて】comico（コミコ）はNHN PlayArtが提供する、無料の漫画サービスです。曜日替りで毎日更新されるオリジナル漫画が無料で読み放題！スマートフォンに最適化された縦読みスタイルだから、漫画をさくさく快適に読むことができます。恋愛・ギャグ・ホラー・アクションなど作品のジャンルが豊富に揃っているから自分に合った作品を楽しめます。

Rage Comic Maker for Android is an application that lets users easily create rage comics on their Android devices.The most downloaded Rage Maker in the Market! Thanks for all users!IF YOU CAN'T FIND THE FACES: many users seem to miss this, but you need to find the MENU button on your device. If you'd like to see this app translated into your native language, and you think you could do it, don't hesitate and contact me!This application is completely free and open source, but features a small ad on the top to support the developer (it cannot be turned off). If you prefer an ad-free version please contact me.Some of the key features: * Flexible number of panels (1-20) * Pan and zoom the comic canvas, as well as image elements * Undo and redo your moves * Different text styles and sizes * Save and share your creations * Use drafts to save comics in progress * Draw straight lines or free curves with different brush sizes and colorsKeyboard shortcuts:Directional pad - move object/canvasW/S - scale object/canvasA/D - rotate objectSPACE - move object to front or send to backBACK - undoR - redoBACKSPACE - delete selected objectOver 200 built-in rage faces (also known as meme faces, troll faces, reddit faces, 9gag faces, tumblr faces, etc.)!You like our app and want to support us? Visit our site for donation information: http://tmarki.com/android/donate

HappySale was created to help you sell locally the things you love but no longer need. It’s a fun and happy way to sell, buy or trade your stuff with neighbors and friends.Creating a new HappySale is a simple 3 step process:1. Take pictures of the item you want to sell2. Enter description and price3. Share on Facebook, Twitter and Google+No hassle, No headaches, Simple.And it’s absolutely FREE.So what more can you expect from HappySale?☆ Automatic item description – Writing long detailed descriptions is a huge pain. Once you enter the name of your item we bring the full item description for your review so that you won’t spend too much time on that, and your buyers will be super happy!☆ Price proposal – One of the hardest things in selling your stuff is the “for how much?” question. You want it to sell, but you don’t want to sell things for less than their worth. HappySale gives you prices of similar items and calculates, based on the information you provide, what is the recommended price you should sell your item.☆ Location-Based marketplace – If you want to see what other people are selling, HappySale brings you the best items sold in your area, and in your social circle.☆ In-app communication – HappySale enables you to chat with sellers directly inside the app. No more annoying emails of phone calls. If you like something - start chatting now!Finally, a personal message to our users: HappySale is a brand new application, and this is our first version. We are eager to provide you with an amazing experience, and hope you will enjoy our app. If you experience issues or problems, please help us improve HappySale by visiting our support website at http://www.happysale.com/support☆ ☆ ☆ ☆ ☆ ☆ Permissions explained:Like most apps, we ask for permissions on your device. These permissions are used to make the HappySale experience everything it is. We would like to explain here why we need these permissions. Transparency creates trust.Camera: We use the camera of your mobile phone or tablet to take photos of the things you want to sell. Then, we make these photos beautiful through filters.Location: We use location information from your device to save you the trouble of telling us where the item is located. We NEVER disclose accurate location information, only an estimated one.Storage: We use the internal memory of your mobile/tablet device to store photos and content from the HappySale app. We NEVER access anything but these photos and content.Accounts: When using HappySale, you will be identified using the account registered on your mobile/tablet device. We NEVER store any passwords or transfer your details to any 3rd party. When you post on HappySale, however, we present your email to potential buyers for communication.

Pro version of one of the most popular apps for American truckers featured by CDL Life, Overdrive Magazine, The Trucker, The New York Times and others. Trucker Path Pro features better design, stability, functionality and is free to use. Part of the Truckload platform - system that helps truck drivers find truckloads. More then 300 000 trucks already in the system. Truckload platform - future of trucking.Trucker Path Pro is a logistical assistant and gps for trucks geared towards professional truck drivers that provides detailed information about all major truck stops, weigh stations, Walmarts locations, number of truck parking spaces, directions, phone/fax numbers, restaurants nearby, type of truck care provided, transflo, weather, fuel prices, etc. It also provides information about weigh stations, rest areas, washes, scales, fuel stations, restaurants, hotels/motels, and allows truckers to plan their fuel and sleep stops with Trip Planner. It has never been so easy to find truck stops, fuel stations and Walmarts locations before.Where are the closest truck stops like Flying J? Who has DEF at a pump? How about a westbound rest area or truck turnout? Weigh stations on the way? All of this in one place - Trucker Path, best gps for trucks on the market.Truck stops: - Flying J Travel Plazas - Loves Travel Stops - TA Travel Center - Pilot - Petro Stopping Centers - AM Best - Pacific Pride Commercial - Petro-Canada - Sapp Brothers - Roady's Truck Stops - Thousands of independent truck stops. Truckload platform - soon to be incorporated in Trucker Path - platform that will help drives to find loads to haul. It has never been so easy to find truckload en route. We're constantly improving our database and functionality for fellow truck drivers. Truckload platform is going to be launched soon. Stay tuned for new versions.

Do you snore?With SnoreClock you can easily check if you snore. Put your smart phone beside your bed and press the red button in SnoreClock. The next morning you will know more! SnoreClock records all noise during sleep and shows red bars where you most likely to snore.Because SnoreClock takes a record of the whole night you could get even more out of it.Check- if you snore- if your partner snores- if you talk in the sleep- if something disturbs your sleepand much more.To check all noises turn your phone to switch to landscape mode. Pinch to zoom and drag to move!SnoreClock was app of the month in the german edition of the MIT Technology Review magazine!Features:1.) Records all the noise while you are sleeping2.) Outstanding snore detection technology3.) Shows red bars where you most likely snore4.) Check the effectiveness of snoring remedies5.) Measure the volume of the entire recording and shows it on the chart6.) Recording time up to 11 hours7.) Upload audio files to Dropbox or Google Drive 8.) Stops the recording on low battery. Recording with charger is recommended!9.) Use gestures in the graph to zoom or to move10.) Runs in background modeTo check all the noises rotate your phone to landscape mode. Pinch to zoom and drag to move!Features of Plus Version:No adsThe Plus Version is available through in app purchase.How to use SnoreClock - Quick Start1.) Put the smartphone near the bed 2.) Plug in the phone if you need a charged battery in the morning3.) Press the red button to start recording4.) The next morning press the red button to stop recording.5.) Use the landscape mode to analyze the data. You can listen to any position in the record. Pinch to zoom and drag to move.If you need help please select the help menu in SnoreClock. There you can access the docs or contact the support.SnoreClock is not a medical device.What users say;*****Incredible App!After using this for just 1 night, now I know why I'm always tired! Awesome execution and interface. I LOVE how we can zoom into and move throughout the graph. This is the most valuable app ever; seriously! I've tried 3 other apps but yours beats them all... easily! Thank you!*****Awakening! This app just opened my eyes! Not only it records my snores but even the sounds and voices of the spirits beyond. A must have app!*****Great app!Clear data on snoring with playback and analysis. No more guessing if you are improving or getting worse. Am now trying various methods to get better quieter sleep.*****AmazingNever rated an app before, this definitely deserves it though. So easy to use, clear and doesn't use up battery life.

The UP(R) App guides you every step of the way to a healthier you. Get started today by tracking your sleep, activities, and diet. HEART RATE THROUGHOUT THE DAYSee how your Resting and Passive Heart Rate (UP3/UP4 needed) change over time and understand what a healthy heart rate means for your health.TRACK WORKOUTSWhether you are training for a big event or just want to get a few more steps in your routine, track your activities and UP will push you to reach your best with streaks, milestone, idle alerts and more.TRACK SLEEP AUTOMATICALLYAutomatically track your sleep (UP2/UP3/UP4 needed) to track sleep stages and get insights on how you can have more energy the next day to be at your best.TRACK FOOD TO MEET DIET GOALSSet goals, log your meals and use an easy to understand food score to get the information you need to improve your diet and reach your ideal weight.NO TRACKER YET? The best place to find and share original recipes.Over 230,000 easy to follow recipes submitted and curated by fellow cooks.A unique and social cooking environment where people post recipes, pictures and discuss meals. This is what makes the site unique - you can follow a complete genealogy of a recipe, and keep on discovering new variations on themes. The recipes themselves don't need to be anything fancy, and that’s another reason why the site is unique. It gives a look into what real people are making for their families at home.It's the best place to share and find recipes.The recipes are synchronized to your watch timeline as soon as you open them. We have helped many people to live healthier and discover the taste of real food.Browse the free recipes for inspiration.Tons of recipe categories; including main dishes, appetizers, drinks, side dishes, desserts, ethnic recipes, soups, stews and diet recipes. Join the fun recipes community!Find recipes for cooking what you have in the fridge by typing the singular ingredient. App Features: - Complete recipes directions, ingredients and reviews.- Search recipes by food title or ingredients.- Forums on food related topics. - Favorite recipes for quick access. Just like a cookbook. - Forums with emphasis in recipes, food and health.- Sharing of recipes to: email, sms, twitter, facebook and others.- Sharing and send web links from allthecooks so your friends can see your recipes.- Create your own recipes; share with friends and community.- Save and share your shopping list and access offline when doing grocery shopping.Our app and site allthecooks.com has already helped millions of people to:- Have a more healthy food menu for free.- Talk with a community of people with the same food tastes.- Discover new recipes and cook great food. App makes it easy to browse substitutions and cook Holidays recipes. Including Easter, Christmas, Halloween and Thanksgiving with turkey recipes. Willys app för dig som är Willys-kund! I appen får du information om veckans erbjudanden på Willys och Willys Hemma rätt ner i fickan. Men inte bara det, Willys-appen är mer än så:ErbjudandenAlla veckans erbjudanden från din Willys- och Willys Hemma-butik rätt ner i fickan. Tydligt, enkelt och miljövänligt.ReceptVarje vecka får du minst två smarta förslag utifrån veckans Willys Plus-erbjudanden. De flesta förslagen har även recept som du når via appen. Att laga middag blir enkelt, gott och billigt!InköpslistorSkapa smidiga inköpslistor som du kan dela inom hushållet via pushmeddelanden. Lägg enkelt till egna varor eller aktuella erbjudanden. Bocka av din lista medan du handlar i butiken.ButikerFå vägbeskrivning till närmaste butik med hjälp av telefonens GPS. Lägg till din favoritbutik för att alltid vara uppdaterad på vassa erbjudanden nära dig.HandlaNå Willys e-handel med ett enkelt knapptryck. Handla online och hämta upp varorna vid Hämta-stationen i anslutning till din butik, eller få dem levererade hem.Mitt Willys PlusFölj upp alla dina köp på Willys och Willys Hemma och se hur mycket du sparat med Willys Plus. Lägg till medsökanden till ditt hushåll direkt i appen.Inte Willys Plus-kund ännu?Willys Plus är Willys med ett plus i kanten. När du ansluter dig till Willys Plus får du fler och bättre erbjudanden varje vecka i Willys och Willys Hemmas butiker. Det är helt gratis att bli Willys Plus-kund. Använd Willys-appen för att ansluta dig, därefter kan du direkt ta del av veckans Willys Plus-erbjudanden – ingen väntan på ett klubbkort eller liknande. Välkommen!Välkommen!Willys-appen behöver tillgång till följande behörigheter i telefonen:- Din plats: För att hitta närmaste Willys- och Willys Hemma-butikerna.- Skicka SMS: Om du vill dela din inköpslista genom att skicka den som ett SMS.- Nätverksåtkomst: För att hämta information från Willys angående allt som visas och hanteras i appen.- Hitta konton på enheten: Delade inköpslistor använder sig av Googles push-notifieringar som i sin tur behöver åtkomst till ditt Google-konto.- Förhindra att telefonen sätts i viloläge: Förhindrar att telefonen sätts i vänteläge just när en push-notifering (delade inköpslistor) tas emot.Google Analytics används i appen för att anonymt samla information om hur den används. Ingen personlig information lagras. Willys app jums, kas ir Willys klients! App sniedz informāciju par nedēļas darījumu pie Willys un Willys Hemma tiesības jūsu kabatā. Bet ne tikai tas, Willys app ir vairāk nekā:piedāvājumiVisi nedēļas piedāvājumus no jūsu Willys un Willys Hemma veikalā tiesības kabatā. Skaidra, vienkārša un videi draudzīgi.recepteKatru nedēļu jūs saņemsiet vismaz divas smart ieteikumus, pamatojoties nedēļas Willys Plus piedāvājumus. Vairums priekšlikumiem ir arī receptes, ka jūs varat piekļūt, izmantojot app. Gatavot vakariņas ir vienkāršs, labi un lēti!Iepirkšanās sarakstiIzveidot elastīgus iepirkumu sarakstus, ka jūs varat dalīties mājsaimniecībā via infoziņas. Viegli pievienot savu produktu vai pašreizējās akcijas. Pārbaudiet off savu sarakstu, kamēr jūs veikals veikalā.veikaliSaņemtu norādes uz tuvāko veikalu, izmantojot tālruņa GPS. Pievienot savu iecienītāko veikalu, kas vienmēr atjaunina asiem darījumiem pie jums.veikalsNu Willys e-komercija ar vienu taustiņu. Veikals tiešsaistē un uzņemt preces pie Download stacija blakus savā veikalā vai tos piegādā.Mans Willys PlusSekot līdzi visiem jūsu pirkumiem Willys un Willys Hemma un redzēt, cik daudz jūs glābti Willy Plus. Pievienot sadarbību pieteikuma mājām tieši app.Ne Willys Plus klients vēl?Willys, Willys Plus ir plus. Kad jūs izveidojat savienojumu ar Willys Plus, jūs saņemsiet vairāk un labākus piedāvājumus iknedēļas Willys un Willys Hemma veikalos. Tas ir pilnīgi bez maksas, lai kļūtu Willys Plus klientu. Izmantojiet Willys app, lai izveidotu savienojumu ar jums, tad jūs varat tieši piedalīties iknedēļas Willys Plus nodarbojas - nav gaida kluba karti vai līdzīgi. Laipni lūdzam!Laipni lūdzam!Willys app vajadzīga piekļuve šādiem vērtējumiem, tālrunis:- Jūsu atrašanās vieta: Lai atrastu tuvāko Willys un Willys Hemma veikalos.- Sūti SMS: Lai koplietotu savu iepirkumu sarakstu, nosūtot to kā īsziņu.- Network Access: Lai iegūtu informāciju no Willys par visu parādīts un apstrādā app.- Atrast kontus ierīcē: Dalīta iepirkumu sarakstus izmanto Google push paziņojumus, kas savukārt nepieciešama piekļuve jūsu Google kontu.- Novērst telefonu no miega: Novērš tālrunis atrodas gaidīšanas režīmā tikai tad, kad tiek saņemts push-notifering (dalīta iepirkšanās sarakstus).Google Analytics izmanto app anonīmi apkopot informāciju par to, kā tā tiek izmantota. Personas informācija netiek glabāta.

Аудио книга включает в себя сборник русских народных сказок. Жемчужины русского, украинского, казахского и белорусского фольклора.Великолепный сборник лучших детских сказок, рассказанных талантливой актрисой откроет вам необычайный и многообразный мир чудес и волшебства, познакомит с добрыми и отзывчивыми героями и их антиподами, а также ненавязчиво научит жизненной мудрости. Эти сказки, несомненно, займут одно из первых мест в вашей домашней коллекции. Содержание:- Маша и медведь- Волк и семеро козлят- Пузырь, соломинка и лапоть- Лисичка со скалочкой- Зайка и лиска- Умная внучка- Лиса и дрозд- Курочка РябаСказка — жанр литературного творчества:Сказка фольклорная — эпический жанр письменного и устного народного творчества: прозаический устный рассказ о вымышленных событиях в фольклоре разных народов. Вид повествовательного, в основном, прозаического фольклора (сказочная проза), включающий в себя разножанровые произведения, тексты которых опираются на вымысел. Сказочный фольклор противостоит «достоверному» фольклорному повествованию (несказочная проза) (см. миф, былина, историческая песня, духовные стихи, легенда, демонологические рассказы, сказ, предание, быличка).Сказка литературная — эпический жанр: ориентированное на вымысел произведение, тесно связанное с народной сказкой, но, в отличие от нее, принадлежащее конкретному автору, не бытовавшее до публикации в устной форме и не имевшее вариантов. Литературная сказка либо подражает фольклорной (литературная сказка, написанная в народнопоэтическом стиле), либо создаёт дидактическое произведение (см. дидактическая литература) на основе нефольклорных сюжетов. Фольклорная сказка исторически предшествует литературной.Свойства сборника для Android - колыбельные сказки для малышей- помощник родителям, бабушкам и дедушкам в убаюкивании детей- аудиосказка развивает воображение ребенка- помогает детям в познании мира через сказку- помогает малышам в изучении новых слов русского языка- аудио книга учит малюток доброте и справедливости- усыпляет не только детей но и взрослых- колыбельные для детей- сказки Андерсена, братьев Гримм, Толстого, Пушкина- сборник сказок для детей ауди- сказки на ночь бесплатно- сказки русских писателей- аудио стихи Корнея Чуковского- Аудио басни Крылова на русском офлайн- Детские песни советских времен - Аудио сказки с картинками- Аудио сказки Шарля Перро- Песни для детей- Песни из мультфильмов детскиеАудиокнига — художественное или познавательное произведение, обычно начитанное человеком (например, профессиональным актёром) или их группой и записанное на любой звуковой носитель. appName: Tokyo 7th シスターズ - アイドル育成＆本格音ゲー
description: 超有名ボカロP『kz(livetune)』『ヒゲドライバー』による楽曲続々追加！誰でも簡単にプレイできる大注目の次世代アイドル育成＆アドベンチャーゲーム――アイドルは新世代（シスターズ）へ――アイドルゲームの新時代を切り開く！フルボイス大ボリュームシナリオ・オリジナル楽曲で遊べるリズムゲーム・アイテムでアイドルを育成・ユニットを組んでバトルしよう！【ゲーム詳細】◆街に飛び出して、新しいアイドルの原石をスカウト！スカウトモードで様々なエリアを捜索し、新しいアイドルを見つけ出そう。自分だけのスーパースターユニットを作り出そう！◇全50話以上の完全オリジナルストーリー40人以上の声を持つアイドル達による全50話以上のシナリオを用意。ボイス数は3000種類以上を収録。シスターズ達と一緒にナナスタを復活させよう！◆お気に入りのアイドルと一緒にリズムゲームに挑戦！Kz(livetune)氏作詞作曲のテーマソング「Star Glitter」がプレイできる！音楽に合わせてタイミングよく画面をタッチ、簡単リズムアクションゲームライブステージを行ったアイドルは親密度がUPしていきます！月毎に描き下ろしボーカル楽曲を続々追加予定！◇登場するアイドルは全48人、カードの種類はなんと200種類以上！毎月必ず続々追加！アイドルには5種類のタイプがあり、それぞれにタイプを持っています。一定レアリティのカードの場合、ポテンシャルを上げて行くとタイプチェンジをする事が可能となります！数人のアイドルは5種類のタイプを超えた進化を遂げる事も！？◆レジェンドボスを倒せ！！スカウトの進行度によりレジェンドボスに挑戦することができるぞ！！育てたアイドル達と一緒に力を合わせて倒そう！一定回数クリアすると新たなシナリオをゲットできる…？【ストーリー】2032年に突如引退した伝説の国民的アイドル「Tokyo7thシスターズ」。彼女たちが表舞台から姿を消してから、誰もがこんな風に感じていました。―アイドルはもう終わった…それから2年。あなたはエンタテイメントの栄華を極める国際指定娯楽都市区画 “TOKYO-7th”にある次世代アイドル劇場『777（スリーセブン）』（※通称：ナナスタ）の二代目支配人に任命されます。とはいえ街は何年も前から変わらず「アイドルはもう時代遅れ」という流れ……ナナスタも例に漏れず、閑古鳥さえも溜め息をつくという有り様です。そんなある日、新しい“マネージャー”があなたのもとに現れます。―アイドルが終わったなら、新しいアイドルを作ればいいんだよ、強い絆で結ばれた本物の「シスターズ」をね！まもなく、あなたと「ナナスタシスターズ」の物語の幕が上がります。【注意事項】対応環境：Android4.03以上※非推奨端末につきましては、動作の保証を行っておりません。万が一問題が発生した場合に、サポート対象外となる可能性がございます。ご了承ください。※一部、古い端末は動作保証外となっております。詳しくはお問い合わせください。このアプリケーションには、（株）ＣＲＩ・ミドルウェアの「CRIWARE (TM)」が使用されています。

Aquestes dades s'agreguen i s'utilitza per ajudar a proporcionar la informació més útil per als nostres clients.Funcions dins el Cineplex Mobile AppLlegir Estat del telèfon i la identitatLi permet anomenar un teatre Cineplex directament des de dins de l'aplicació mòbil.Presa de fotografies i vídeosLi permet utilitzar la càmera del telèfon per escanejar un cartell o Codi QR que pot ser part d'una oferta especial o promoció.Ubicació GPS que pot ser la ubicació aproximada (basada en xarxa) o la ubicació precisa (GPS i basada en xarxa)Permet que l'aplicació per determinar la seva ubicació, a continuació, us mostrarà els cinemes més propers a la seva ubicació.Accés a la xarxa completa, rebre dades d'Internet, connexions de vista de la xarxa, veure connexions WiFiPermet qualsevol característica relacionada amb la xarxa en l'aplicació, com ara la integració social de compte de xarxa per enllaçar amb altres propietats com ara Cineplex Cineplex Connect.Afegir / modificar els esdeveniments de calendariLi permet crear un esdeveniment de calendari, en general al voltant d'anar a veure una pel·lícula o esdeveniment especial, i si ho desitja, compartir aquest esdeveniment del calendari amb les seves xarxes socials.Llegiu la capacitat d'emmagatzematge de contingut actual de l'emmagatzematge USBPermet que l'aplicació determini si hi ha prou espai per a descarregar la revista Cineplex al dispositiu mòbil.Troba els comptes al dispositiuPermet la integració de comptes de xarxa dins de l'aplicació.Control de Vibració i desactivar el mode standPermet el reproductor de vídeo dins del seu telèfon mòbil per jugar un tràiler de la pel·lícula sense interrupció.

CuidAPPlas es una aplicación de la Federación Española de Cáncer de Mama (FECMA) desarrollada con el apoyo de Samsung y la colaboración de la Sociedad Española de Oncología Médica (SEOM) y avalada por el Grupo Español de Cáncer de Mama (GEICAM).CuidAPPlas es una aplicación que acerca a las mujeres, especialmente las más jóvenes, los hábitos de vida saludables y las principales recomendaciones para la detección precoz del cáncer de mama. Se trata de una app informativa y práctica, que nos anima a registrar y crear avisos de nuestras visitas al ginecólogo y pruebas médicas, así como a hacer un seguimiento de la fertilidad y la menstruación. Toda la información introducida queda registrada en un historial que podremos consultar cuando sea necesario. Además, a través de un cuestionario orientativo, podemos construir nuestro perfil y obtener información sobre los factores y hábitos de nuestra vida que son relevantes para la detección precoz de la enfermedad. CuidAPPlas is an application of the Spanish Breast Cancer Federation (FECMA) developed with the support of Samsung and the collaboration of the Spanish Society of Medical Oncology (SEOM) and endorsed by the Spanish Group of Breast Cancer (GEICAM).CuidAPPlas is an application that about women, especially younger, healthy lifestyle habits and key recommendations for early detection of breast cancer.This is an informative and practical app, which encourages us to register and create reminders of our visits to the gynecologist and medical tests, as well as to monitor fertility and menstruation. All information entered is recorded in a history that we consult when necessary.In addition, through a policy questionnaire, we can build our profile and information on the factors and habits of our life that are relevant for early detection of the disease.

appName: Thiên giới hoàng hậu - Cực hay
description: Giới thiệu: Thien gioi hoang hau Hoàng thượng, hưu!Phủ thừa tướng tam tiểu thư, Mộc Thanh Dao bị Nam An vương Mộ Dung Lưu Chiêu một quyền đánh chết, nhưng lại nghênh đón một nữ nhân hoàn toàn mới , hào quang bắn ra bốn phía, mị lực kinh người.Mộc Thanh Dao , mặc dù ngươi là hoàng đế cao quý, cho ta thiên giới sính lễ, nhưng ta đường đường tham mưu trưởng lục chiến, quân đoàn thứ 17, lại cùng nữ nhân khác cộng thị nhất phu sao? nam nhân như vậy ta hưu!Mộ Dung Lưu Tôn, hoàng đế tuấn mỹ túc trí đa mưu trong thất quốc, lại bị một nữ nhân háo sắc hưu, đôi mắt đen nhuộm tia sáng chói mắt, hắn sẽ không chịu để yên!Mộ Dung Lưu Chiêu, Huyền Nguyệt quốc Nam An vương, lạnh lùng tà mị, xem nữ nhân là vật hạ đẳng, một đấm đánh chết nữ nhân háo sắc, nhưng lại nghênh đón một người hoàn toàn mới, mê đắm hắn!Sở Thiển Dực, con trai của Huyền Nguyệt quốc hữu thừa tướng, phúc hắc vô địch, mắt cao hơn đầu, nhưng lại thích cái háo sắc nữ nhân kia, đây là không phải là gọi tự gây nghiệt không thể sống?Vô Tình, quỷ y của Vô Tình cốc, trích tiên mỹ nam, mới gặp gỡ nàng, thoáng như ngàn năm hiểu rõ đợi chờ, ta nguyện từ bỏ qua này thân, hóa thành cây hứa nguyện, một thân đơn độc từ đây.Trưởng Tôn Trúc, Thanh La quốc thái tử, yêu nghiệt duy mỹ, Người đời không nhìn được vàng cẩn ngọc, lại đem minh châu xem như bụi đất, ta nguyện ý lấy Thanh La quốc thái tử phi vị cưới ngươi làm vợ.Trời hiện dị tướng, phượng rơi tướng phủ, người được phượng thống nhất thất quốc, có ai biết? Phượng lại là cái nữ nhân mang danh háo sắc khắp thiên hạ.

Zoek en vind uw favoriete nieuwe auto, occasion, motor en/of klassieker met de Auto Trader app.De functies van de Auto Trader app zijn:Functies:Auto's, Klassiekers, Motoren en Bedrijfswagens zoeken.Bewaarde zoekopdracht: sla een zoekopdracht eenvoudig op voor een volgende keer.Bewaarde auto’s: bewaar je favoriete auto’s.Foto galerij: foto’s worden full-screen getoond.Direct contact opnemen met de autoverkoper.AutoWeek nieuws - autonieuws, interessante testverslagen en video’s.Deel de advertentie met familie en vrienden.Selecteer je favoriete auto uit 220.000 soorten voertuigen.Selecteer uit de resultatenlijst een auto.Lees de autospecificaties en omschrijving.De zoekresultaten zijn verrijkt met waardevolle AutoWeek-data zoals gebruikskosten, consumentenwaarderingen of AutoWeek-waarderingen.Bekijk foto’s en video’s op groot formaatSla je favoriete auto opDeel je auto op Facebook, Twitter of via e-mailBekijk waar de auto staat in NederlandBel of mail de aanbieder van de auto

Mit der BAWAG P.S.K. eBanking App für Smartphones können Sie ganz einfach Ihre Bankgeschäfte von unterwegs erledigen. Die eBanking App bietet Ihnen die höchsten Sicherheitsstandards. Ihre Bankdaten werden durch ein individuelles Sicherheitsmuster zusätzlich geschützt. Funktionen /Finanzübersicht/Die Finanzübersicht bietet Ihnen einen Überblick über Ihre zum eBanking berechtigten Konten. /Kontostand/Hier können Sie jederzeit Ihren aktuellen Kontostand ansehen. Mit der QuickKontostand-Funktion können Sie diesen jetzt sogar ohne vorherigem Login nur mittels Sicherheitsmuster abrufen./Kontodetails/Hier finden Sie Detailinformationen zu Ihren Konten./Umsätze/In der Umsatzanzeige sehen Sie die Kontobewegungen (Buchungen). /Umsatzsuche/Nutzen Sie diese Funktion, wenn Sie auf der Suche nach einem bestimmten Umsatz sind./Wertpapierpositionen/Ihr Depot wird mit den entsprechenden Wertpapierpositionen inkl. der Positionsdetails in der Finanzübersicht angezeigt./Inlandsüberweisung/Mit dieser Funktion können Sie Überweisungen innerhalb von Österreich beauftragen. Mit der IBAN-Scanfunktion können Sie eine vorgedruckte IBAN erfassen. /Eigenübertrag/Wenn Sie Geld zwischen Ihren eigenen Konten überweisen möchten, wählen Sie diese Funktion./Überweisung SEPA/Wählen Sie diese Funktion, wenn Sie in ein Land der EU oder in die Schweiz, Monaco, San Marino, Norwegen, Island oder Liechtenstein, in der Währung EUR überweisen möchten. Mit der IBAN-Scanfunktion können Sie eine vorgedruckte IBAN erfassen./Überweisung Ausland/Wählen Sie diese Funktion, wenn Sie in ein Land außerhalb des SEPA-Raumes überweisen wollen und Sie nicht in der Währung EUR überweisen möchten. /Scan & Transfer/Mit dieser Funktion können vorgedruckte Zahlungsinformationen von einem Zahlschein für Inlandsüberweisungen rasch erfasst und überwiesen werden./Zahlen mit QR-Code/Scannen Sie ganz einfach einen QR-Code ein, und die Überweisungsdaten werden automatisch als Inlands- bzw. EU-Standardüberweisung übernommen. /Kontrollmappe/Alle gezeichneten Zahlungsaufträge können Sie in der Kontrollmappe mit deren Status überprüfen./Filialfinder/Der Filialfinder zeigt Ihnen den schnellsten Weg zur nächsten BAWAG P.S.K. Filiale./Geldautomat Finder/Mit dem Geldautomat Finder finden Sie immer einen Geldautomaten in Ihrer Nähe. /SmartCash/SmartCash ermöglicht Ihnen, Bargeld an Geldautomaten in den Foyers der BAWAG P.S.K. zu beheben. Sie bekommen einen kostenlosen Code per SMS zugesendet, mit welchem Sie einmalig am Geldautomat beheben können. /Kontokartenadministration/Mit dieser Funktion können Sie die Limite Ihrer Kontokarte ändern, eine neue PIN anfordern, ein Duplikat Ihrer Karte bestellen oder Ihre Karte sperren. /Wertkarte aufladen/Laden Sie in unserem Webshop verschiedenste Wertkarten online mit Guthaben auf./Rechner/Über die Rechnerfunktion haben Sie alle Rechner der BAWAG P.S.K. im Überblick./Kreditkarte sperren/Für den Fall eines Verlusts oder Diebstahls Ihrer Kreditkarte finden Sie hier alle wichtigen Telefonnummern, um Ihre Karten so schnell wie möglich sperren zu lassen./Mails/Rufen Sie Ihre Postfachnachrichten direkt in Ihrer App auf./Kontakt/Hier finden Sie alle wichtigen Kontaktdaten./Terminvereinbarungsformular/Vereinbaren Sie schnell und einfach einen Termin in Ihrer Wunschfiliale./Individualsortierung/Sie können die Icon-Menüstruktur nach Ihren Wünschen mittels Drag&Drop festlegen. In den Einstellungen kann diese zurückgesetzt werden.Dieses Feature wird ab Android 4.0 unterstützt./Sprachen/ Die eBanking App ist in sechs Sprachen erhältlich (Verfügbarkeit abhängig von den Einstellungen des Gerätes): deutsch, englisch, serbisch & türkischHinweis:Die Scanfunktionen werden bei folgenden Geräten nicht unterstützt:* Geräte ohne nach hinten gerichteter Kamera beziehungsweise ohne Kamera * Geräte ohne Autofokus-Unterstützung * Geräte mit zu geringem Speicher A BAWAG P.S.K. eBanking app okostelefonokra, akkor könnyen csinálni a banki útközben. A eBanking app nyújt Önnek a legmagasabb biztonsági követelményeknek. Az Ön banki adatok továbbá védi az egyén biztonságát mintát.Jellemzők/ Pénzügyi áttekintés /A pénzügyi összefoglaló áttekintést ad a eBanking törvényes számlákat./ Egyensúly /Bármikor megtekintheti a folyó fizetési mérleg. A Quick Balance funkció segítségével letölteni nélkül is előző bejelentkezést, csak az a biztonság, mintás ezt most./ Fiók adatai /Itt talál részletes információt a számlákat./ Értékesítési /Az értékesítési hirdetési számla tranzakciók (foglalások)./ Sales keresés /Használja ezt a funkciót, ha keres egy konkrét értékesítés./ Értékpapírok pozíciók /A portfólió jelenik meg a megfelelő értékpapír-pozíciók incl. A pozíciókat a Pénzügyi Szemle./ Belföldi átutalás /Ezzel a funkcióval megadhatja az átutalások Ausztrián belül. Az IBAN-scan funkció lehetővé teszi, hogy rögzítse egy előnyomott IBAN./ Self-carry /Ha azt szeretnénk, hogy pénzt között a saját számlák, válassza ki ezt a funkciót./ Transfer SEPA /Válassza ki ezt a funkciót, ha szeretné, hogy adja át egy ország az EU-ban vagy Svájcban, Monaco, San Marino, Norvégia, Izland vagy Liechtenstein pénznemében EUR. Az IBAN-scan funkció lehetővé teszi, hogy rögzítse egy előnyomott IBAN./ Külföldre utalását /Válassza ki ezt a funkciót, ha azt szeretné, hogy adja át az ország területén kívül a SEPA területén, és nem akarja átadni a valuta EUR./ Scan & Transfer /Ez a funkció előnyomott fizetési információkat lehet gyűjteni, és át gyorsan egy fizetési űrlapot belföldi átutalások./ Ábrák a QR-kód /Szkennelhet egy QR-kódot, és az adatok automatikusan elfogadni, mint a hazai, vagy EU-szabvány átadása./ Check Pénztárca /Minden feliratkozott fizetési megbízások, akkor ellenőrizze a check mappát az állapotát./ Iroda kereső /Az áruház kereső megmutatja a leggyorsabb útvonal a következő BAWAG PSK Branch./ ATM kereső /Az ATM kereső mindig megtalálja egy ATM közelében./ Smart Cash /Intelligens Készpénz lehetővé teszi, hogy készpénzben ATM a folyosói a BAWAG PSK kijavítani. Kapsz egy ingyenes kódot SMS-ben küldött, amellyel meg tudod oldani, amint az ATM./ Fiók kártyák Adminisztráció /Ez a funkció lehetővé teszi, hogy módosítsa a határait fiókja kártyát, kérhet új PIN-kódot, rendeljen egy másolatot a kártya vagy megszünteti a kártyát./ Érték kártya feltöltés /Feltölt online webáruházban különböző prepaid kártyák egyenlegét./ Számítógép /A számológép funkcióval van az összes számítógépet a BAWAG PSK Áttekintés./ Hitelkártya zár /Abban az esetben, elvesztése vagy ellopása a hitelkártya itt megtalálja az összes fontos telefonszámok blokkolni a kártyák, amilyen gyorsan csak lehetséges./ Mail /Hívja fel postafiókját üzenetek közvetlenül a app./ Kapcsolat /Itt megtalálod fontos elérhetőségeit./ Kinevezés formában /Gondoskodjon egy találkozót gyorsan és egyszerűen a kedvenc áruház./ Egyéni válogatás /Megadhatja, hogy az ikon menü felépítése, hogy a szeretet húzással. A beállítások, ezek vissza lehet állítani.Ez a szolgáltatás az Android 4.0./ Nyelvek /A eBanking app hat nyelven (a rendelkezésre álló beállításaitól függ a készülék): német, angol, szerb és törökMegjegyzés:A beolvasási funkciók nem támogatottak az alábbi eszközöket:* Devices nélkül hátrafelé néző kamera vagy kamera nélkül* Devices nélkül autofókusz támogatása* Készülékek kevés memória

V3 Mobile Plus provides simple and fast identity authentication service for secure mobile financial transactions.It interoperates with mobile banking, credit card, stock trading and shopping services ensuring all of your mobile transactions are secure.< Features >1. Anti-VirusAhnLab’s mobile anti-virus engine protects your smartphone from viruses, worms, Trojan horses and other malware.When you open an application interlocked with V3 Mobile Plus, the anti-virus engine will get updated to the latest version, and Real-Time Scan will scan your device for malware. When a malicious file is detected, you can remove it immediately.* The anti-virus feature will run even if you do not use the ‘Authenticator' service.2. AhnLab AuthenticatorAhnLab Authenticator is an identity authentication service that is simpler than the SMS or ARS authentication method required for some online services on your own smartphone.If you need additional identity authentication for secure transactions of mobile banking or payment on smart phone, just use AhnLab Authenticator. Enjoy simple and fast one-time security code authentication for secure online financial transactions.Using 'AhnLab Authenticator' will prevent authentication-bypass.※ Mobile Network Operators* Only supported on a smartphone registered in your name with a MNO (SKT, KT and LGU+) or MVNO.※ How to Use AhnLab Authenticator* To activate “AhnLab Authenticator” through V3 Mobile Plus, you need mobile data or Wi-Fi connection.* When using the service for the first time through an application, you need to consent to the Terms of Use and register your device.* Allow notification when using online banking or app-card applications interlocked with V3 Mobile Plus for security code check and one-touch authentication.* To keep your USIM card secure, install the USIM agent application provided by your MNO and keep it updated to the latest version.[Note]* When you install/open multiple applications simultaneously, the service may not work properly according to your device.- If you have closed the application interlocked with V3 Mobile Plus 2.0, but the service is still running, go to Settings > Manage applications and select V3 Mobile Plus 2.0 and force stop it.- When an error occurs while using an application interlocked with V3 Mobile Plus 2.0, go to Settings > Manage applications and select the application and clear the data, and then restart the application.- If you installed V3 Mobile Plus from an unofficial application market, reinstall the service via Google Play Store. ※ We cannot reply to Review comments. If you have any questions or encounter any errors, please email us your smartphone model, OS version, application version and details at customer@ahnlab.com.

From the world's most trusted pregnancy brand, "What to Expect When You're Expecting", this app guides you through pregnancy day-by-day and week-by-week. Based on your due date, you'll receive personalized information and the latest parenting news, and join a tight-knit community of other parents and moms-to-be like you. You’ll be empowered with the best tools and support to help you prepare and feel in control every step of the way – helping you achieve a happy, healthy pregnancy. - Personalized daily tracker shows your week and day of pregnancy, baby's development measured in fruit sizes, and a countdown to your due date- A daily feed of pregnancy tips, reasons to smile every day, health news, and passionate stories from real parents, created just for you- Week-by-week development info, helping you understand your changing body and the latest on baby's development through each stage- Pregnancy videos showing just what to expect this week- Meet moms-to-be in the same week of pregnancy and share experiences, tips, photos and encouragement in your birth group- Special groups devoted to birth locations, interests, medical conditions, parenting style, and more!

The smartphone camera app "aillis" gives you everything you need to take and edit photos. Whether you're shooting selfies or professional photographs, the powerful editing tools featured in this app allow you to unleash your inner creativity. Produce quality collages, add adorable personal touches, and do much, much more with aillis.Selfies: Snap a quick photo with your inner camera. Use the Live filter and Beauty feature to show the world the real you.Camera features: aillis comes complete with a timer, flash, mirror mode, level, grid, and all the other features you need to take the perfect picture.Filters: Brighten up shadowy photos, make your lunch snapshots look even more delicious, or choose from any one of a myriad of ways to make your pics stand out.Add Text: Create your own movie posters by adding catchy slogans to your pictures, scribble poppy messages, or add your favorite meme. You can even choose the font!Brushes: Go Picasso on your pictures with options that let you pick the color and brush size.Stamps: Decorate your photos with over 20,000 unique stamps just waiting to be discovered.Collages: Combine multiple photos into one, perfect collage and relive the memories all over again.Share: Upload your fixed-up photos instantly to Facebook, Instagram, or the social network of your choice.Multilingual support: aillis offers support for Chinese, English, French, German, Indonesian, Italian, Portuguese, Russian, Spanish, and more.Follow us on Instagram:http://instagram.com/aillis_official

Introducing Skype Qik (say “quick”), a free* video messenger made for capturing moments and sharing laughs throughout your day. Set up a group and immediately start shooting and swapping videos. Send something to crack your friends up, or show off a new dance move—whatever you want. New messages are added to a chat that you can watch like a movie with a single tap. Qik even lets you erase your video right out of the chat.**Don’t just send just text or photos. Go full-video with Qik.What can you do with Qik?•Create groups in a flash: grab a bunch of friends from your phone’s address book and start a private chat. •Pre-record and send video clips (Qik Fliks): can’t respond right away? Thumbs-ups, smileys and more, starring you. •Erase your message and it disappears from the conversation.** •Keep it fresh—messages are automatically erased from Qik after two weeks.•Start a conversation any time—no login, usernames, or passwords needed.* Mobile data rates may apply.. We recommend using an unlimited data plan or WiFi connection.** It may be possible for recipients to capture and save videos elsewhere before you delete them from Qik.

"Screen Off and Lock" vous permet d'éteindre votre appareil du bout des doigts, sans utiliser de bouton physique.** Si vous aimez ce soft ou si vous voulez soutenir mon développement d' applications : s'il vous plaît, allez voir la version payante ( don ) avec plus de fonctions ! Merci ! **** Pour désinstaller l'application, s'il vous plaît, allez à la page de configuration et cliquez sur le bouton "Supprimer de l'administrateur du dispositif " **Avec plus de 2 millions d'utilisateurs et plus de 30 langues supportées , "Screen Off and Lock" est le n°1 des applications de mise en veille d'écrans dans le Google Play Store."Screen Off and Lock" vous permet d'éteindre vos appareils à partir :1 . D'un raccourci de lancement2 . De Widget taille 1x1 - 4x4, redimensionnable dans Android 4.0 + ( également disponible en écran de verrouillage pour Android 4.2 +) (version Don )3 . De la barre de notifications4 . D'un bouton flottant sur toutes les applications ! ( Double Tap pour l'utiliser) (version Don)5 . Du bouton de recherche (si votre appareil l'a)Autres caractéristiques :1 . Plusieurs animations lors de la mise en veille de l'écran ( y compris le très fameux style "Old TV" )2 . Effet sonore lors du verrouillage / déverrouillage de l'écran3 . Vibrations lors de l'extinction de l'écranRemarques:Pour ceux qui ne peuvent pas voir l'animation lors de l'extinction de l'écran, même après avoir réinstallé l'application, s'il vous plaît suivez les procédures ci-dessous:Android 4.x : Allez dans « Paramètres> Options pour les développeurs > Echelle animation transition " , puis sélectionner 1x pour cette option.Android 2.x : Assurez-vous d'avoir sélectionné l'option " Toutes les animations " dans " Paramètres> Affichage> Animation".

Bestelle bequem hochwertige Gerichte mit unserer App! Periscope lets you broadcast live video to the world. Going live will instantly notify your followers, who can join, comment and send you hearts in real time. The more hearts you get, the higher they flutter on the screen.Other features:• REPLAY: When your broadcast is over, you can make it available for replay so viewers can watch later. Viewers can replay your broadcast with comments and hearts to relive the full experience. Replays currently last 24 hours. You can delete your replay at any time.• PRIVATE: If you want to broadcast to specific people, press the Private option before going live and choose who you want to invite to your broadcast. • TWITTER: You can choose to share your Periscope broadcasts on Twitter by tapping the bird icon before you start broadcasting. When you go live, you’ll tweet a link so that your Twitter followers can watch on the web (or in the app)• MANAGE NOTIFICATIONS: Periscope will suggest people for you to follow based on your Twitter network. You can always follow new people, or unfollow them if you don’t want to be notified when they go live. You can also adjust notification preferences in Periscope Settings (in Profile)• HEARTS: Hearts are a fun, easy way to let the broadcaster know you're enjoying the broadcast. Tap the screen to share the love!
