Conosci il modo più salutare per dimagrire?Leggere innumerevoli articoli nelle riviste, fare delle diete sbagliate, o riempirvi di pillole dietetiche “magiche” non è la giusta risposta, nonostante molte persone si rivolgano a queste soluzioni. La miglior risposta è anche la più facile – chiedi ad un nutrizionista come perdere peso in una maniera salutare! Il suo consiglio suonerà più o meno così: "Le diete veloci sono pericolose e non salutari, perciò devi controllare quello che mangi e quanto consumi! Taglia i dolci e gli hamburger. Controllati e mangia il più possibile del cibo salutare. Inoltre, devi registrare tutti i tuoi pasti in una tabella e contare le calorie!"A questo punto potresti pensare…Usare una tabella per contare le calorie? Che noia! Come ammetteranno milioni di persone, dopo due o tre giorni, smetterai semplicemente di usare la tabella e ritornerai alle tue vecchie cattive abitudini, mangiando oltre il dovuto…Nel nostro mondo moderno ed high-tech, ci deve essere un’altra soluzione, no? Certo!La app "Perdere peso senza dieta" è un contatore di calorie semplice da usare che ti fornisce un modo divertente e confortevole per perdere peso! Dovrai semplicemente registrare tutti i tuoi pasti nell’app, (che è molto più comodo di portare una tabella ovunque tu vada!) e ti dirà se il tuo pasto era salutare o meno. Calcolerà inoltre le calorie, proteine, grassi e carboidrati. Se ti dimentichi di registrare un pasto qualsiasi, l’app te lo ricorderà!Inoltre, quanto tempo della tua giornata spensi a correre, camminare, saltare o nuotare? Registra tutti i diversi tipi di attività fisica nell’app e questa ricalcolerà quanto dovrai assumere durante la dieta in modo che il tuo corpo assuma il corretto apporto calorico necessario agli esercizi svolti.Non dimenticare di pesarti! "Perdere peso senza dieta" controlla il tuo peso, così come il tuo busto, giro vita e le misure della coscia, in modo che tu possa controllare i tuoi progressi nel raggiungimento dei tuoi obiettivi di dimagrimento. La grafica di facile lettura sarà una fonte di motivazione ed incoraggiamento nel continuare a lavorare. Anche se non sai come mangiare in maniera salutare, e nemmeno che esercizi fare per tornare in forma, la nostra app ti suggerirà un’alimentazione e dei programmi di allenamento personalizzati che ti aiuteranno a perdere peso in maniera sana e sostenibile. Tutto ciò di cui hai bisogno è di cuocere i cibi che ti suggeriamo e fare gli esercizi raccomandati per raggiungere tutti i tuoi obiettivi!"Perdere peso senza dieta” è più di un semplice contatore di calorie; questa nuova app rivoluzionaria ti darà innumerevoli suggerimenti e trucchi su come perdere peso in maniera salutare!“Perdere peso senza dieta” ti offre queste uniche ed utili caratteristiche:- Grafici giornalieri per monitorare proteine, grassi, carboidrati- Cronologia progresso delle misure busto, vita, fianchi e misure- Monitoraggio Consumo di acqua- Promemoria di consumo giornaliero e consumi di acqua- Scrivere note, impostare stati d'animo, di capacità fotografiche- Fotografare il cibo in modo da poterlo registrare in un secondo momento- Base personalizzata per il cibo e l’allenamento- Pianificazione dei tuoi pasti ed esercizi futuri- Programmi di perdita di peso predefinitiInsieme a tutti questi suggerimenti, trucchi ed una costante guida ad una sana perdita di peso, otterrai anche premi (perle) per un uso frequente del nostro contatore di calorie! Queste perle ti daranno diritto ad uno sconto per l'acquisto della versione senza pubblicità dell’app! Inoltre, se otterrai un numero sufficiente di perle, potrai persino rimuovere i banner pubblicitari gratis!

Așa am ajuns să avem cel mai mare parc de taxiuri, controlat și reînnoit periodic. Grija noastră față de mașini, e grija noastră pentru ca fiecare călătorie a ta să fie ireproșabilă. Siguranța ta este importantă, mașinile Eurotaxi sunt întreținute, iar periodic sunt verificate în service. Cu noi drumul tău este unul liniștit într-un ambient curat, lipsit de fum și zgomot, iar șoferii îți vor acorda 100% din atenția lor. Am investit în oameni și în formarea lor ca profesioniști. Avem grijă ca personalul nostru să fie mereu pregătit pentru a răspunde într-un timp scurt și cu amabilitate nevoilor tale. Operatoarele tratează cu respect și promptitudine fiecare cerere. Șoferii respectă standardele și protocoalele pentru ca orice călătorie să fie eficientă și plăcută - nu fumează în timpul călătoriei, nu vorbesc la telefon, nu ascultă muzică la un volum ridicat, iar dacă cursa începe fără a fi pornit aparatul, aceasta va fi gratis. Pentru că prima impresie contează, șoferii noștri sunt mereu îngrijiți - singurii din Iași care au ținută obligatorie. Am crescut o dată cu piața ieșeană, am anticipat schimbările și ne-am adaptat constant cerințelor. Am stabilit parteneriate și am colaborat cu profesioniști și specialiști calificați. Ne-am onorat contractele și am răspuns cu promptitudine comenzilor. Avem cea mai simplă și cea mai accesibilă aplicație online care face legătura directă între tine și cel mai apropiat taxi. Suntem aici pentru a-ți face fiecare plimbare cu Eurotaxi una memorabilă. Continuăm să călătorim împreună.

¿Qué puedes consultar o hacer con esta aplicación?Configura la pantalla de inicio con el botón menú (superior derecha), chequeando las secciones que quieres que se muestren al iniciar la aplicación y el fondo deseado:- El tiempo: muestra la previsión elaborada por la AEMET (actualizado cada 2 horas, mientras tanto se puede consultar offline). Busca por nombre del municipio, provincia, localización y por voz.- Tráfico: muestra las incidencias registradas en la Dgt. Accede también al mapa de google según la provincia seleccionada con la capa del tráfico.- Calendarios: accede al calendario laboral elaborada por la seguridad social de tú municipio. Calendario clásico (offline) con eventos importantes. Calendario 2015 fórmula 1, calendario 2015 motogp, calendario de la liga de fútbol, calendario de nombres (offline), horóscopo, lunar ...- Kiosko: prensa nacional e internacional, accede a los principales medios de comunicación y revistas del país, puedes crear tú propio kiosko seleccionando tus periódicos y revistas favoritas.- Titulares: muestra los titulares de las fuentes seleccionadas. Pulsa el icono de la tierra y podrás seleccionar las fuentes de tus titulares.- Televisión: consulta la guía y la noticias de televisión- Lotería: consulta los últimos resultados de la lotería.- Cine: cartelera, estrenos y noticias de medios especializados.- Cuaderno: crea tus listas de tareas a realizar (en el caso de tener tareas pendientes crea una notificación). Puedes compartir, añadir por voz, añadir lista de la compra, reproducir frases (esta opción es necesario que el teléfono tenga instalado speechtotext), guardar tú posición para luego visualizar en el mapa, grabar un recordatorio, exportar las notas a un fichero de texto guardado en la tarjeta de memoria (Cuadernonotas), que luego puedes importar en el mismo dispositivo o en otro donde tengas instalada la aplicación. - Diccionario: consulta en el diccionario de la rae, teniendo un registro de las palabras consultadas, además se podrá consultar también en la wikipedia y en un diccionario de sueños.- Salud: encontrar información sobre temas de salud en diferentes medios, .- Radio: reproductor online de las principales emisoras de radio de españa, más emisoras por tipo de música.- Buscar: recopilación de algunos de los principales sitios de búsqueda. Desde esta opción, pulsando en el icono del mundo, podrás seleccionar si quieres añadir el enlace buscado a tú kiosko- Aplicaciones: selecciona o busca las aplicaciones que tienes instaladas en el móvil (cajón de aplicaciones).- Calculadora IMC: una sencilla calculadora para saber cual es tú índice de masa corporal y guardar histórico.- Cronómetro: sencillo cronómetro con la opción de contabilizar la distancia recorrida activando el gps.- Mapas: diferentes tipos de mapas, tiempo, provincias, comunidades, continentes, capitales.- Texto a voz: un sencillo conversor de texto a voz, con una serie de frases precargadas en inglés y español.Nota1: para eliminar municipios, provincias, palabras, periódicos, excepto en la notas, se ha de realizar una presión continuada sobre el registro que se quiere eliminar.Nota2: cuando se está buscando un municipio por provincia y se quiere seleccionar otra provincia, hay que volver a pulsar la lupa de búsqueda y seleccionar provincia.Nota3: en el navegador de la aplicación se puede acceder directamente al enlace visitado con el navegador del móvil, también se puede compartir el enlace, realizar una captura de lo que estás viendo y compartirla.

九陰 -Age of Wushu-（キュウイン）武学を極めて最強武術を手に入れよう！◇◆九陰 -Age of Wushu-の特徴◇◆スマホゲームとは思えないほどの多彩な技と武器が存在！空も飛べる爽快感、技の駆け引きで勝敗が左右する多彩な戦闘システムなど圧倒的なボリュームだからこそ実現した、やりこみ要素が満載！◇◆あらすじ◇◆時は、明朝前期。帝位を略奪した「永楽帝」は、政権を揺るぎないものにするため、陰謀を企てた。それは、伝説の秘伝書『九陰真経』を手に入れし者が究極武術を会得できるという噂の流布であった…。思惑どおり、江湖の豪傑達は、秘伝書を巡る一時的な激戦により疲弊し、朝廷に抗う者など現れはしなかった。しかし、秘伝書に疑義を抱く者たちもいた。それは…江湖でも声望の高い流派の武人たちである。君は、彼らと共に『九陰真経』の真実を解き明かすことができるのであろうか。真実に近づくほど、さらなる戦乱を呼ぶことになるとも知らずに…。■多彩なアクション戦闘■流派と武器を組み合わせた自分だけの戦闘スタイルやさらに、戦闘スタイルを強化する為の様々なパッシブスキル「攻撃」「防御」「フェイント」の駆け引きによる緊迫した戦闘など多彩な組み合わせでいまだかつてないアクション戦闘を楽しもう！■縦横無尽に空も飛べる移動方法「軽功」■「軽功」は、ジャンプや空を飛びながら移動出来る等アクロバティックなキャラクター移動が可能！■プレイヤー同士でアイテムの取引が可能な「貿易」■欲しいアイテムが手に入らない…そんなお悩みも安心！九陰では、レア装備やスキル書など入手困難なアイテムもプレイヤー同士で取引が可能！■ライバルたちと武術を磨いて競い合おう！■身に着けた戦闘スタイルでライバルたちと競い合おう！1vs1のシンプルな対戦からフラッグバトルなど様々な対戦形式が存在。自分にあった対戦方法で、頂点を目指そう！■ギルド戦や流派戦など多人数戦も充実！■1vs1だけが対戦じゃない！ギルドに加入すれば、最大25vs25のチーム戦にも参加可能！さらに、所属している流派同士でMOBA形式による対戦など多人数戦も充実！◆推奨OS◆Android 5.0以上◇公式サイト◇http://9in.snail.com◇公式Twitter◇ https://twitter.com/9in_jp◇公式Facebook◇ https://www.facebook.com/9in.ageofwushu/

With SketchBook, capture everything from your smallest doodles to your biggest ideas, all in one place, no matter where you are. Just added: Time-lapse recording is now available for Android! Easily capture in-app video of your drawing process to share with your network. We also removed the Sign In requirement for many of the advanced features. Now, just download and discover a more powerful drawing app, without signing in. We’ve also made it easier to import your traditional art onto a layer in SketchBook with Import from Camera. Mehr unter flinc.org+ Anzeige von Verkehrszeichen: Warnung vor scharfen Kurven, Überholverboten, Unfallgefahr und mehr+ Urban Guidance (b,c) - Nutzen Sie auch öffentliche Verkehrsmittel zur Navigation+ Widget für direkten Zugriff auf eigene Ziele+ Aktiver Fahrspurassistent (a)+ Bluetooth-Unterstützung HFP oder A2DP (a)+ Lokale POI Suche (c)+ Foursquare POI Suche (c)+ Glympse - Sende Sie Ihre Position ausgewählten Kontaken (c)+ Traffic Live Verkehrsinformation (a,c)+ Radar Info für fix installierte Anlagen (a)+ Reality View Pro (a)+ Aktiver Fahrspurassistent (a)+ Geschwindigkeitsassistent (a)+ NAVIGON Reality Scanner (a)+ NAVIGON MyRoutes (a)+ Panorama View 3D (b)+ Text-to-Speech (a) und präzise Sprachansagen+ verschiedene Stimmen (Dialekte) (a)+ Erweiterte Fußgängernavigation+ Koordinateneingabe (a)+ NAVIGON FreshMaps XL – Alle Karten Europas mit und zwei Jahre lang bis zu viermal jährlich die neusten Kartenupdates aus Expertenhand!(b) + NAVIGON cockpit (b)+ Mobile Alert Live (b,c)+ NAVIGON LPG + Bio-Diesel Tankstellenfinder (b)+ 2D und 3D Kartendarstellung + Direktzugriff auf Kontaktadressen (a)+ Nach-Hause-Funktion mit einem Klick+ Smartwatch Connect - Ermöglicht Fussgängernavigation auf der SONY SmartWatch 2 bzw. der Samsung Gear 2/neo. Erfordert zusätzlich die Installation der kostenfreien Erweiterung "NAVIGON Smartwatch Connect", verfügbar in Google Play bzw. Samsung Apps im Gear manager (b)+ Kartenmaterial - Neukunden erhalten das zum Zeitpunkt der App-Installation neuestes NAVIGON Kartenmaterial vom Marktführer HERE für AT, CH, DE und LI(a) Optional bei Select(b) Optional für alle(c) Dieser Service benötigt eine Datenverbindung(d) Ab android 2.3.3WICHTIGE HINWEISE:Es werden ca. 1,6GB freier Speicherplatz benötigt. Bitte stellen Sie sicher, dass ausreichend Speicher zur Verfügung steht. Das Kartenmaterial muss bei einigen Telefonen nach der Installation der App per WiFi (WLAN) geladen werden. Bitte achten Sie unbedingt auf eine stabile und sichere Datenverbindung! Beim ersten Starten MÜSSEN ca.25kB als "Mobile Daten" zur Registrierung der App gesendet werden. Danach kann, wenn gewünscht, in den Einstellungen der App jedwede Datenverbindung durch NAVIGON abgeschaltet werden (Internetverbindung nutzen...). Bitte beachten Sie, dass dann alle mit (c) gekennzeichneten Services und der In-App Shop nicht mehr zur Verfügung stehen.In Roaming-Gebieten benötigt die App, solang noch kein Paket erworben ist, von Zeit zu Zeit eine Prüfung des Netzwerks. Sollte NAVIGON im Ausland einmal nicht starten, aktivieren Sie bitte die Datenverbindung bis die app gestartet ist. In diesem Fall werden ca. 15kB gesendet.NAVIGON wünscht Ihnen viel Spaß beim Navigieren – ganz gleich ob im Auto, auf dem Fahrrad oder zu Fuß!

The GPS Test app for Android is a utility that shows GPS information read from your phones internal GPS. Will support GLONASS phones. The app has several colour schemes, which could be used to match other instrumentation, used along side the app. It has a "night mode" colour scheme as well.If you like this app, please like GPS Test on Facebook: -http://www.facebook.com/gpstestGPS Test has five screens full of information: -1) GPS signal (SNR) bar chart, showing the signal strength for each satellite, as well as the accuracy and status of the GPS.2) Satellite positions in the sky (skyview), shown on a rotating compass.3) Your current location on the earth shown as text and on a world map. The current position of the sun and the day/night transition curve is also shown.4) Your current speed, heading and altitude shown as text.5) The current time read from the GPS and the local time in your current timezone, as well as the sunrise and sunset times at your location.Coordinate Grids supported by GPS Test:-OSGB, UTM, MGRS, USNG, CH1903, Maidenhead.Datums supported by GPS Test:-WGS84, NAD83, NAD27, ED50, AGD66, AGD84, SAD69If you like this app please look at ***GPS TEST PLUS***.Which has:-* Simple Navigation.* Location Sharing (email, sms, twitter etc)* Dials (Altimeter, Speedo and Compass)* 7 segment LED font* Dot Matrix font* HUD modeWorks on Honeycomb O/S and large screen tablets.GPS Test blog - http://gpstestapp.blogspot.com/INTERNET permissions are only required for analytics and app wall in the AppBrain library. The app will work fine without a WiFi or data conection.

App Store ve Play Store'de bulabileceğiniz bu harika uygulama, farklı birçok dil seçeneği ile matematikte kullanılan tüm temel formülleri sunmaktadır. İçerdiği ana başlıklar şunlardır: - Geometri - Cebir - Trigonometri - Denklemler - Analitik Geometri - Türev - İntegral - Birim Çevirici Bu uygulama aynı zamanda geometrik şekilleri hesaplamak veya denklemlerin köklerini bulmak için birçok araç sunar. Ayrıca kullanıcılar istedikleri formülleri E-posta, yazıcı çıktısı veya facebook gibi birçok yolla paylaşabilir. Uygulamanın yeni özellikleri: - Çoklu dil desteği: İngilizce, Fransızca, Vietnamca, Çince, Japonca, İspanyolca, Almanca, Korece, Rusça, Portekizce, İtalyanca, Yunanca, Endonezyaca Tayca, Arapça, Hintçe, Bengalce, Malayca ve Türkçe. Kullanıcılar, dil butonu ile İngilizce ve diğer diller arasında geçiş yapabilirler. Yakında daha fazla dil seçeneği ile karşınızda olacağız. - Favoriler : Kullanıcılar bu klasöre sık kullandıkları formülleri kaydedebilirler. - Arama fonksiyonu: Her kategoride Arama çubuğuna yazarak hızlıca istediğiniz formülü bulun. Holen Sie sich die innovativste Benzinpreis-App für unterwegs. Mit der TankenApp tanken Sie immer an der richtigen Tankstelle – zum richtigen Zeitpunkt. Dank top-aktueller Preisdaten, intelligenter Preisprognose, Preisempfehlungen entlang einer Strecke, und vieler weiterer Funktionen ist es jetzt so einfach wie noch nie zuvor, beim Tanken bares Geld zu sparen. Wir nutzen die Daten der Markttransparenzstelle.AKTUELLE BENZINPREISDATEN: Jeden Werktag 200.000 Preisaktualisierungen, dabei werden 10.000 Tankstellen mindestens einmal täglich aktualisiert.BENZINPREIS-PROGNOSE: Jetzt oder später tanken? Die Antwort liefert die Prognose der Preisentwicklung der nächsten 12 Stunden.SUCHE ENTLANG EINER STRECKE: Suche nach günstigstem Benzinpreis entlang einer Strecke (z.B. Berlin – Hamburg).GPS-ORTUNG: Preisempfehlungen auf Wunsch durch automatische GPS-Ortung sorgen für maximalen Komfort. Eine Alternative bietet die intuitive Suche nach Postleitzahl oder Ort.BENZINPREISALARM: Eine Push-Nachricht erinnert Sie, sobald ein von Ihnen eingestellter Preis unterschritten wird. InkPad Notepad is the simple, elegant, easy way to keep notes on your phone, or on the web.Once upon a time, you had to write down notes in a paper notepad and carry it around with you. If you wrote a shopping list or to do list, you might go to the store and discover you had forgotten your notepad. But how often do you forget to bring your mobile phone with you? Introducing InkPad, the notepad you’ll only forget as often as your phone!Inkpad Notepad let's you access your notes online at www.InkpadNotepad.com. You can create or edit notes from the convenience of your computer's web browser, and always have access to your notes from your phone when you're offline too.CREATE NOTESInkPad is designed to look like a paper notepad, and is just as simple to use. When you open InkPad, you’ll see a list of all notes you’ve created. To add a new note, tap on the “+” button at the bottom of the screen. The first line of text will automatically be used as the title.CREATE TO DO LISTCreate a note as usual, then select the "to do list" button at the top of the note screen.CREATE SHOPPING LISTCreate a note as usual, then select the "shopping list" button at the top of the note.EDIT NOTE OR TO DO LISTNow you can write your note. Just like a paper notepad, you don’t have to do anything special to save your notes, they are auto-saved for you.SAVEAs mentioned above, notes are auto-saved. You don’t have to do anything special to save them.BACKUP NOTES TO SD CARDBy default, notes are backed up to SD card as text files. You can turn this feature off in Notepad Settings.SYNC NOTES ONLINEWith version 2.0, Inkpad Notepad now lets you sync/backup notes online. You can access your online notes at www.InkpadNotepad.com by signing in with the same Google account you selected in the mobile app.SEARCH YOUR NOTES OR TO DO LISTSInkpad Notepad now gives you an option to search your notes or to do lists. From the home screen, tap on the search icon, then begin writing. As you write, the list of notes will be filtered to only display notes containing the search keyword. Press the "X" button to close note search, and view all notes as usual.SHARE NOTESAt the bottom of each note is a “share” button. Tapping it brings up all the ways to share. Typical ways include email, SMS, etc. CHANGE NOTE’S TITLETo change a notes title, tap on the title area at the top of that note.DELETE NOTEIf you don’t want a note any longer, you can delete it in several ways: 1) Open the note, tap the “delete” button at the bottom of the page. 2) From the main notes screen, long-press the title of a note, then tap on “delete”.REMOVE ADSThe free version of InkPad Notepad is ad supported. If you would like to remove the ads and support the continued development of InkPad Notepad, you can do so. From the main screen, press your phone’s menu button, then tap the “remove ads” button.BACKUP NOTESTo backup a note, press the share button and email to yourself the note you want to backup.TYPICAL USESWrite To do lists (Note: check-list support is now here for to do lists!), shopping lists, addresses, email, SMS, Twitter updates*, write lyrics, poems, or even a novel if you feel like it! The uses are limited only by your imagination.Follow @workpail on twitter (http://twitter.com/workpail) and facebook (http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100001471431772) to receive updates about InkPad Note pad.Known issues: some users have experienced problems when using Swype keyboard, please email me if you have problems. Atrix users with previously installed version of the note pad will have to change the font to "Android default font".*Assumes separate Twitter client is installed, Twitter cannot post note pad content longer than 140 characters.

A 2nd number for your personal smartphone—that’s your Sideline. Sideline is the free phone solution for small businesses, entrepreneurs, freelancers, or anyone who needs a 2nd phone line. Now you can keep work and life on separate numbers, not separate phones.ADD A FREE NUMBER IN YOUR AREA CODEIf you need a local number, just select the area code and get a number that works wherever you do. You get to talk and text from a dedicated business line—and because it’s a real phone number, you can call and text anyone, even landlines. CALLING & TEXTINGYour second number works just like your first. Separate caller IDs, notifications, and ringtones make it clear who’s contacting you. For outbound communication, just open Sideline. With your free phone number, you get unlimited texting and Sideline calling uses the carrier plan you already have.CARRIER CALL QUALITY, FROM AN APPSideline works with your carrier network to give you the quality and reliability you need to work from anywhere. This also lets you split your calling minutes (which are probably unlimited) between two numbers. Unlike “cloud-based,” “virtual,” or buzzword phone systems, Sideline doesn’t rely on a perfect WiFi signal or expensive data plan to keep you connected. KEEP YOUR PERSONAL NUMBER PRIVATEYou probably shouldn’t give out your personal phone to just everyone. That’s why there’s Sideline. But it’s not just a second phone line for work. It can be your temporary number. Your anonymous number. Your work phone. Your disposable number. Your fake phone number. It’s whatever you need it to be to protect your primary cell number.MORE FEATURESOn top of your free phone number, Sideline comes with nifty features such as SMS text messaging, MMS picture messaging, group messaging, custom voicemail, stickers, and emoji. All for free.

Glide is the live video messaging app for people who want more personality and expression when communicating with those who know them best. If you're feeling that text can't say enough, you're ready for Glide. Get a little closer.▶ HOW GLIDE WORKS• Just hit the blue button and speak naturally into the camera. Tap it when you’re done and your video message gets sent immediately. It can be 3 seconds or up to 5 minutes of your you-ness.• Someone can actually watch as you’re recording your video, or whenever they have a chance. Techies call this “asynchronous.” We call it massively convenient. • Is it more fun to send or receive a Glide? That’s a cosmic question. The answer is “yes”• All of your videos are stored on the cloud, so they don’t take up any space on your device. It’s unlimited and free!• To record and share what’s happening around you – a parade, a field of dreams – just switch to the outward-facing camera. Your friends will feel that they’re right there with you.• It’s a new form of back-and-forth chat that helps relationships sparkle by collapsing time and distance, even if “distance” is just across the street. • Glide group chats are easy to create – set them up on the fly, with up to 50 of your closest friends.• Works on Android and iOS - all phones, tablets and the Apple Watch. Communicates on WiFi, 3G, 4G & LTE. ▶ BEYOND THE BASICS• Share photos, too – on Glide messenger or social media• ZOOM in and out while recording a video, for added drama• Too much coffee causing hand-shake? Tap to focus while you’re shooting• Romantic lighting? Not a problem. Glide uses your device’s flash to brighten up• Cool filters make your videos look awesome• Super Emojis - express how you feel with a smiley on steroids• ASL and deaf friendly instant video messaging ▶ GLIDE IS BUZZING"Glide's rapid-fire video-messaging approach works remarkably well for live conversations, and it's nice to have the option to leave your friends and family messages that they can watch later." - CNET"Glide live video messaging software is like video voicemail for mobile devices" - Forbes"Although the first-generation Apple Watch lacks a built-in camera, Glide for Apple Watch is the closest thing to the stuff of science fiction people have been dreaming up for years." - idownloadblog.com▶ WE'RE AN AWARD WINNING MESSENGER!• TechCrunch Disrupt NY - Startup Alley "Audience Choice" Winner• Best Apps Market - "Best Apps Award"• Featured by Apple in Great Free Apps, New & Noteworthy + What’s Hot ▶ GET IN TOUCH WITH USVisit our website: www.glide.meFacebook: www.facebook.com/glidemeTwitter: www.twitter.com/glideapp or @sarahglideInstagram: www.instagram.com/theglideappNeed help? support@glide.me

تطبيق رياض الصالحين مع الشرح المبسط هو تطبيق إسلامى لأجهزة الأندرويد يحتوى على جميع أحاديث كتاب رياض الصالحين للإمام النووي مع الشرح المبسط من كتاب تطريز رياض الصالحين لفضيلة الشيخ فيصل المبارك. البرنامج مجانى تماما وهو أيضا خالى تماما من الإعلانات كباقي تطبيقاتي الإسلاميةمميزات وخصائص البرنامج:- جميع أحاديث كتاب رياض الصالحين مع الشرح، مقسمة إلى كتب وأبواب- التعريف بلإمام النووي ونبذة قصيرة عنه...- التعريف بالشيخ فيصل المبارك ونبذة قصيرة عنه...- مجانى تماما وخالى تماما من الإعلانات- إمكانية البحث عن حديث- إمكانية إضافة الأحاديث إلى المفضلة- إمكانية إضافة الملاحظات على الأبواب- إمكانية تغيير نوع وحجم الخط- إمكانية إظهار أو إخفاء التشكيل- إمكانية تغيير ثيم البرنامج- لا يحتاج إلى الإتصال بالإنترنت- لا يحتاج إلى أي صلاحيات خاصة- الإلتزام بمعايير جوجل للتصميم- سيتم إضافة المزيد إن شاء اللهسيتم تحسين التطبيق فى النسخ القادمة إن شاء اللهأرجو إرسال إقتراحاتكمإذا واجهتك أي مشاكل بعد التحديث، يمكنك أن تقوم بتحميل أي من النسخ القديمة من هذا اللينك:http://goo.gl/hPT0Jإذا وجدت أى مشكلة أو خطأ فى البرنامج لا تتردد فى مراسلتيعن كتاب رياض الصالحين:كتاب مختصر جمعه المصنف من الأحاديث الصحيحة، مشتملًا على ما يكون طريقًا لصاحبه إلى الآخرة جامعًا للترغيب والترهيب والزهد ورياضات النفوس، وقد التزم فيه أن لا يذكر إلا الأحاديث الصحيحة، وأحاديثه في مواضيع مختلفة مثل: العبادات، والمعاملات، والعادات، بحيث يصدر المؤلف جملة الأحاديث بعنوان لما تتضمنه الأحاديث بحيث يكون بابا لتلك الأحاديث.عن كتاب الشرح (تطريز رياض الصالحين):هذا كتاب شرح فيه مؤلفه كتاب رياض الصَّالحين للإمام النووي شرحًا مختصرًا جدًّا، مكتفيًا بشرح غريب بعض الألفاظ الواردة في أحاديث الكتاب، وذكر بعض الفوائد المستفادة والمستنبطة من الأحاديث الواردة في الكتاب. The HP Print Service Plugin enables printing on your AndroidTM KitkatTM (v4.4) and newer device without the need for additional print drivers. This app supports a large variety of HP Printers including HP OfficeJet, HP LaserJet, HP DesignJet, HP Photosmart, HP DeskJet and HP Envy.Easily print from Gallery, Photos, Gmail, Yahoo Mail, Chrome, Google Drive and many other applications supporting print. Just tap the menu button to reveal the print option. Location of menu button may vary depending on your model of AndroidTM device. Discover and print to HP printers that are:•Connected to the same network as your mobile device.•Broadcasting a Wi-Fi Direct network on supported HP Printers.•Connected to the mobile device via a USB On-the-Go cable.After installing the HP Print Service Plugin, it is important to turn on the plugin. This is done by going to SettingsPrintingHP Print Service Plugin under the General Settings section from many devices and toggling the setting to “On”. For Samsung devices, it is done by going to Settings -> NFC and sharing -> Printing -> HP Print Service PluginFor more information on using the HP Print Service Plugin or details on supported HP Printers, please refer to the following URL:http://support.hp.com/us-en/document/c04024231For more information on Mobile Printing in general, please also refer to:http://www.hp.com/go/mobileprinting

Verpasste Sendungen nachschauen oder live erleben: Mit der App der ARD Mediathek haben Sie jederzeit bequemen Zugriff auf die mobil verfügbaren TV-Angebote des Ersten, der Dritten Programme, der ARD-Digitalkanäle sowie von arte und 3sat. Viele Fernsehsendungen der ARD gibt es als Video-on-Demand oder Video-Podcast. Zudem gibt es rund um die Uhr News, Musik und Hintergrundinfos in den Radio-Livestreams der ARD-Wellen. Folgende Funktionen bietet Ihnen die App der ARD Mediathek: Sie können - alle TV- und Radio-Livestreams nutzen- verpasste Sendungen nach Datum (7-Tage-Rückschau) finden, - Film-Highlights, z.B. den "Tatort" oder den "Polizeiruf 110" finden,- in der Rubrik "Reportage & Doku" stöbern,- mit der Suchfunktion gezielt nach Sendungen oder Podcasts recherchieren,- mit der "Empfehlen"-Funktion Clips in den sozialen Netzwerken oder per Mail mit Freunden und Bekannten teilen- zum Download bereitgestellte Videos und Audios auf Ihr Gerät laden- Videos und Audios über ein externes Gerät (z.B. Chromecast oder Apple TV) nutzen- in der Rubrik "Einslike" Videos von Einsplus, Einsfestival und den jungen Hörfunkwellen anschauenDie App der ARD Mediathek ist kostenlos. Da der Abruf von Videos in der Regel hohen Datentransfer verursacht, empfehlen wir jedoch die Nutzung mit einer Daten-Flatrate oder im WLAN-Netz. Hier ist zudem die Qualität der Videos am höchsten.

'15.3.16일 이전 『롤리팝(5.0.1)업그레이드로 스마트뱅킹 접속』이 안되실 경우＊환경설정앱 - 앱(또는 애플리케이션 관리자) - 전체보기 - Android System Webview를 선택후 해당앱이 버전 40으로 나타나는 경우에는 업데이트삭제를 실행시켜 주세요.＊안드로이드 시스템 웹뷰 40버전의 오류로 인한 NH스마트뱅킹의 로딩화면이 차단되고 있는 현상입니다.＊단, '15.3.16일 이후 업그레이드를 실행하신 고객님은 구글에서 웹뷰 37버전을 포함후 업그레이드 하고 있으므로 본 조치사항은 필요 없습니다. 12.14일버전 업그레이드[업그레이드 사항]* 다계좌이체 버튼 동작이 안될 경우 및 거래화면에서 일부 동작이 비정상 경우 조치* 이미지가 깨지거나(엑스박스) 비정상적으로 크거나 작게 나오는 화면 UI관련 오류 조치* 보안키패드UI가 정상적이지 않은 경우(버튼끼리 겹쳐서 입력에 제한 등) 조치* 농협 앱 간 실행 시 (뱅킹->카드 또는 카드->뱅킹) 강제종료 현상 조치[다운로드 유의사항]안전한 금융거래를 위해 루팅한 단말기에서는(과거 루팅 시도 등) NH스마트뱅킹 서비스 이용이 불가합니다. 해당 단말기는 제조사 A/S센터 등을 통해 완전초기화 후 NH스마트뱅킹 어플을 설치/이용하시기 바랍니다.*루팅 : 단말기의 OS를 임의변조하거나 악성코드 등에 의해 변조된 경우(보안이 취약한 상태로 거래의 안전성을 보장할 수 없음)안드로이드 os 2.2 이상의 모든 버젼 및 갤럭시s2, 베가레이서 등의 최신폰을 포함한 모든 스마트폰/태블릿PC에서 뱅킹 사용이 가능합니다.설치시 '출처를 알 수 없는 소스' 와 같은 메세지가 나와 설치가 안되는 경우는 환경설정->응용프로그램->알수없는 소스 를 설치 허용으로 설정한 후 스마트뱅킹 설치를 하시면 됩니다. 설치후 위 설정값은 원래대로 설치허용을 해제하여 주십시요.OS 4.0 아이스크림 샌드위치으로 업그레이드후, 보안엔진 모듈 화면에서 진행이 되지 않는 경우, 인증서 로그인 시 '전자서명오류' 발생 시 에는 환경설정 - 개발자옵션 - 활동보관안함(체크해제) - 백그라운드 프로세스 제한(표준제한)으로 설정을 바꾸시면 원활한 서비스가 가능합니다. NH스마트뱅킹 설치 시 '기본 설치 위치에 애플리케이션을 설치할 수 없습니다.' 와 같은 메시지가 출력 되는 경우는 해당 기기의 '시스템메모리' 영역에 남는 용량이 적을 경우 발생됩니다.환경설정 - 저장소 메뉴로 가서 기기에 남은 시스템메모리를 확인 하시고 용량이 적게 남았을 경우불필요하거나 사용하시지 않는 앱을 삭제하시면 정상적으로 설치 및 사용이 가능하십니다.명품처럼 소장가치가 있는~~ NH스마트뱅킹 세상에서는○ 명품디자인과 사용자 편의에 맞는 최적화○ 다양한 금융서비스(조회,이체,펀드,대출,카드,공과금납부 등)제공○ 농협만이 할 수 있는 다양한 특화서비스(농산물/쇠고기 이력조회,로또서비스, 증강현실을 통한 영업점찾기 등)를 제공합니다~~ "15 .3.16 dienų iki atvejis andoesil" saldainis (5.0.1) modernizuotos su smart bankų ryšį.
